42006035	Dopa pilyaminyipape nakamana nyisu angae karo karaminyi dupwa mona reto yulu pyakamyuo bange isingi nyero lao suu pyaa nao mee maiyuo karalapape . Dopa piraminyi dokopa yole kuHsa nyerami . 42006037	Wambu dupwa kando yapalya yapana pyuo suu pyao kara nalapape . Dopa pii narami ramo dokopa Anatumi nakama kando yapalya yapana pyuo suu pyao kara nara . 42006044	Isa dupwa peparaena jingi dupwa kando dokopa isa doko keyangelamo lao isa doko koolamo lao namwa soo gisingi . Doko suu pyao nepereke dokona piki jingi lyii nange . Girapo isa mende ikyalkya dokona lyii nangeko .

42007007	Dokona namba opetae emba karene dokona kapa epa naroko lao suu pyapala epa napu . Doko embame mee pii lao dokopa , nambana kendemande akali mee inginya lakape .

42007010	Dokopa akali epeyami dusipa kapu kyuo anda papala kendemande akali baa mee ingiyamo siyamo kandeyami .

42007012	Anda malu palyuo karenge dokona anda dupwa nyuo sukusa pyambuo kana kame piyami dokona kambu repeta epeyamo dokopa akali mende kumuyasa soo neta epeyami . 42009010	Aposele dupwa kapu kyuo epapala dopa pimwa dopa pimwa lao Yesu lamaiyami . Dokopa baame banya disaepole dusipa lanyuo yuu taone Betesaita lenge dokona nakama iki yapaiyuo kakondo peyami .
42009011	Wambu rukuraka pyuo kareyami dupwa baa dokona pamolyamo lao sepala baa peyamo dokona moko minyuo peyami . Dokopa baame nakama yako lapala Anatunya isingi yulu dokona lao nakama mana lamaiyuo anga pingi wambu nyisapenge dupwa pyuo nyepa piya .
42009012	Yuu kwuaya dokopa akali akalisa ipisu lama dusipa baa kareyamo dokona epapala dopa lamaiyami . Namwa yuu muiyane dakena karamano dokona wambu malu rukuraka pyuo karaminyi dupwa yuu andape dupwanale nenge nyuo nao luu pali pena lape , leyami .
42009013	Dopa leyaminyipape baame nakama lamaiyuo , Nakama rangeme nenge lapo maiyalapape , leya . Nakamame lao , Namwana borete kingi pakipi oma lamape dolapo iki silyamo . Wambu dapwa peparaena nenge ropo pyala pena lepe .
42009014	( Akali malu mee wakasa 5,000 ) kareyami dokona suu pyao leyami . ) Dokopa baame banya disaepole dusipa lamaiyuo . Wambu dupwa akalisa kingi paki larapu malu palyara malu palyara pyuo petena lalapape , leya .
42009015	Dokopa nakamame wambu dopa pyuo peparae isa petena leyami .
42009016	Dokopa borete kingi pakipi oma lamape dolapo nyepala yake dulu kandalyo kandapala ateŋa lao ange leya . Lapala nenge minyuo kau lapala wambu malu peteyami dupwana lenge kambu siyamo dupwana retena lao banya disaepole dupwa maipa piya .
42009017	Reteyaminyisa wambu malumi neyaminyipa sikya piya . Enakana nenge kau lasi kakana siyamo dupwa yapo nyuo pisiki minyasi akalisa ipisu lama dusipana paki pyuo simbuyami .
42009018	Yuu mendepa Yesu baa iki ateŋa lao peteyamo dokopa banya disaepole dusipa role pyao peteyami . Dokopa baame nakama piso soo , Wambu dupwame namba kando apiŋi lao apa lami kandapisi ? leya .
42009019	Dokopa nakamame isingi lao , Wambu lapome emba Jone bapitisimo nyakamalngi doko lenge . Lapome emba Ilalnja ienge , lapome yuu wamba akali Anatumi pyongo piyamopa nolako lao kareyami dokona mende kumuo palyuo lopo ipyalyamo lenge , leyami .
42009020	Dokopa baame nakama lamaiyuo , Dopa lao lalyaminyiko doŋo nakama rangeme namba apiŋi lao suu pilyamisi ? leya . Dokopa Pitame lao , Emba Anatunya Koraisa doko leya .
42009021	Dokopa , dopa pyuondeŋe lao wambu mende lamai nalapape , lamaiyuokondali pyuo leya .
42009022	Ikinyingi Akali yaso koo naramopa Kamongo dupwamoo purisi akali mupwa dupwape Mawa Pii mana lenge akali dupwapeme banya pii soo nyii narami . Nakama baa pyao kumakarami . Pyao kumakaraminyipa kumuo palyuo yuu rema epo paparamopa baa dee sipuro epara ingilyamo , leya .
42009023	Lapala wambu peteyami dupwa peparae lamaiyuo dopa leya . Akali mendeme namba paronoli pyuo eparo lao suu pyara ramo doko baa range kame soo kaepala yuu yangaramo yaka lao banya isa mamando minyalyuo nyepala soo namba paronuli pyuo epara .
42009024	Dokona lao mendeme banya yanenge range lete wal pyao nyero lao suu pyara ramo doko kyakana renge doko isa nembarasa pira . Mendeme baa namba reke lao kumara ramo doko kyakana renge kando nyepala lete wal pyao parasa pira .
42009025	Dokona akali mendeme bange yuu muu dupwana peparae silyamo dupwa nyuo reto karara ramo dokopa koo keta paramo doko bange dupwame baa nyisarape ?
42009026	Mendeme nambana pii dokonape nambana kingi dokope elya nyuo karara ramo doko , Rakangemoo aŋala poo pyasi dupwa pipya yanga paupau andake lao eparaminyi dokopa Ikinyingi Akali dokome yanga paupau andake lao epapala wambu nakama kando elya nyerako .
42009027	Dopa piramopape wambu dae karaminyi dupwana lapo ene kuma napala Anatunya isingi yulu doko kandarami , doko kinyi langilyu leya .
42009028	Pii dupwa dopa lapala yuu mange lama nyero ingyuowale epo papeyamopa Yesumi Pitamoo Jemesa Jonemoo lanyuo yuu kyau ketae dokona ateŋa lala peyami .
42009029	Papala baa ateŋa lao kareyamo dokopa banya lenge kambu doko wakale maro leya . Dokopa banya komau ama kyewa lao mama nyepala lepo lepo piya .
42009030	Dokopa akali Mosesepa Ilainjapa nakamba baamoo pii lao kareyamipya .
42009031	Akali dolapo yanga paupau lao pano epapala Yesu Jerusaleme dokona Anatu laramuli pyuo kumara dokona lao kareyami .
42009032	Pitamoo akali baa role pyao kareyami dolapo pipya lenge kenda kenda piyamopape luu pali napala baa yanga paupau leyamo dokope akali baa role pyao kareyami dolapope angi kandeyami .
42009033	Kandapala akali dolapo Yesu yaki nyuo panya piyambinyi dokopa Pitame Yesu lamaiyuo , Rapu Pingi , namwa dae kapa karamano . Anda paka rema yukumanale . 42009036	Pii lao otapeyamo dokopa Yesu baa iki kareyamo kandeyami . Dokopa yuu gii dusipana dopa piyamo kandeyama lao mendali lamai nao kalyamo kareyami .
42009037	Dokona yangama dokopa yuu kyau doko yaki nyuo epeyami dokopa wambu malu mee rukuraka pyuo baa kando nyela epeyami .
42009038	Dokopa wambu malu kareyami dokona akali mendeme pii ketae palyuo dopa leya . Mana Lenge , nambana ikinyingi doko embame kandakala ipib' yaka lao langilyu . Baa nambana wane mendaki baako ikiŋi leya .
42009039	Imambu mendeme baa minyarelyamopa baa aopa ala lenge . Dopa pilyamopa pungwa pungwa pyao karo kambu apupu epo pilyamopa waiya lao paa napala baa uki palyingi .
42009040	Nambame embena disaepole dusipa raka lanyi nembakana lapunu doko nembalana saka nami leya .
42009041	Yesumi isingi lao dopa leya . Nakama wambu epapu isa anda karaminyi dupwa , Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyaa napala simbi simbi pyuo karaminyi . 42009042	Wane baa ene epeyamo dokopa imambu koo dokome nyuo mangalo kyaso reteyamosa pungwa pungwa pyao siya . Dopa piyamopape Yesumi imambu koo doko pyalana pyuo lamaipala wane doko pyuo elya pyuo nyiya . Pyuo nyepala banya rakange doko range maiya .
42009043	Dokopa wambu peparae , Anatu baa ama porai wakasa karamo , lao mona nembeyami . Baame yulu wakale wakale pyuo kareyamo dupwa kandapala wambu peparaeme yako lao kareyaminyipa baame banya disaepole dupwa kando dopa lamaiyuo leya .
42009044	Pii mende langiru doko nakamana kale kata dokona epo palu palyuo palena . Doko akali lapome Ikinyingi Akali doko puu maiyapala wambu pinya lao mairami , leya .
42009045	Dopa leyamopape banya pii doko soo gisa nayami . Pii renge doko kyanga pyaro kareyasa nakamame soo nyepa napala baa pii dokona renge piso selana pakayami .
42009046	Yuu mendepa disaepole akali yango sukusa api angi mupwa lao apiyanda pyuo kareyami .
42009047	Yesumi nakama monarena suu pyao kareyaminyi doko kando sepala wane mende nyepala banya paralisa pisiya .
42009048	Pisapala baame nakama dopa lamaiya . Mendeme nambana kingi lao wane dake yako lao nyerami ramo doko namba yako lao nyeramisa pira . Nakama peparae karaminyi dokona api mende kamame kuki ingyuo karamo doko baa mupwa ingyuo karapyamosa pilyamo , leya .
42009049	Dopa leyamo dokopa Joneme lao dopa leya . Rapu Pingi , akali mendeme embena kingi lao imambu koo raka lanyi nembo karapyamo kandapala baame namwa role pyao kara nange dokona kaena lamwa , leya .
42009050	Dopa leyamopape Yesumi baa lamaiyuo , Baa kaena laa nalapape . Mendeme nakama kando sisu nyuo kara nalyaminyi baa nakama nyiso kararasa pira leya .
42009051	Anatumi Yesu ketae minyalyuo nyera yuu gii doko repeta epeyamo dokopa baa Jerusaleme dorena panya suu pyapala kata nyiya .

42009053	Peyaminyi dokopa banya lenge kambu Jerusaleme dorena pambwaro karo panya lao epeyamo dokoko kandapala Samaria wambu dupwame baa yako lao nyii nayami .
42009054	Dopa piyaminyi doko kandapala banya disaepole Jemesa Jonepa dolapome Yesu kando dopa lamaiyambi . Kamongo , isare yake panda piso lupyuo epapala nakama rao otena lambape , leyambi .
42009055	Dopa pyuo leyambinyi dokopa baa kapu kyepala nakamba kaena lao pyalana pyuo lamaiya .
42009056	Dokopa nakama anda kuki lama repe repe pyuo karenge wakale mendena peyami .

42009058	Dokopa Yesumi baa dopa lamaiya . Yana suwa kararope dupwa yuu rumbyapala palyuope yaka bii lao papingi dupwa anda pipala palyuo pilyaminyipa lkinyingi Akali doko luu palinya mendasa ayemba retowape pira ingya nange leya .
42009059	Lapala Yesumi akali mende lamaiyuo , Namba paronuli pyuo ipu leya . Leyamo dokopa baa dopa leya . Kamongo , nambana rakange wambo malu pela paparole leya .
42009060	Dopa leyamopape baame baa dopa lamaiya . Kumasi dupwame nakama rangena kumasi yango dupwa malu pinya . Embame Anatunya isingi yulu dokona lao boo pyao pupi , leya .
42009061	Akali mendalimi dopa leya . Kamongo , namba emba parenyili pyuo eparoko doŋo nambana ree palu anda karaminyi dupwa yako lao nakama wambo karena lapapuli yaka leya .
42009062	Dokopa Yesumi baa dopa lamaiya . Mendeme yuu apu renge masene doko minyaro karo kapu kyilyapala matarena kandara doko Anatunya isingi yulu dokona sukusa kapa karara ingya nalyamo leya .
42010001	Dopa lapala enakana Kamongo dokome wambu akalisa yanda ipingi dee ipisu lamape rombo palyapala lama lao pakarapu yuu taone dupwana baa enakana para ingiyamo dupwana wambo pena leya .
42010002	Pena lao dopa lamaiya . Nenge mahi wambu pipyamopa manjo nyerami dupwa kuki lama karaminyi . Dokona ee rangena kamongo dokome yulu pingi akali lapo opetae ee doko manja pena lapyali yaka lao ateŋa lalapape .
42010003	Nakama kata nyuo pupwa . Nakama sipisipi ikyanena mendeke karaminyipa suwa reeko wambu nalana pyuo karaminyi sukusa dokona pupwa lao letoŋo .
42010004	Pakeya minya nao nyuu byake manja nao kimbu suu mende manja naoko papala katasa wambu mende yako laa nalapapeko .
42010005	Anda mendena kolando parami ramo dokopa , Anda dakena mona sipyamopa karamili yaka lao wambo lalapape .
42010006	Dokopa akali mende mona seramopa kareya kande doko nakamana mona kyuu lao singi renge doko baa keta palira . Akali mona seramopa kara nara ramo dokopa renge doko nakama range keta epo palira .
42010007	Anda nakama yako lao nyerami dokonako iki palipwape . Yulu pingi akali yole nyingi doko suu pyao nakama nengepe ipwangepe joo kararami dupwa mee nao palipwape . Anda kambu yaka laa nalapape .
42010008	Nakama taone mendena parami dokopa dokona nakama yako lao nyerami ramo doko nenge jerami doko yakaŋa lao nalapape .
42010009	Nakamana anga pingi wambu dupwa pyuo nyepala nakama lamaiyuo , Anatunya isingi yulu doko nakama repeta ipya lyakande , lao lamaipape .
42010010	Anda malu palyuo karenge mendena sukusa paraminyi yuu range wambu dupwame nakama yako lao nyii narami ramo dokopa nakamana anda kambu dokona karo dopa lalapape .
42010011	Nakamana anda taone dakena yuu sinjimu dokome nambwana kimbu dokona parepeta sipyamo dokoko nakama kwao karaminyi lao lasaka pyuo pyarendanyi nembakalyambanoŋo . Anatunya isingi yulu doko nakama repeta ipwa doko kame see nalapape , lao lamaipwape .
42010012	Nambame nakama dopa langilyu , Yuu gii angi pyaka seramo dokopa yuu malu palyuo karenge dokona range dupwa yuu Sotoma range dupwa randa nao kareyaminyipape nakama kamame wakasa narami lyakande .
42010013	Nakamana yuu Korasina wambu dupwa nakama keta randa narami . Betesalta wambu dupwa nakama keta randa naramiko . 42010014	Dokona suu pyao Anatumi kote laramo dokopa nakama randa andake naraminyipa Taya Saltonepa range kuki pyuo narami .
42010015	Dee , yuu Kapaneame range wambu dupwa nakama rangeme yake panda dokona range minyalyuo nyeramipi ? Ama daa , nakama panda koo dokona isa maiyaramisa pira .
42010016	Mendeme nakamana pii sera ramo doko nambana pii serasa pira . Mendeme nakama rekya lanyi nembara ramo doko namba rekya lanyi nembarasako pira . Mendeme namba rekya lanyi nembara ramo doko namba mapanyi peeyamo doko kando rekya lanyi nembarasa pira ingilyamo leya .
42010017	Wambu akalisa yanda ipingi ipisu lama wambo pena leyamo dupwa mona pyakalyuo pyao laeyo epapala lao , Kamongo embena kingi lao karamwanopa imambu koo dupwa namwana pii warombo sepala pilyaminyiko leyami .
42010018	Dokopa Yesumi nakama dopa lamaiya . Satane baa yuu pele pili lapala yake dorena karo isa ipyamo kando karapu .
42010019	Nakama kaupi popokyalyape meme pyuo yanda pimwal dupwana poral doko nyuo anamanyi nembo karamiŋi lao poral renge doko joo kaelyo kande leya . Dokona mendeme nakama ukiaki minya nara .
42010020	Dokoko doŋo imambu dupwa nakamana pii warombo soo pilyaminyi dokona mona pyakalyuo pyao kara nalapape . Nakamana kingi yake panda dokona pyasi palamo dokona mona pyakalyuo pyao karalapape , leya .
42010021	Yuu gii dokopa Imambu Poo Pyasi Yesu keta paleyamosa mona pyakalyuo pyao karo dopa leya . Rakane yake pandape isa pandape dolapona Kamongo karene doko , embame wambu singi dupwame see nana lao pii dusipa yalu pisala wane nyaŋa dupwa pano lamaipi dokona nambame emba ange leto . Kinyi Rakane , emba range rae maipala pinya lao suu pyapala pipilyamo .
42010022	Rakane dokome peparae dupwa namba keta sinya lao jiya . Dokona suu pyao wambu mendeme Ikinyingi doko apiyakalende karamo lao see nalyaminyi . Rakane baa iki soo karamo . Dee isa wambu mendeme Rakane baa apiyakalende karamo lao see nalyaminyiko . Ikinyingi baa iki sepala wambu baa suu pyaramuli pyuo polo lamairamo dupwa opetae silyaminyi leya .
42010023	Lapala disaepole dupwa peteyami dokona kapu kyepala nakama iki siyaminyipa dopa lamaiya . Nakamame yulu dusipa emboneme kandamilyamo .
42010024	Dokona lao nakama dopa langilyu , Anatunya poropeta akalipi kiŋi akaii malu dupwapeme nakama kandelyaminyi doko kandamwali yaka lao suu piyami doko kanda nayami . Pii nakama simi doko simwaii yaka lao suu piyaminyipape see nayami leya .
42010025	Dokopa Mawa Pii soo gisingi akaii mendeme roya karapala baa makande pyuo dopa leya . Mana Lenge , namba apa pyuo kyakana renge palu palenge doko nyerose ? leya .
42010026	Dokopa Yesumi baa kando dopa lamaiya . Buku Baepole pyasi palamo dupwa apa letase ? Emba kandee dupwa apa lao polo langilisi ? leya .
42010027	Dokopa baame isingi lamaiyuo , Kamongo doko embena Anatuŋu doko mona reto dokopa embena mona dokope imambu dokope pupi lao yulu pingi poral dokope suu pingi dokope dusipa peparae baa maiyare . 42010028	Dopa leyamo dokopa Yesumi isingi dopa lamaiya . Emba rolae lalyane . Dopa pyuo karare ramo doko lete karalu karare leya .
42010029	Lowana mana lenge baame Yesunya pii sepala range elyape lapuli lao suu pyapala lao , Nambana maki palyuo penge dupwa apimoo lyasilisi ? leya .
42010030	Dokopa Yesumi dopa isingi lao , Akali mende Jerusaleme karo lambuo pao Jereko panya peya . Peyamo dokopa akali kendepo nenge lapome baa nyepala komau rokwanyi nembo pyao reteyami . Baa repeta kumara ingiyamo dokopa yaki nyuo peyami .
42010031	Peyaminyipa purisi akali mende kata dokona lambuo peyapya . Pao akali siyamo doko kandapala pakiki palyama peya .
42010032	Peyamopa Lipae akali mendeme epo kandapala dopako pyuo pakiki palyama kanjakalo peyako .
42010033	Pakiki palyama peyamopape Samaria akali mendeme kata epo baa siyamo mare dokona epeya . Epo kandapala baa kondaya .
42010034	Kondapala baa siyamo dokona papala piyami dupwa mamba welepe waene ipwangepe kulimbwapala komau dokome yama pyakamiya . Pyakamipala banya mena ose mata dokona minyalyuo nyuo retapale lanyuo pao upuuili wambu palima papingi anda dokona retapala baa isaru pyuo kareya .
42010035	Dokona yangama dokopa baame kana lama nyepala upuuili wambu palima papingi anda range akali maipala dopa leya . Embame baa isaru pyuo karakape . Pyuo kararene dokopa kana lapo isa paramo doko nambame dee kamba laeyo epapala emba ropo pyaro leya .
42010036	Akali kendepo nenge dupwame nyuo piyaminyi akali doko akali rema dusipana mendali apimi baa maki palenge ingilyase ? Apa lao suu pilipi ? leya .
42010037	Dokopa baame lao , Akali baa kondapala nyisiyamo dokoko , leya . Dokopa Yesumi baa dopa lamaiya . Emba papala baame piyamuli pyuo pyuo karape leya .
42010038	Yesu banya disaepole dupwa pipa kata pao taone mendena sukusa peyaminyipa enda mende kingi Mata lenge dokome banya anda dokona baa yako lao nyiya .
42010039	Banya kakingi mende kingi Maria lenge peteya . Dokome Kamongo dokona kimbu siyamo dokona pisipala banya mana pii soo peteya .
42010040	Soo peteyamopa Mata baame nenge kiso isaru pyuo kareyamopa yulu malu palipala baa minyuo lyakalyaka paeyasa saka naya . 42010041	Dopa leyamo dokopa Kamongo dokome baa isingi lamaiyuo , Mata , Mata , bange malu dupwana suu pyao emba lyakalyaka papipyamosa mona yanyi pyapyamo karene .
42010042	Dokona yulu mendaki pipingele leya . Maria baame yulu rolae mendaki kando nyilyamo dokona kaena lao laa naro leya Yesumi .
42011001	Yuu mendepa Yesu yuu mendasa ateŋa lao peteya . Lao otapeyamo dokopa banya disaepole mende baa piso soo , Kamongo Joneme banya disaepole dupwa ateŋa lenge dokona mana lamaiyamo doko suu pyao embame namwa mana langipi leya .
42011002	Dokopa baame nakama dopa lamaiya . Nakama ateŋa lalana dokopa dopa lao lalapape . Rakane , embena kingi doko poo pyasi ingyuo palenale . Embena isingi yulu doko epo palenale .
42011003	Yuu peparae namwa nenge napengele dupwa joo karape .
42011004	Wambu namwa kando koo pyakange dupwa namwa nyuo kame sakamipala kaenge doko suu pyao namwame koo pyakao karenge dupwa embame nyuo kame sakao karape . Embame namwa makande pirali dupwana lanyuo paa napipi .
42011005	Lapala Yesumi nakama dopa lamaiya . Nakama petaminyi dokona mendeme kukwa andasukulya dokopa nakamana puu minyingi dokona anda dokona papala baa dopa lamamiyuo , Yangone , borete rema jelase .
42011006	Nambana puu minyingi mende kata papyuo ipyamo dokome nenge daapyasa saka nalyo larami ramo dokopa baame andakare palyuo isingi lao , Embame angalyi pyuo laa napipi . Kambu upi laro karamo . Nambana wane wanakepe dupwa role pyao luu palamano . Namba sipurapala bange mende emba kapa jii naro laramo dokopa apa pirami ?
42011007	
42011008	Dokona ingyuo pii mende langilyu , Baa embena puu minyingi dokome sipurapala jii nara ramo doko emba elya nao piso sepa sepa pyuo kararene dokona lao sipurapala kapa jera ingilyamo .
42011009	Dokona suu pyao dopa langilyu , Piso selapape . Dokopa nakama jera . Kotarami dokopa kando nyerami . Kambu dowa dokona kapa kapa pipwape . Dokome kambu lumbwakara .
42011010	Piso serami dupwa peparaeme kapa nyerami . Kotarami dupwame kando nyerami . Kambu dowa dokona kapa kapa pirami dupwana lao kambu lumbwakamira .
42011011	Nakama wane mandenge dupwame ikinyingimi oma mende jinya lara ramo dokopa oma kaepala mee kau koo mairamipi ?
42011012	Panda kola kapa jinya lara ramo dokopa kau popokyalya mairamipi ?
42011013	Dokona suu pyao nakama koo ingyuo petaminyi dupwame nakamana wane wanakepe dupwa bange keyange malngi doko suu pyao Rakane yake panda dokona keyange wakasa karamo dokome wambu Imambu Poo Pyasi jinya lao piso serami dupwa eŋa nembapala mal narase ? leya .
42011014	Baame yuu mendepa imambu koo pii laa nange mende raka lanyi nembo kareya . Imambu koo doko yaki nyuo peyamo dokopa akali pii laa nange dokome pii leyasa wambu dupwame ayaka lao mona nembeyami .
42011015	Mona nembeyaminyipape nakama kareyami dupwana lapome dopa leyami . Belesapulu imambu koo dupwana kamongo dokome baa minyapyamo dokome imambu koo dupwa raka lanyi nembo karamo leyami .
42011016	Dopa lao kareyaminyi dokopa lapome Yesu baa makande pyuo , Yake panda dokona yulu renge palenge mende namwa pyuo lasaka pipili yaka leyami .
42011017	Dopa leyaminyipape baame nakama suu pyao kareyami doko soo gisapala dopa lamaiya . Rara mendakindeme liti pipala yango sukusa yanda pirami ramo doko rara doko walya lao otarasa pira . Dee akalyanda liti mendeme paka lakyuo yango palyuo pira ramo doko walya lao isa para .
42011018	Dokona suu pyao Sataneme baa range paka lakyuo karara ramo doko banya isingi yulu doko apa pyuo palu palyuo parase ? Dokona lao nakamame namba kando , Belesapulumi nyisapyamopa imambu koo dupwa raka lanyi nembo karene , letaminyi .
42011019	Belesapulu namba nyisapyamosa imambu koo dupwa raka lanyi nembo kararo ramo doko nakamana wambu dupwa apimi nyisilyamopa imambu koo dupwa raka lanyi nembo karengese ? Dokona suu pyao pii lalaminyi kandapi doko kinyi panda kyambo lao nakamana wambu dupwa kando makande pyuo selapape .
42011020	Doko Anatunya poralnya renge dokome minyapyamopa nambame imambu koo dupwa raka lanyi nembo karenge dokona Anatunya isingi yulu doko nakama keta ipyasa pilyamo .
42011021	Akali poral mendeme yanda walakape minyuo banya anda rapu pyuo karara dokopa banya bange keyange dupwa kapa mee sera .
42011022	Kapa seramopape akali kama porai mendeme epo baa pyao isa palyapala dokopa banya yanda kaku konambepe retaro kararamo dupwa nyepala banya pinjale bange nyuo wambu yango mokwa soo maira .
42011023	Mendeme nambana nyiso piso karo pii nara ramo doko nambapa sisu nyuo kararasa pira . Mendeme nambapa role pyao kara napala wambu sukusa nyuo kara nara ramo doko baa wambu bolombalo lao pena lao kararasa pira .
42011024	Imambu koo mende akali mende yaki nyuo papala dokopa yuu lapo ipwa epa nange dupwana anja paliru lao koto papira . Papyuo panda kando nyii napala , Nambana anda yaki nyepala ipu dokona kapu kyuo dee parole lara .
42011025	Lapala epo anda doko burumi manjisi bange dupwa rolae soo piramo kandara .
42011026	Dokopa papala imambu yanda ipingi nyero baa dopale daa , ama koo wakasa dusipa lanyuo dokona kolando pao palirami . Dokopa akali doko wambo koo ingyuo kareyamo dopale ingyuo kara nara , enakana ama koo wakasa ingyuo karara leya .
42011027	Pii dopa lao kareyamo dokopa enda mende wambu rukuraka pyuo peteyami dokona sukusa peteyandeme pii ketae palyuo lao dopa leya . Endame emba manjo nyuo anju joo peteyamo dokona elyape keta pisamo leya .
42011028	Leyamopape baa dopa lamaiya . Pii letene doko rolae daa . Wambu Anatunya pii warombo soo pisipala pyuo karaminyi dupwa keta renge keyange palamo leya .
42011029	Wambu malu rukuraka pyuo peteyami dokona lapo kondo konda pyuo epo buu minyiyami dokopa baame dopa lamaiya . Wambu epapu karaminyi dupwa koo ingyuo karaminyi . Namba kando Anatunya yulu pilipi lao wambumi pii nange yulu mende pii lao makande pyuo letaminyi . Doko pii naronopape Jonana yulu piyamo dokona mana nyelapape .
42011030	Anatumi Jona keta kongwalu piyamopa Ninepa wambu dupwa mana nyiyami doko suu pyao wambu epapu isa ando karaminyi dupwa namba Ikinyingi Akali keta Anatu mende piramo soo nyerami .
42011031	Kote pii andake paliramo yuu gii dokopa Kuini donorena range baame wambu epapu isa ando karaminyi dupwa kando isipyara ingilyamo . Kuiui enda doko banya yuu range nanesa doko yaki nyepala yuu kipwa kipwa dupwana kata londeta epo Solomena pii keyange doko sela epeya . Epapu mendeme Solomonepa manda manji napyamo doko kamame wakasa ingilyamo doko dae kata kande .
42011032	Kote pii andake paliramo gii dokopa Ninepa akali dupwame sipurapala dae wambu dupwa kando koo piyami lao kote larami ingilyamo . Dokona lao Joname boo pyao lao kareyamo dokopa Ninepa wambu dupwame banya pii sepala mona enenge palyuo kareyami . Doko mende Jona dokona suu pyao kamame wakasa ingilyamo doko dae kata kande leya .
42011033	Mendeme lambe kalpala anda isarena iminjingi panda dokona reta naope dee penge dokome nee pyuo pisa naope pingi . Dopa pyuo yalu pii napala rate dokona ketae retenge dokopa wambu andakare eparami dupwame isare doko kapa kando epenale lao pingi .
42011034	Embena lenge doko rangena yongona lambe dopale rao karamo . Dokona embena lenge doko mondo lao rao karara ramo doko yongo peparae yangaramopa piso karo piri . Lenge doko kwaeyara ramo doko yanenge peparae iminjaramopa karare .
42011035	Dokona yangapyamo karene doko monarena iminja nana lao waso karape .
42011036	Embena yongo peparae yanga paupau laramopa dokome kuki lamape iminja nara ramo doko lambe keyange rao dokopa yanenge peparaena yanganyi peenge dopale ingyuo paresa pira leya .
42011037	Yesu pii lao kareyamo dokopa Parisi akali mendeme baa nenge role pyao nambanale epena leya . Leyamopa andakare pao peteyambi .
42011038	Parisi akali dokome Yesu nenge nalana dokopa kingi wate pii napyalyamo lao kandapala mona nembeya .
42011039	Dokopa Kamongo dokome baa dopa lamaiya . Nakama Parisi dupwame kapope disipi dupwa netarename iki wate pingi . Nakamana monarename panga soope waa nyingipi yulu koo pingipi dupwa palyuo simbulyamo .
42011040	Nakama kopyali karaminyi . Nakamana yanenge pyuo wasiyamo dokome mona doko opetae wasa nayase ?
42011041	Dokona ingyuo monana koko palenge dupwa wambu dupwa maiyuo karalapape . Dopa pirami ramo dokopa bange peparae elyape sakara lyakande .
42011042	Parisi dupwa nakama randa narami ingilyamo . Dokona lao mokwame yokope kyalya yokope nenge nenge yoko wakale wakale dupwa peparaena akalisa silyamo dokona mendaki larapu Anatu pingyu malngi . Mailyaminyi doŋo yulu rolaepe Anatu mona retengepe kaelyaminyi . Yulu doloma kae napala yulu keyange doko opetae pyuo kararaminde pimi .
42011043	Parisi akali dupwa nakama randa narami ingilyamo . Dokona lao sinakoke anda dupwana isa petenge mupwa dupwana pisimwali yaka lao suu pyao karaminyi . Nenge ropo pingi kamapi dupwana karo wambu dupwame nakama yako lamili lao suu pyao karaminyi .
42011044	Nakama randa narami ingilyamo . Dokona lao yanyanda nee pyuo silyamopa akali lapome yanyandalyamo lao suu pyao nao kamenge ketae dokona kata penge nakama Parisi dupwa dopale ingilyamo leya .
42011045	Mawa Pii singi akali dokona mendeme baa dopa lao lamaiya . Mana Lenge , embame dopa lalene doko namwa opetae lao nembapisa pipya leya .
42011046	Leyamo Yesumi , Mawa Pii singi akali dupwa nakama opetae randa narami ingilyamoko . Akali bange kenda malminyi randa nao soo puminyipape nakamame kingi pambu dokomepe nyiso minya nalyaminyi .
42011047	Nakama randa narami ingilyamo . Dokona lao nakamana rakange kyawa dupwame Anatunya pyongo piyamopa nolako lao kareyami akali dupwa nyuo pyao kumakayami dupwana malu anda nakamame mondo lao pyakamingi .
42011048	Rakange kyawa dupwame pyao kumakayaminyipa nakamana malu anda mondo pilyaminyi dokome nakamana rakange kyawa dupwame kopetame pyuo kareyami doko lyakal pilyamo .
42011049	Dokona lao Anatunya pii rolae dopa leya . Nambame poropeta akali lapope aposele akali lapope nakama kararaminyi dokona pena lakamironopa nakama dokona lapo pyao kumakao randa maiyuo pyuo kararami .
42011050	Dokona isa panda wasiyamo gii dokona piso epo poropeta akali dupwa peparaena ranjama kulimbwapa piyami dokona epapu isa ando karaminyi dupwa keta kote pii palira .
42011051	Akali Epolo piyamo dokona piso epo kama enakana Sakarayame Anatu bange kiso maingi rara singi pakirena tembole anda angi singi kanya dokona piyaminyipa kumuya dokona ranjama dupwa peparaena epapu isa ando karaminyi dupwa keta kote sera lao nakama kinyi langilyu .
42011052	Nakama Mawa Pii singi akali dupwa randa epara ingilyamo . Singinya renge anda dokona kii ikyane doko retaro karaminyi . Nakama kolando paa napala wambu kolando panya lao kareyami dupwa kaena lao daa lao kareyami , leya .
42011053	Yesu baa yuu doko yaki nyuo panya piyamo dokopa Mawa Pii mana lenge akali dupwape Parisi dupwapeme baa piso sokondali pyuo pii malu lapyali lao angalye piyami .
42011054	Baa pii koo kote laramali mende larape lao lyakaro iso kareyami .
42012001	Dopa pyuo kareyaminyi dokopa wambu ama malu wakasa paka pyuo karapala wambu yango dupwa kete pyao kalyuo kareyaminyipa baame banya disaepole dupwa kanda soo lao dopa lamaiya . Parisinya isi doko waso karalapape . Nakamana pii lama lao yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge yulu dopalesa leto .
42012002	Dakepa nee pyuo silyamo dupwa peparae panara . Yalu piyami dupwa peparae kando nyerami .
42012003	Kukwama pii yalu pyuo wato larami dupwa korakama dokopa wal nembo larami . Panda dongena pii iso laminyi dupwa peparae andeyangi ketae dokona karo porakalyuo kaeyo lao boo pyao larami .
42012004	Nambana puu minyingi dupwa selapape . Wambu yongo pyao kumakapala dokopa imambu kokwa selana saka nange dupwa kando paka nalapape .
42012005	Mende kando pakarami dokoŋo lao nakama repe repe langyuo leto . Doko Anatumi pyao kumakapala koo panda dokona kapa nembara doko kando pako karalapape . Kinyi langilyu , Anatu baa kando pakalapape .
42012006	Yaka pimbinangae kingi paki dusipa kumasi kana lamame iki ropo pyao nyii nangese ? Dopa pilyaminyipape Anatumi yaka dokona mendepe kame see nange .
42012007	Anatu baame nakamana kyawasi malu dokona yaka lao otasi karamo dokona nakama pako kara nalapape . Anatumi nakama rungi mngi pyao karapyasa yaka pimbinangae ama malu dupwa pipa nakamapa kapa ingya nalyamo doko see nalyamisi ?
42012008	Dee dopa langilyu , wambu peparaeme isa wambu yango dupwana lenge kambu dokona nambana lao polo larami ramo doko lkinyingi Akali dokome nakamana lao Anatunya aŋala dupwana lenge kambu dokona polo larako .
42012009	Laramopape mendeme isa akali dupwana lenge kambu dokona pako karo namba mata joo nambana kingi laa narami ramo doko Akalinya Ikinyingimi Anatunya aŋala dupwana lenge kambu dokona baa mata maiyuo banya kingi laa narako .
42012010	Mendeme Ikinyingi Akali kando kokwa soo laramo doko Anatumi doko kapa nyuo kame sakamira . Sakamiramopape mendeme Imambu Poo Pyasi kando kokwa soo pii mende lara ramo dokopa kame sakami nara .
42012011	Nakama sinakoke anda dokonape kote singi akalinya lenge kambu dokonape dee mupwa dupwana lenge kambu dokonape lanyuo peyami kande dokopa apa pyuo isingi laro laope aki pii lamairo laope mona yanyi pyaramopa kara nalapape .
42012012	Gii dokopa Imambu Poo Pyasimi pii lapengele ingyaramo dupwa emba mana langiramopa lao karare .
42012013	Dokopa Yesu baa role pyao kareyami dupwana mendeme baa lamaiyuo dopa leya . Mana lenge rakane kumapyasa nambana yangonge dokome moyange bange dupwana lapo namba mokwa soo jinya lamaiyapili lao langilyu leya .
42012014	Dokopa baa isingi dopa lamaiya . Yangone , apimi namba rombo palyuo embena kote pii lao rolapala moyange dupwa mokwa soo nakamba jereŋe lapyase ?
42012015	Lapala nakama lamaiya . Bange malu nyuowane lao suu pingi , doko waso karalapape . Isa bange malu nyepala kamongo penge dokona renge kulisa mende pali nalyamo leya .
42012016	Lapala baame kongwalu pii mende nakama lamaiyuo leya . Yuu mendepa akali bange ama malu singi mendeme banya yuu dokona ee nengepe malu siya .
42012017	Siyamopa baa rangeme retarono panda doko see nalyamo dokona aki mende pirose lao suu piya .
42012018	Dokopa monarename baa range dopa lao suu piya . Nambana nengena anda dupwa kete pilyamo dokona lalyapala kamame reeko lapo piru . Elya pipala dokopa nambana nengepe bange dupwape kapa sera .
42012019	Ama embone petamo . Bange malu dupwame ee kana malu mee sera . Dokona ingyuo namba mee male male lao karo nenge ipwangepe nao rae maiyuo kararo ingilyamo .
42012020	Dopa lao suu piyamopape Anatumi baa dopa lamaiya . Emba kopyali , kukwa dakepa embena imambu rekya lao para ingilyamo . Paramopa bange dupwa rapa rapa pyuo retapi dupwa apinya ingyarase ?
42012021	Dokona ingyuo akali mendeme bange malu reto rungi rungi pyuo karapala Anatu kando mona reta nara dopale ingyara leya .
42012022	Lapala banya disaepole dupwa dopa lamaiya . Renge dokona lao , aki nenge napala kapa kararo laope yanenge dokona aki komau pee piro laope suu pyao mona yanyi pyaramo kara nalapape .
42012023	Dokona lao nenge dokome iki wambu kapa ingyarase ? Yongo doko komau wapusi dokome elyape keta parase ? Pii mende daase ?
42012024	Yaka simbalrapinyi dupwa suu pyalapape . Dupwame ee wara pipala jingi lyii nange , bange retenge andape nenge retenge andape pipala kara nangeko . Anatumi nenge maiyuo karenge kandale . Dokona ingyuo yaka dupwa andake ingyapala nakama mee kuki ingyuo kandelyande daa .
42012025	Nakama walya lao kuma namwali yaka lao suu pyao mona yanyi pyaramopa kararami ramo dokome ee kana mendasipa opetae lete kararamisi ?
42012026	Nakama yulu dopale kapa pii narami ingilyamo dokona akipamo doloma suu pyao mona yanyi pyapyamopa karaminyi ?
42012027	Isa jingipi isoko dupwanape apa pyuo andenge doko suu pyalapape . Dupwame yulu pii nao , puu wale pyaa nao ando karenge . Dopa pyuo karelyaminyipa Solomone baa ama neta rao au piyamopape isa jingi dupwa kama wakasa rao kuikui lao au pingi .
42012028	Dokona suu pyao isoko epapu keyange andelyamo dupwa rakya dokopa nyuo isare dokona kisingi doko Anatumi au pyuo kandalapape lao yanenge keyange malngi doko suu pyao nakama dopako pyuo komau wapwaka narase ? Nakama Anatu kapa pirape lao suu pingi lama manjo karaminyi .
42012029	Dokona suu pyao aki nengepe waene ipwangepe naro lao koto papyuo mona yanyi pyaramopa kara nalapape .
42012030	( Dokona lao wambu Anatu suu pyaa nange yuu mure lao karaminyi dupwame bange dopale iki koto karenge . ) Koto karaminyipa nakamana Rakane dokome nakama nenge naa napala nano kararami doko silyamo .
42012031	Bange dupwa koto karaminyi doko kaepala banya isingi yulu doko kando nyimwali lao koto karalapape . Dokopa baame bange dupwa opetae nakama jera .
42012032	Nakama nambana mena mondo ingyuo karaminyi dokona paka nalapape . Rakane dokome banya isingi yulu doko rae maiyuo jera .
42012033	Nakamana bange retenge dupwame ropo pyao kana nyepala wambu mende aeya napyamo karaminyi dupwa mokwa soo maipwape . Pakeya momo naa nara mende koto nyelapape . Nakamana bange kulisa yake panda dokona reto karalapape . Panda keyange dokona seramo dokopa lisiwame dupwame naa naope waa nyingi akali dupwame anda doko lalyapala waa nyii naoko pirami .
42012034	Embena bange silyamo mare dokonako embena mona doko pao yukwaro kararasa pira .
42012035	Nakama komau wapwaro karo nakamana lambe kisapala minyuo karalapape .
42012036	Kendemande wambu dupwame nakamana kamongo baa enda nyilyaminyi dokona nenge andake napala anda epelyape lao isaro kareyami dokona mende makande pyuo leto . Doko baa epo kambu dokona kapa kapa pilyamopa walya lao kambu lumbungi doko suu pyao nakama dopako pyuo rapa rapa pyuo karalapape .
42012037	Kamongo epapala kendemande wambu lenge rao pisiraminyi kandaramopa nakama keta renge keyange maira . Kinyi langilyu , baame komau wapupala nakama taepo dokona petena lapala nakama nenge maira .
42012038	Andasukulya panda yangalana piramopape nakama mee dopako pyuo isaro pisiraminyi epapala kandara ramo akali kamongo doko kendemande dupwa kando rae maira .
42012039	Pii dake kame see nalapape . Anda range akali doko waa nyingi akali yuu gii anjokorape epara lao soo gisapyali doko lenge rao pisipala anda pyasu pyao epa nana lapyali .
42012040	Ikinyingi Akali doko nakama kamenge kararami dokopa eparaŋa dokona rapa rapa pipala karalapape leya .
42012041	Pitame lao , Kamongo , kongwalu pii doko namwasa letepe panda wambu dupwa peparaesa letepe ? leya .
42012042	Dokopa Kamongo dokome dopa leya . Kendemande akali apiyakalende mupwa ingyuo parase ? Doko akali mende mona palenge dokome yulu kaeya nao pyuo kararamopa banya kamongo dokome baa yapo nyepala doloma rapu pyuo nenge mokwa soo maipa pyuo karena lara doko .
42012043	Kamongo dee kapu kyuo epo kendemande akali yulu rolae pyuo kararamo kandaramo dokopa kendemande akali doko baa rae maiyuo para .
42012044	Kinyi langilyu , kamongo baame banya bange peparae rapu pyuo karena lao rombo palyara .
42012045	Dopa piramopape yulu pingi akali baa kopyali ingyapala , Nambana kamongo walya lao epa nalyamo lao suu pyapala yulu pingi enda akalipi yango pyarako pyao baamoo wambu yango role pyao nenge nao waene ipwange malu nao pipala kyawa sisingi bolombalo laramo pisirami .
42012046	Dopa pyuo piso kamongo doko walya lao epa nara lao suu pyao kamenge pisiramo yuu gii dokopa banya kamongo epara . Epapala baa pyakepanyi nembo kaepala wambu yanengena mamba kiso lao kararami dupwa koo keta kararami dokonako pyambwara .
42012047	Dokona suu pyao kendemande akali mendeme banya kamongome yulu dopalende pipilinya suu pyalyamo lao sepala pinya wangu laka nara ramo doko banya kamongo dokome baa poralyuowale pyara ingilyamo .
42012048	Dopa piraminyipape kendemande akali mendeme kamenge karo koo mende pira ramo doko banya kamongo akali kuki pyuo pyaroko pyara . Namwa keta yulu paliramuli pyuo pirama . Dokona suu pyao yulu andake mende namwa kete paliramo dokopa yulu andake pirama . Dee yulu kama andake palira ramo doko namwa yulu kama andakeoko pirama ingilyamo .
42012049	Isa yuu dakena isare pyao pyale lala epeyo doko epapu anji nyepapyali yaka lao suu pilyu .
42012050	Namba bapitisimo mende nyero ingilyamo doko pyaka sepapyali yaka lao monarena reke lao karalu karapyamopa karo .
42012051	Namba isa yuu dakena nakama kui lao karalapa lao epelyamo lao suu pilyamisi ? Doko daa lyakande . Liti pyuo kararami lao epeyo .
42012052	Dokona suu pyao anda mendaki dokona wambu kingi paki palirami dupwa paka lakyuo lamame rema dusipa kando yango palyuo kararami . Dee rema dusipame lama dolapo kando sisi nyuo kararamioko .
42012053	Nakama sisi nyuo karo rakange dokome ikinyingipa sisi nyerambinyi , wanenge dokome endangipa sisi nyerambi . Akali mendena endangipa ayangepa sisi nyerambi , akalinya etenge dokome banya ayangepa sisi nyerambioko leya .
42012054	Wambu malu mee kareyami dupwa kando pii mende konda pyuo lamaiya . Doko neta anda penge kata dorena kopa mende silyamo doko kandapala apunda eparalyamo lao suu pingi . Apu dokona rae doko epenge kandale .
42012055	Donorena piso raiya minyuo epelyamo kandapala isasa piralyamo lenge . Dokopa dopa pingi .
42012056	Nakama panga soo yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge dupwa kando mende leto . Isa pandape yakerenamepe mende rengya piralyamo lao panapyamo dokona renge doko kapa kando silyaminyi . Silyaminyipape yuu gii dakepale yulu andake mende piralyamo doko akipamo sepa nalyamipi ?
42012057	Dee , anjuku yulu rolae lao pakana palyuo range suu pyaa nalyamipi ?

43005018	Leyamopa baa koro petengena mawa pii doko kokwa siyamo dokona iki baa pyamwali lao suu pyao kareyaminde daa . Baa Anatu doko nambana Rakange leyamo dokopa baapa Anatupa mendarele leyasa piya dokona baa ama pyama lao , lao suu pyao kareyami .
43005019	Yesumi nakama dopa lamaiya . Kinyi kinyi langilyu , Ikinyingi baame yeelyo sisu lao mende pii nange . Rakangeme pyuo karenge kandelyamo yulu doko iki kapa pingi . Dokonako ingyuo Rakange pilyamuli pyuo Ikinyingi dokome pyuoko karenge .
43005020	Dokona lao Rakange baame Ikinyingi doko mona reto karapala baame pyuo karenge yulu dupwa peparae lasaka pingi . Enakana dokopa yulu kamame wakasa dupwa iasaka pyuo kararamopa nakama kando yamarangyuo parami .
43005021	Dokona suu pyao Rakange dokome wambu kumuo palenge dupwa lete minyalyuo nyingi doko suu pyao Ikinyingi opetaeme lapo letena renge malru lao suu pilyamuli pyuo malngi .
43005022	Rakange baame akali mende kando yapalya yapana pyuo laa nange . Baame wambu yapalya yapana pyuo lenge yulu doko Ikinyingi maiya .
43005023	Wambu peparaeme Rakange kando ketae pyambuo karaminyi dopako pyuo Ikinyingi ketae pyambuo karena lao maiya . Mendeme Ikinyingi kando ketae pyambuo kara narami dupwame Rakange mapanyi peeyamo doko ketae pyambuo kara naramisa pira .
43005024	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , mendeme nambana pii soo nyepala namba mapanyi peeyamo doko kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karaminyi dupwa keta kyakana renge kulisa doko palira . Kumungi renge doko yalo epo lete renge dokona karamo dokona baa keta kote pali nara ingilyamo .
43005025	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , yuu gii mende pyaka sera doko pyaka soo kaepyamopa wambu kumuo palaminyi dupwa Anatunya Ikinyingi pii laramo doko sepala lete parami .
43005026	Rakange letena renge renge kuiyuo karamuli pyuo Ikinyingi keta pyamaiyiya .
43005027	Baa Ikinyingi Akali ingilyamo dokona lao kote kapa lara inginyi pyambuya .
43005028	Pii dake sepala mona nemba nalapape . Yuu gii mende pyaka seramo dokopa wambu malu anda palaminyi dupwa peparae banya kambu dokona pii neta eparamo doko sepala lopo neta eparami . Wambu yulu keyange pingi dupwa lete karalu karalana lopo epo , wambu koo pingi dupwa kwao parami dokona lao lopo eparami .

43005030	Namba range sipurapala mende pii nange . Anatu baa namba langinginyili pyuo pakana palyuo kote lao rolenge dokome rolae ingyuo penge . Namba range suu pyao mende pii napala namba mapanyi peeyamo dokona pii sepala pinya lao suu pyao karo .
43005031	Namba rangesa lao laro ramo nambana pii doko bulumbulu mee pyara .
43005032	Mendalimi nambasa lao lao karenge doko banya pii doko pii kinyi lao soo gisilyu .
43005033	Jone kareyamo dokona lapo piso sela pena leyaminyipa baame pii kinyi dokona rolo leya .
43005034	Rolo leyamopape isa akalimi namba nyiso pii mende lamilinya suu pyaa nalyo . Pii doko nakama lete wal pyao paramiŋi lao karo .

43005036	Dopa piyamopa nambame pii lao karenge dokome Jonena pii doko anale palamo . Dokona lao Rakange dokome yulu pyuo lumwa pipi lao jiyamo nambame pyuo karo dupwameko Rakange dokona namba mapanyi peeyaŋa lao lasaka pilyamo .

43005040	Yaka letaminyipape letena renge doko karo namba piso sela epa nalyaminyi .
43005041	Isa akali dupwame namba lakandamili yaka lao suu pyao kara nalyo .

43007028	Dopa leyami dokopa Yesu tembole anda dokona mana lao karo dokopa pii ketae palyuo dopa leya . Nakamame namba kando anja karo epee lao soo gisilyamisi ? Dopa pyaaminyiko doŋo nambame sisu lao epeyonde daa . Namba mapanyi peeyapala angingyuo karamo doko nakamame kando see nalyaminyi .
43007029	Baame namba mapanyi peeyamo dokona karo epeyo dokome nambame baa kandenge leya .
43007030	Dokopa nakamame baa puu maiyalana suu pyao lao kareyaminyipa banya yuu gii doko ene pyaka sepa nayamo dokome wambu mendeme baa minyara nayami .
43007031	Minyara nayaminyipa wambu malu meeme baa angiŋi lao suu piyami . Akali dake yulu andake malu lasaka pyuo karamo doko Koraisa eparamo dokopa yulu kamame wakasa lasaka pyuo kararase ? leyami .
43007032	Wambu malu mee pii dopale yalu pyuo lao kareyaminyi doko sepala Parisi akali dupwame purisi akali mupwape nakamana yanda singi lapo Yesu puu maipala nyela pena leyami .
43007033	Dokopa Yesu dopa leya . Yuu mendasipa iki dee nakama pipya kararama . Karapala namba mapanyi peeyamo karamo dokona paro .
43007034	Nakamame namba koto karapala kando nyii narami . Namba kararo dokona nakama epana saka narami leya .
43007035	Juu wambu dupwa yango sukusa dopa leyami . Namwame baa kando nyii narami lao anja paro lao suu pyao letase ? Yuu kipwa kipwa Giriki wambu karenge dupwana Juu wambu lapo bolombalo lao papala karaminyi dupwana pao Giriki wambu dupwa mana lamairu lao panya karape ?
43007036	Baame , Namba kotapala kando nyii narami lapala kararo dokona epana saka narami , lalamoko kandapi doko aki rengendena lalape ? leyami .
43007037	Nenge nao kareyami yuu dusipana lumwa pingi yuu gii wakasa dokopa Yesu sipurapala pii ketae palyuo dopa leya . Wambu mendeme ipwa nano pyuo karara ramo doko namba karo dokona ipupwape .
43007038	Mendeme namba kapa ingingi lao suu pyaramo doko pii pyasi palengenyili pyuo banya monarena kyakana renge palenge ipwa guu lao pyasumakao karara leya .
43007039	Dopa lao wambu baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao kareyami dupwame Imambu ene nyerami dokonako palyuo kongwalu pii leya . Anatumi Yesu ene yanga paupau lanyi pyambwapa nayamosa Imambu doko maipa naya .
43007040	Pii leyamo doko sepala wambu lapome , Akali dake Anatunya pii nolako lenge akali angi ingilyamo leyami .
43007041	Lapome , Dake Koraisalamo leyami . Leyaminyipa lapome , Koraisa baa yuu Galili rae epara ingilyase ?
43007042	Koraisa Dapitinya para pyasi ingyuo yuu Beteleme taone Dapiti paleya dokona rae epara ingilyamo lao pii pyasi dokona pali nalyase ? leyami .
43007043	Mee wambu dupwa dopa lao baa kando wakale wakale suu pyao kareyami .
43007044	Lapome baa puu maimwali yaka lao suu pyao kareyaminyipa mendeme baa minyara nayami .
43007045	Yanda singi dupwa purisi mupwa Parisi dupwape kareyami dokona laeyo epeyaminyipa nakamame , Akipamo baa lanyuo epa nalamisi ? lamaiyami .
43007046	Yanda singi dupwame isingi lao , Baa letamo akali mendeme dopakale ingyuo laa nange leyami .
43007047	Parisi akali dupwame nakama lamaiyuo , Nakama opetaeko kyambo langalase ?
43007048	Akali angi dupwape Parisi akali dupwape karaminyi dokona mendeme baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karamisi ?
43007049	Doko wambu nakama lyingi lyangi kuiyuo karaminyi dupwame Mawa Pii see nao karaminyi dokome nakama keta koo palira ingilyamo leyami .
43007050	Leyaminyipape nakama dokona akali mende Nikotimasa lenge baa wambo Yesu kandala peya akali dokome sipurapala dopa leya .
43007051	Namwana Mawa Pii palamo dokona , Namwame akali mende koo pipyalyamo lapala mee langa kote laa nange . Dopa pipyalyamo lao piso soo otapala kote lenge .
43007052	Nakamame , Emba opetae Galili rangekose ? leyami . Pii pyasi dupwa poraiyuo mana nyuo kandarenepa Gaiili range poropeta mende sipura nara ingilyamo lao kandare leyami .
43008001	Wambu peparae anda peyaminyi dokopa Yesu yuu Olipi Kyau dokona peya .
43008002	Wamba yangama dokopa tembole anda dokona dee kamba epeya . Wambu peparae baa kareyamo dokona epeyaminyipa baame isa pisipala mana lamaiya .
43008003	Dokopa enda mende akali kepo pyuo palipyamopa kando nyiyami doko Mawa Pii mana lengepe Parisi dupwapeme baa nyepala lanyuo epeyami . Lanyuo epo wambu peteyami dokona enda doko sukusa roya kareyami .
43008004	Dopa pipala Yesu dopa lamaiyami . Mana Lenge , enda dake akali kepo pyuo palipyamopa kando nyelaminyi lyakande .
43008005	Moseseme Mawa Pii pyao reto , Dopale pingi dupwa kaname pyao kumakalapape leya kande . Embame baasa kando apa lare ? leyami .
43008006	Yesu koo mende larape lao kote lamwali yaka lao suu pyapala baa apa letape lao selana makande pyuo leyami . Dokopa Yesu pongwa napala kingi kyawa dokome yuu dokona kiki pyuo peteya .
43008007	Dokopa nakamame baa piso soo lao sulu siyami dokopa baame roya karapala nakama lamaiyuo , Nakama karaminyi dokona mende koo pali naya kande doko wambo sipurapala enda baa kaname pyalase leya .
43008008	Lapala dee kamba pongwa napala yuu dokona kingi kyawa dokome deeyako kiki pyuo peteya .
43008009	Dokopa pii leyamo doko sepala nakama mendaki mendaki lao andapae dupwa wambo peyaminyipa pao karo ote leyami . Dopa piyaminyi dokopa Yesu enda dokopa yeelyo kareyambi .
43008010	Yesu baame kandalyuo kandapala , Enda , wambu lao karalaminyi kandapi dupwa anjukunya kata pamipi ? Nakama mendeme emba kote laa naramipi ? leya .
43008011	Baa , Kamongo lapala , Mendeme laa naramilyamo leya . Dokopa Yesumi lao , Namba opetaeme emba koo pingiŋi laronde daa . Papala deeko kamba koo pyuo pisa napipi leya .
43008012	Yesumi nakama dee mende lamaiyuo dopa leya . Namba isa yuunya yanga paupau lenge renge karoŋo . Mendeme namba paronuli pyuo eparamo doko baa iminjinginya moko palyuo papi napala baa keta letena yanga paupau lenge renge doko palira leya .
43008013	Dokopa Parisi dupwame baa lamaiyuo , Emba rangeme namba dopa pyuondeŋe leene pii doko kinyi daa , leyami .
43008014	Yesumi isingi dopa leya . Namba rangena yulu suu pyao lapunupape nambana pii kinyi ingyuo pelyamo . Namba anja karo epeyo lao anja paro lao soo gisapala lao karo . Soo gisapunupape nakamame namba anja karo epee lao anja pare lao soo walengena palya nalyaminyi .
43008015	Nakamame yanengena ketae kando koo epengepe yapalya yapana pyuo lenge . Namba wambu koo epengepe yapalya yapana pyuo lao kara nalyo .
43008016	Lao kara nalyoŋo doko namba koo epengepe yapalya yapana pyuo lao kararo ramo doko namba iki laa nao karo namba mapanyi peeyamo dokopa laramba dokome rolae laro .
43008017	Nakamana Lowa dokona akali lamame mendakinya palyuo lao kararambi ramo doko pii kinyilyamo lao suu pyarami lao pyasi palamo kande .
43008018	Namba rangeme dopa pyuondeŋe lao karonopa Rakange dokome namba dopa pyuondeŋe lao karengeko leya .
43008019	Dopa leyamo dokopa nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Embena rakane anja karamo ? leyami . Yesumi isingi lao , Namba kando soo rola naminyi doko suu pyao Rakange baa soo rola nalyaminyiko . Namba soo rolamili doko nambana Rakange baa opetae simili , leya .
43008020	Baame tembole anda dokona mana lamaiyuo karo dokopa kana mone retapa pingi anda dokona karo pii dasipa lao kareya . Lao kareyamopape banya yuu gii ene pyaka sepa nayasa mendeme baa puu mal nayami .
43008021	Yesumi dee pii mende lamaiyuo , Namba mendasa paronopa nakamame namba koto karo nakamana koo dupwa paleta kumarami . Namba parono dokona kapa epa narami leya .
43008022	Dokopa Juu wambu dupwame lao , Baa paro dokona kapa epa narama letamo doko rangeme pyapala kumuo parape ? leyami .
43008023	Baame nakama dopa lamaiya . Nakama isa panda rae , namba ketae panda rae , nakama isa yuu dakena range , namba isa yuu dakena rangende daa .
43008024	Nakamame namba Baaŋa lao suu pyaa narami ramo doko yulu koo pyuo karaminyi dopako pyuo karo kuma rami ingilyamo . Dokona lao nakama koo paleta kumarami langyalono kandapi leya .
43008025	Nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Emba apisi ? leyami . Yesumi nakama lamaiya . Wamba kanda soo piso langyuo kareyo kande dokoko .
43008026	Nakamasa lao koo koo lao pii malu laro ingilyamo . Ingyapyamopape namba mapanyi peeyamo doko kinyi angi lao karapyamopa baame namba pii langiyamo siyunuli pyuo isa wambu dupwa polo langyuo karo leya .
43008027	Baame Rakangesa lalyamo lao soo gisa nayami .
43008028	Dokopa Yesu dopa leya . Ikinyingi Akali minyalyuo nyerami dokopa namba Baaŋa lao soo manji nyerami . Namba range sisu lao mende pii nao Rakange dokome mana langiyamuli pyuo lao karee lao soo gisarami .
43008029	Namba mapanyi peeyamo doko nambapa karambano . Yuu peparae nambame baa rae mairali yulu dupwa pingi dokome namba yaki nyii nao karamo leya .
43008030	Dopa lao kareyamo dokopa wambu malumi baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala mona maiyami .
43008031	Dokopa Yesumi Juu wambu baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao kareyami dupwa dopa lamaiya . Nakamame nambana pii kare kare soo soo kararami ramo doko nambana disaepole angingyuo kararamisa pira .
43008032	Dokopa pii angi kinyi doko soo gisaraminyisa pii kinyi dokome nakama kiiramo neta nyera leya .
43008033	Nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Namwa Aporakamena para pyasi ingyuo karamano . Yuu wamba akali mendeme puu maiyamopa kara nayama . Kiiramo neta nyera lalene kandapi doko apa piyandena lalese ? leyami .
43008034	Yesumi isingi dopa lamaiya . Kinyi kinyi langilyu , wambu yulu koo pyuo karenge dupwa peparae koona kendemande ingyuo karaminyi .
43008035	Kendemande akali mendeme mende nyiso karara ramo doko banya ree palu ingyuo puu pao paa nara . lkinyingi dokome angingyuo karalu karara .
43008036	Dokona lkinyingi dokome nakama kiiramo nyera ramo doko nakama kinyi kinyi moko nyisi kararami .
43008037	Nakama Aporakamena para pyasi ingyuo karaminyi doko silyu . Silyuko doŋo nambana pii doko soo nyii nalyaminyi dokona nakamame namba apa pyuo pyamane lao karaminyi .
43008038	Nambana Rakangena lenge kambu dokona kandeyonuli pyuo lao karo , nakamame nakamana rakange langilyamo nyili pyuo pyuo karenge leya .
43008039	Dokopa nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Aporakame baa namwana rakange kandale leyami . Yesumi nakama dopa lamaiya . Nakama Aporakamena wane pili doko baa pyuo kareyamo doko suu pyao pyuo karamili .
43008040	Dokonako ingyuo Anatumi pii kinyi langiyamo doko nakama langipunupa nakamame namba apa pisala pyapamape lao karaminyi . Yulu dopale Aporakame pii naya kande .
43008041	Nakamana rakange pyuo kareyamuli pyuo nakamame pyuo karaminyi leya . Nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Namwa Anatu kaeyapala kura ipwa likya likya ingyuo kara nalyamano . Namwana Rakange mendaki angi doko Anatuko karenge leyami .
43008042	Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo , Anatu nakamana Rakange ingyapyali dokome namba mona retamili . Dokona lao Anatunya arokwa dokona karo epeyo . Namba rangeme sisu lao epeyonde daa . Baame namba mapanyi peeyamosa epeyo .
43008043	Namba lao karo doko akipamo soo gisa nalyamisi ? Nakamame nambana pii doko selana epe nasingi dokona soo manja nalyaminyi .
43008044	Nakamana Rakange Satane dokona rango doko napala pyuo karamwali lao karaminyi . Baame ene busiyamo dokona piso epo wambu pyao kumakao kareyamoko karenge . Baa keta pii kinyi doko pali nalyamosa baame pii kinyi dokona mende suu pyao lara ingya nange . Baa renge kuiyuo kyambo lenge dokome kyambo lengena rakange kyawa ingyuo karamo .
43008045	Dopa pipyamopape nambame nakama pii kinyi langilyu dokona pii kinyilyamo lao suu pyaa nalyaminyi .
43008046	Nakama karaminyi dokona api mendeme namba kando koo piinyi kandeyo lao kapa neta pyaramisi ? Namba pii kinyi laro ramo doko akipamo nambana pii kinyilyamo lao suu pyaa nalyamisi ?
43008047	Anatunya ingyuo karaminyi dupwame Anatunya pii dupwa soo karenge . Nakama Anatunya ingyuo kara nalyaminyi dokona namba soo kara nalyaminyi leya .
43008048	Juu akaii dupwame baa lamaiyuo , Emba Samaria akali ingyuo imambu koo mendeme maralyipyamo karene lalamano doko kapa laa nalyamase ? leyami .
43008049	Yesumi isingi lao dopa leya . Namba imambu koo maralyapyamo karonde daa . Nambame Rakanena kingi ketae nembo karo . Nakamame nambana kingi isa nembelyaminyi .
43008050	Dopa pilyaminyiko doŋo namba range ketae ululi karapuli lao suu pyao kara nalyo . Mendeme namba ululi karapiii lao suu pyao karamo dokome lao rolara .
43008051	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , mendeme nambana pii lengenyiii pyuo pyuo kararami ramo doko kumungi renge doko kanda nara .
43008052	Juu wambu dupwame baa lamaiyuo , Epapu emba imambu koo maraiyapyamo karene doko soo kaelyamano . Aporakame kumuya . Anatunya poropeta akaii dupwa kumuyamiko doŋo embame lao dokopa mendeme nambana pii lengenyiii pyuo pyuo karara ramo doko kumungi renge doko nakanju see nara laiene kandapi .
43008053	Namwana rakange Aporakame kumuya dokona suu pyao emba mupwa kamame wakasandelyamo . Anatunya akaii dupwako kumuyami kande . Emba range apiyakalende suu pyapala lao karese ? leyami .
43008054	Yesumi isingi lao dopa leya . Namba range lao ketae pyambwapuii nambana pii doko kuiisa ingya napyaii . Nambana Rakange nakamame Anatu lenge dokomeko namba ketae pyambuo karamo .
43008055	Nakamame baa soo nyepa nange . Nambame baa soo nyingi . Nambame baa soo nyepa nange lapuii doko nakama kyambo lao karenge dokonako mendeke ingyuo karapuii . Dopa pipyamopape nambame baa angi soo nyepala banya pii lengenyiii pyuo pyuo lao karenge .
43008056	Nakamana rakange Aporakame dokome namba yuu gii eparo doko kandaro lao sepala monanda pyakaiyuo pyao kareya . Enakana angi kandapala mona paleyamopa kareya leya .
43008057	Dokopa Juu akaii dupwame baa dopa lamaiyami . Emba ee kana akaiisa pao akaiisa kingi paki ene karapa nalene kande doko embame Aporakame kandengese ? leyami .
43008058	Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo , Kinyi kinyi langilyu , Aporakame ene karapa nayamopa namba kareyono doko erotonge mee karalu karenge .
43008059	Dopa leyamo dokopa nakamame baa kaname pyamanale lao lapo nyiyaminyipa Yesu yalu pipala tembole anda dokona potemo peya .
43009001	Baa katasa paole pyuo karo dokopa akaii mende lenge kwaesi manjinyi peeyami doko kandeya .
43009002	Dokopa banya disaepole dupwame baa piso soo , Rapu Pingi , akaii doko baa rangeme koo piyasa panda endangi rakangepame mende koo piyambisa baa lenge kwaesi manjo nyiyamisi ? leyami .
43009003	Yesumi isingi lao Akali dokome koo mende pyuope endangi rakangepame koo mende piyambisa baa lenge kwaesi manjo nyiyaminde daa . Anatunya yulu andake baa keta maro lara ingiyasa lenge kwaesi manjo nyiyami .
43009004	Yuu yango karamo dakepa namba mapanyi peeyamo dokona yulu doko pyuo kararama ingilyamo . lminjaramo dokopa mendeme yulu kapa kando pii nange yuu gii doko oo epopyamo .
43009005	Namba isa yuu dakena kararono yuu gii dusipa isa wambu dupwana lao yanga paupau lakamyuo kararo leya .
43009006	Pii dopa lapala baa yuunya kepakali kyaso retapala awal kukuli lasi rukuraka pyuo pyakerena lao piya . Pipala awal dokome akali dokona lenge doko kisakamiya .
43009007	Kisakamipala baa lamaiyuo , Ipwa pete Silome lenge dokona poeyanyi nembala puu , leya . ( Silome doko namwana pii Mapanyi Peenge dopale . ) Pao ipwa poeyanyi nembapala kapu kyuo kata kapa kando epeya .
43009008	Dokopa anda maki palyuo penge wambu dupwame baa wamba bange jinya jinya lao peteyamo kandeyami dupwapeme lao , Akali wamba bange jinya jinya lao pisipya kandapi doko daase ? leyami .
43009009	Lapome , Doko baalamo leyami . Lapome , Daako doŋo mee banya lenge kambu nyilyamo leyami . Baame , Namba lyakande , leya .
43009010	Nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Apa pipala lenge rapi ? leyami .
43009011	Baame isingi lao , Akali Yesu lenge dokome awal pyakerena lapala nambana lenge doko kisakapala namba ipwa Silome dokona poeyanyi nembapala puu langipyasa namba pao poeyanyi nembapala lenge mee ingyapyamo kandapu leya .
43009012	Nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Baa anja karamo ? leyami . Baame , Namba soo gisa nalyo , leya .
43009013	Akali wamba lenge kwaeyamo kareya doko Parisi akali dupwa kareyami dokona lanyuo epeyami .
43009014	Yesumi awai pyakerena lapala akali banya lenge doko yuu gii koro petenge dokopa pyuo elya pyakamiyapya .
43009015	Parisi dupwame , Apa pisala embena lenge rapi ? lao baa dee kamba piso siyami . Dokopa baame nakama lamaiyuo , Baame nambana lenge dokona awal kisakapyamopa ipwa poeyanyi nembapala kapa kando karo , leya .
43009016	Parisi lapome , Akali dokome koro petenge mawa pii yalo pelyamo dokona Anatumi baa rombo palyiyande daalamo , leyami . Dopa leyaminyipa lapome , Akali koo pyuo karenge dokome apa pyuo yulu andake dopale lasaka pyuo kararase ? leyami . Dopa lao nakama apiyanda piyami .
43009017	Dokopa nakamame akali lenge kwaeyamo doko kambako piso siyami . Emba baame lenge elya pyakapyamo doko baasa kando embame apa lao suu pilisi ? leyami . Baa Anatunya poropeta akali , leya .
43009018	Akali doko wamba lenge kwaeyamopa kapa kandeya doko Juu wambu dupwame kinyi dopa pipyalyamo lao suu pyaa nayami . Suu pyaa napala akali lenge elya pyakamiya dokona endangi rakangepa dolapo epena lapala
43009019	piso soo , Nakambana ikinyingi lenge kwaesi manjo nyiyamba letambinyi doko dakese ? Epapu baa apa pipala kapa kandelyase ? lao piso siyami .
43009020	Banya endangi rakangepame isingi lamaiyuo , Akali dake nambwana ikinyingi lenge kwaesi manjo nyiyamba doko soo karambano .
43009021	Soo karambwanopape epapu apa pipala baa kandelyamo lao apimi banya lenge elya pyakamipyape lao nambwa see nalyambanoko . Baa piso selapape . Baa andapae dokome rangeme lara , leyambi .
43009022	Banya endangi rakangepame Juu wambu dupwa pakapala dopa leyambi . Juu wambu dupwame wambo mendakinya palyuo , Mendeme Yesu baa Koraisa , lara ramo doko baa sinakoke anda epa nana lao ralinyi nembarama leyami .
43009023	Leyamisa endangi rakangepame dokona pakapala lao , Baa andapae karamo dokona range piso selapape leyambi .
43009024	Dokopa dee kamba akali doko epena lapala baa lamaiyuo , Anatunya kingi lao pii rolae laroŋo lao kingi ketae nembo rolo lape . Akali doko yulu koo pingi doko silyamano leyami .
43009025	Dokopa baame lamaiyuo , Baa yulu koo pingipi mee lao see nalyo . Namba mendaki iki soo karo doko , nambana lenge kwaelyamopa karenge doko epapu kapa karo leya .
43009026	Nakamame baa lamaiyuo , Baame emba apa pyakapyase ? Apa pisala embena lenge doko elya pyakapyase ? leyami .
43009027	Baame nakama isingi dopa lamaiya . Wamba langyuo kaeyalono kandapi doko nakama nambana pii soo nyakayami . Akipamo nakamame dee kamba semana letamisi ? Nakama opetae banya disaepole ingyuo karamwali lao suu pilyamisi ? leya .
43009028	Dokopa nakamame baa kilya kandalya kandana pyuo lamaiyuo , Emba banya disaepole , namwa Mosesena disaepole ingyuo karamano .
43009029	Anatumi Mosese pii lamaiya doko soo gisilyamano . Soo gisamwanopape akali dae lao karamo doko anja karo epeya lao see nalyamano leyami .
43009030	Akali dokome dopa lao isingi lamaiya . Pii nangende pyaka selamolyamo . Baa dokome dopa lao isingi lamaiya . Pii nangende pyaka selamolyamo . Baa anja karo epeya lao see namiko doŋo baame nambana lenge elya pyakapya .
43009031	Anatumi yulu koo pingi wambu dupwana pii sakami nange . Sakami nalyamopape wambu mendeme Anatu ketae pyambuo yako lao karo baa letamuli pyuo pyuo karara ramo doko Anatumi dokonako pii sakamyuo karenge doko silyamano .
43009032	Isa yuu doko kanda soo ingiyamo dokopa piso epo wambu mendeme akali lenge kwaesi manjo nyiyaminyi mendena lenge elya pyakamiyami leyaminyi see nange .
43009033	Akali doko Anatumi rombo palyiyamopa epa nayali doko baame mende kapa pii napyali leya .
43009034	Nakamame baa kando lao , Koo andake pipala emba manjo nyiyami doko embame namwa mana langirisi ? leyami . Lapala baa neta nembeyami .
43009035	Baa ramanyi nembeyaminyi doko Yesumi sepala koto kando nyepala baa lamaiyuo , Embame lkinyingi Akali kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karepe ? leya .

43009039	Dokopa Yesumi dopa leya . Isa yuu dakena kote lao rolala epeyo dokome wambu lenge raa nao kareyami dupwame kando soo kararaminyipa lenge rao kareyami dupwa lenge kwaeramo parami leya .
43009040	Parisi lapo baa kareyamo dokona repeta kareyami dusipame baa lamaiyuo , Namwa opetae lenge koonde karamase ? leyami .

43010001	Yesumi dopa leya . Kinyi kinyi langilyu , mendalimi mena sipisipinya kakopasa kambu rolae dokona epa napala kata wakale mendena yalala epara ramo doko waa nao kendepo nengendeme pirasa pira .
43010002	Dopa piramopape mendali kata kolando penge dokona epara ramo doko sipisipinya rapu pinginde eparasa pira .
43010003	Baa epelyamosa kambu rapu pingi akali dokome kambu lumbwakamalngi . Sipisipi dupwame banya pii doko sakamilyaminyipa baame banya rangena sipisipi kingi lao gee lao penge .
43010004	Banya sipisipi kando gee lapala wambo pelyamopa banya sipisipi dupwa banya pii sepala baa pelyamuli pyuo pao karenge .

43010011	Namba sipisipi dupwana rapu pingi angingyuo karo . Rapu pingi angi keyange doko sipisipi dupwana lao kumuo maira , kumakamingi .
43010012	Akali sipisipi range daa mee kanana rae maiyuo rapu pyuo karenge dokome yana suwa kararope andake nalana pingi doko epelyamo kandapala sipisipi dupwa yaki nyepala raio penge . Dokopa yana suwa kararope andake dokome sipisipi dupwa nao rokwapala bolombaio lanyi nembo pyuo karenge .
43010013	Akali doko baa kana iki suu pyao pyuo karo sipisipi dupwa suu pyaa nange dokome ralo penge .
43010014	Namba sipisipi angi keyange rapu pyuo karenge . Rakange dokome namba soo gisilyamopa nambame Rakange doko soo gisingi doko suu pyao nambame nambana range dupwa soo gisilyunupa nambana range dupwame namba soo gisingi .
