43012024	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , witi jingi mende yuunya pao kuma nara ramo doko baa etorenge suiu sera . Dopa piramopape endangi yuunya palyuo kene pyapala rumbingi dokopa jingi malu lyingi .
43012025	Mendeme range karamo dokona mona nyepala kyawa minyuo karalana suu pyara ramo doko letena renge dokona pyakuirasa pira . Mendeme rangena yulu dokona mona mal napala kame soo kaera ramo doko baa letena renge nyepala karalu karara ingilyamo .
43012026	Mendali nambana yulu pyuo karara doko namba paronuli pyuo epara ingilyamo . Dokome namba karare dokona nambana yulu pingi akali dokopa role pyao kararamba . Mendali nambana yulu pyuo kararamo doko Rakaneme baa ketae pyambwaramo karara .
43012027	Epapu namba monarena pulunongo pyapyamopa karo . Dokona apa larose ? Rakane , yuu gii dakepa yulu palamo dokona namba keta pali nanale lao namba nyisape , larose ? Daa , gii dakepana yulu palamo dokona palira lao epeyo .
43012028	Rakane , embena kingi ketae pyambuo karape leya . Dokopa yake panda dokona piso pii mende lao , Wamba dokopa nambana kingi doko ketae pyambuo kareyo . Deeko lao ketae pyambuo kararo leya .
43012029	Wambu malu doo kareyami dupwame pii doko sepala , Yuu gala lalyamo leyami . Wambu lapome , Aŋala mendeme baa lamailyamo , leyami .
43012030	Yesumi pii mende lao dopa leya . Pii doko namba reke lao lao epande daa . Nakamana lao lao epamo leya .
43012031	Epapu gii dakepa isa wambu dupwa lao yapalya yapana pira ingilyamo . Epapu isa wambu dupwana kamongo doko nyuo ralinyi nembara .
43012032	Namba nyuo ketae minyalyuo palyarami gii dokopa wambu peparae namba palirunu dokona sukusa sukusa pira leya .
43012033	( Baa apa pyuo kumuo yaso nao paro lao pii doko wambo leya . )
43012034	Dopa leyamo dokopa wambu malu kareyami dupwame baa dopa lamaiyami . Mawa Pii dokona Koraisa baa karalu karara lao palelyamopa namwa singi . Dokona apa pyuo lkinyingi Akali doko minyalyarami ingilyamo lalese ? Ikinyuigi Akali doko baa apisi ? leyami .
43012035	Yesumi nakama dopa lamaiya . Yuu gii mee lama nakama pipya yanga paupau lao karalopyamo . lminjasara lapala yango karamo dokopa kata nyuo puu pao parami . Mendali iminjilyamo dokopa kata penge doko anja pelyo lao see nao penge .
43012036	Yanga paupau lao karenge doko baa nakama sukusa karamo gii dusipana baa kinyi lao suu pyao karalapape . Dokome nakama yanga paupau lengena wane wanake ingyuo parami leya . Dopa lapala kanjakala pao nakama baa kanda nana lao yalu pyuo kareya .
43012037	Nakama kando kareyaminyipa baame yulu andake malu lasaka pyuo kareyamopape nakamame baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao kara nayami .
43012038	Dopa piyaminyi doko Anatunya poropeta akali Aisaya lenge dokome pii mende leyamo dokona suu pyao piyamisa piya . Pii doko dapa lao palamo . Kamongo , namwa lalamano doko api mendeme kinyilyamo lao suu pyalamisi ? Kamongona poralnya renge doko apimoo keta paneyamo kandeyamisi ? lao palamo .
43012039	Renge dokona lao baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyaa nayami . Dokona lao Aisayame pii mende dopa leya .
43012040	Anatumi nakamana lenge koo inginyi pyambuo , mona kana pokwanyi pyambuo piyalyamo . Nakamana lengeme kando monarena soo giso pipala namba kararo dokona kapu kyepala pyuo elya pyuo nyakape lasarami lapala dopa piyalyamo , leya .
43012041	Aisaya baame Yesu yanga paupau laramo doko wambo kandapala baasa lao leyalyamo .
43012042	Dopa leyamopape Juu rapu pingi akali mupwa lapo dupwapeme baa kapa ingilyamo lao suu piyami . Lao suu pyapala sinakoke sukusa karamano doko ramanyi neta nembaraminyi lao nakamame Parisi akali dupwa kando pakapala dopa lao suu pilyamano lao polo laa nayami .
43012043	Anatumi nakama lakandara dokona poraiyuo mona nyuo kara napala isa akali dupwame nakama lakandarami dokona suu pyao kareyami .
43012044	Dokopa Yesumi pii ketae palyuo lao dopa leya . Mendalimi namba kapa ingingi lao suu pyara dokome nambako iki suu pyaa narasa pira . Namba mapanyi peeyamo doko suu pyao kararasa pira .
43012045	Doko suu pyao mendeme namba kandara dokome namba mapanyi peeyamo doo kandarasa pira .
43012046	Mendalimi namba kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karara doko iminjingi dokona pisu piso pisa nana lapala namba yanga paupau lao isa yuu dakena epeyo .
43012047	Wambu mendeme nambana pii dupwa sepala minya nao karara ramo dokopa nambame baa kando kote laa naro . Dokona ingyuo isa wambu dupwa kando yapalya yapana pyuo lala epeyonde daa . Nambame isa wambu dupwa nyiso pyuo nyela epeyo .
43012048	Mendalimi namba kando waso waso pii napala soo nembo pyuo karara ramo doko yuu gii lumwa pira dokopa pii lapunu dokomeko baa kando lara ingilyamo .
43012049	Dokona lao nambame sisu lao lapunde daa . Rakane namba mapanyi peeyamo dokomeko namba pii laro dupwa langipyamosa pilyamo .
43012050	Dokona suu pyao baame lalu lao leyamo pii doko kyakana renge kulisa doko sulu singi doko soo gisilyu . Dokona pii lao karo doko Rakaneme dopa lape lao lapyamuli pyuo leto leya .
43013001	Pasopa nenge repeta pyaka siyamo dokopa Yesumi isa yuu dakena yaki nyepala rakange keta paponolyamo lao soo manjo nyiya . Baame banya wamba mona reto kareya dopako pyuo mona reto karo kumuya .
43013002	Alemanji nenge napa nayaminyi Satane dokome Jutasa Isakeriote Saimonena ikinyingi dokona monarena kunji pyao Yesu mata kando lena leya .
43013003	Dokopa Yesu Rakaneme yulu peparae kingi rakana palyakayamopa karo epapala dee Anatu karamo dokonako parolyamo lao soo gisiya .
43013004	Soo gisapala nenge nao peteyaminyi dokona roya karapala banya komau sakisi doko koko retapala saole mende nyepala wapuya .
43013005	Wapupala disi mendena ipwa kulimbuo retapala disaepole dupwana kimbu dupwa wate pipapu saole wapuyamo dokome pyao nembapa pyakamiya .
43013006	Dopa pyuo karo Saimone Pita peteyamo dokona epeya . Dokopa Pitame baa lamaiyuo , Kamongo , embame nambana kimbu wate pyakarese ? leya .
43013007	Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo , Pilyunu doko dakepa soo gisa nalene . Rengya sere leya .
43013008	Pitame baa lamaiyuo , Embame nambana kimbu wate pyaka nalu nao nare leya . Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo , Nambame emba wate pyaka naro ramo doko emba nambana mana nyii nare leya .
43013009	Saimone Pita baame baa dopa lamaiya . Kamongo , nambana kimbu yeelyo daa . Nambana kingipi ayembape opetaeko pyakape leya .
43013010	Yesumi baa lamaiyuo , Mendali wate pyuokondali piramo doko dee wate pira ingya nara . Kimbu iki dee wate pira ingyara . Dokopa banya yanenge peparae elyape sera . Sipyamopa nakama elyape karaminyipa mendaki iki karo pisipyamopa karamo leya .
43013011	( Akali dokome mata kando lara lao soo gisapala lao nakama peparae elyape daa leya . )
43013012	Nakamana kimbu wate pyakamipala banya komau dusipa nyepala wambo peteyamo dokona pisipala nakama lamaiyuo , Namba mende pyakalono doko nakama soo gisilyamisi ?
43013013	Nakamame namba kando , Namwana Mana Lenge , Kamongo lenge kandale . Namba dopale ingyuo karo dokona kapa rolae letaminyi .
43013014	Nakamana Kamongo , Mana Lenge dokome nakamana kimbu wate pyakapu ramo dokona nakama rangeme mendeme mendena kimbu wate pyakamirami ingilyamo .
43013015	Nakama pipunyili pyuo pyuo kararami lao yulu doko lasaka pyano .
43013016	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , kendemande akali dokome wakasa ingyapala banya kamongo doko kando ulu pili londele lao kara nange . Dee mendeme akali mende wai pii minyuo pena laramo doko suu pyao minyuo paramo akali doko mapanyi peeyamo dokona kando ulu pili londele lao kara nangeko .
43013017	Pii doko soo gisapala kararami ramo doko nakama keyange keta palirami .
43013018	Nakama peparaesa kando laa nalyo . Nambame akali rombo palyiyu dupwa soo kaeyo karo . Pii pyasi palamo mende , Nambana nenge nao pisipyamo akali doko kapu kyepala kimbu yukaname namba kalyalana pira leyamo doko leyamuli pyuo pira .
43013019	Angi pyaka seramo dokopa namba baalyamo lao soo nyerami lapala ene pyaka sepa nalyamo dakepa dopa piraŋa lao langilyu .
43013020	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , mendeme namba pena laro doko yako lao nyeramo dokome namba yako lao nyerasa pira . Mendeme namba yako lao nyeramo dokome namba mapanyi peeyamo doko yako lao nyerasa pira , leya .
43013021	Yesu pii dopa lapala baa monarena randa piyamopa karapala dopa lao polo leya . Kinyi kinyi langilyu , nakama petaminyi dokona mendeme namba mata kando lara , leya .
43013022	DisaepoIe dupwame mendeme mendali kanda kanda pipala apisa letamo lao saka nayami .
43013023	Banya disaepole dokona mende Yesu mona reteya doko Yesunya paralisa peteya .
43013024	Akali doko Saimone Pitame gyaakai pipala , Baa apisa letase lao piso sepe leya .
43013025	Dokopa akali doko Yesunya kyangali dokona lalyuo sili lapala dopa pyuo piso , Kamongo , emba lalene doko apisi ? leya .
43013026	Yesumi isingi lao , Borete kunjasi dake poeyapala mairunu akali doko leya . Lapala borete doko poeyapala Jutasa Saimone Isakeriotena ikinyingi doko maiya .
43013027	Borete doko maiyapeyamopa Satane Jutasa baa keta epo maralyiya . Yesumi baa lamaiyuo , Emba mende piri ingilyamo doko waiya lao pipi leya .
43013028	Dopa pyuo leyamopa nenge nao peteyaminyi dupwame baa pii lamaiyamo dokona renge angi doko soo gisa nayami .
43013029	Lapome Jutasa kana mone bokote minyuo kareya dokome Yesumi Pasopa nenge narama ingilyamo dokona ropo pinyale lalyamo panda pendewa wambu dupwa kana lapo mainyale lalyamo lao suu piyami .
43013030	Jutasame borete nyepala aopa kamanda peya doko kukwama .
43013031	Baa kamanda papeyamopa Yesu dopa leya . Epapu Ikinyingi Akalinya kingi ketae pyambusi silyamo . Dee baa keta Anatunya kingi doko ketae pelyamoko .
43013032	Dee dopako pyuo Ikinyingi Akali doko enakana Anatu baa keta kingi ketae pyambusi karara . Doko aopa pira ingilyamo .
43013033	Nambana wane dupwa namba yuu gii malu ingyuowale nakama pipya role pyapeta kara narama . Nakamame namba kotarami . Dokona suu pyao Juu wambu lamaipu dokoko epapu nakama langilyu , Namba panya karo dokona kapa epa narami .
43013034	Mawa pii enenge mende jilyu . Nakama yango mendali mona reto karalapape . Nambame nakama mona reto karenge dopako pyuo nakama yango mendali mona reto karalapape .
43013035	Nakama dopa pyuo yango mendali mona reto kararami ramo doko wambu peparaeme nakama nambana disaepolelamo lao kando serami leya .
43013036	Saimone Pitame baa lamaiyuo , Kamongo , emba anja parese ? leya . Yesumi isingi lao , Namba paro dokona epapu moko minyuo eparami ingya nalyamo . Ingya napyamopape rakyame dokopa nakama eparami ingilyamo leya .
43013037	Pitame baa lamaiyuo , Kamongo akipamo emba pare dokona epapu kapa eparo ingya nalyase ? Namba emba kumuo jero leya .
43013038	Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo , Embame namba kumuo jerese ? Kinyi kinyi langilyu , kola kali pii lapa naramopa embame namba yuu remasa mata joo lare leya .
43014001	Nakama mona rando karo nalapape . Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao namba opetaeko suu pyao karalapape .
43014002	Nambana Rakanena anda dokona panda malu silyamo . See napyali doko nakama kararami panda doko rapa rapa pyakala pelyo lapulisi ?
43014003	Dokona suu pyao nakama kararami panda doko pao rapa rapa pyakapala namba kararo dokona nakama opetae kararama lapala dee kamba epo dokopa nakama nyuo nambana arapunya karako leya .
43014004	Dokona suu pyao nakamame namba anja paro kata doko singi kandale .
43014005	Tomasame baa lamaiyuo , Kamongo , emba anja pare lao see nalyamano dokona kata angi doko apa pyuo kando nyeparamase ? leya .
43014006	Yesumi baa lamaiyuo , Namba kata angi dokope kinyinya renge dokope letena renge dokope karo . Mendali namba keta epa nara ramo doko Anatu karamo dokona kando nyii nara .
43014007	Namba soo gisamili doko nambana Rakane doko opetae soo gisamiliko . Doko namba kandapala dokome baa opetae kando soo gisilyaminyi .
43014008	Pilipame baa lamaiyuo , Kamongo , Rakange doko namwa lasaka pipi . Dokopa namwa mona seramopa kararama , leya .
43014009	Yesumi baa lamaiyuo , Pilipa namba nakama pipya yuu andarele karenge doŋo nakamame namba apisi lao soo gisa nalyamisi ? leya . Mendalimi namba kandapala dokome baa opetae kando soo gisilyaminyi . Doko suu pyao namwa Rakange lasaka pipi letene doko akipamo letese ?
43014010	Namba Rakanena arapunya karapunupa Rakane doko nambana keta karamo doko kinyilyamo lao suu pyaa nalyamisi ? Pii langyuo karo doko namba rangeme sisu lao langyuo karonde daa . Rakane namba keta karapala banya yulu range pyuo karamo .
43014011	Namba Rakanena arapunya karapunupa Rakane nambana arapunya karamo langyalono doko kinyilyamo lao suu pyaa narami ramo doko dee nambana yulu andake dupwa kandapala kinyilyamo lao suu pyalapape leya .
43014012	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , namba kapa ingingi lao suu pyao kararami dupwame namba pyuo karo yulu dopale pyuo kararami . Nambame Rakane karamo dokona parono dokona yulu kamame wakasako ingyuo pyuo kararami .
43014013	Nambana kingi lao mende piso serami ramo doko namba pyakaro . Rakanena kingi doko namba keta ketae paramo karara .
43014014	Nambana kingi lao mende piso serami ramo doko namba pyakaro .
43014015	Nakamame namba kando mona reto kararami ramo doko nambana mawa pii dupwa elya pyuo minyuo kararamisa pira .
43014016	Dokopa nambame Rakane kando ateŋa lakao kararonopa baame Nyisingi wakale akali Kinyi lenge Imambu doko julu joo jera .
43014017	Isa wambu dupwame kanda napala see nao karaminyi dokome kapa nyerami ingya nalyamo . Nakama range baa soo gisilyaminyi dokona lao baa nakama pipya karaminyi . Kararaminyipa baa nakamana mona anda dokona epapala palira .
43014018	Nakama range iki karalapa lao yaki nyuo kaeyalu kaeyo kaeronde daa . Nakama kararami dokona epapala kaeyaro .
43014019	Rengya usale dokona isa wambu menge dupwame namba dee kanda nalominyi . Dopa piraminyipape nakamame namba kandarami . Namba angi lete karo dokona nakama opetae lete kararami .
43014020	Namba Rakanena arapu dokona karelyonopa nakama nambana arapunya karaminyipa namba nakama pipya karo pilyu doko yuu gii mende pyaseramo dokopa nakamame soo gisarami .
43014021	Mendeme nambana mawa pii soo nyepala suu pyao karamo dokome namba mona retapyamosa pilyamo . Dokona suu pyao mendeme namba mona retaramo doko nambana Rakane dokome baa mona reto kararamopa nambame baa mona reto nolakarono dokopa namba kandara leya .
43014022	Jutasa ( Isakeriote doko daa ) baame lamaiyuo , Kamongo , apa pyuo namwa yeelyo kando nolakapala isa wambu dupwa kando nolaka narese ? leya .
43014023	Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo , Akali mendeme namba kando mona retara ramo doko nambana pii warombo soo karara . Dokopa nambana Rakangeme baa mona retaramopa baa karara dokona nambwa epo baamoo pipya role pyao palu palirama .
43014024	Mendeme namba mona reto kara nange doko nambana pii warombo soo kara napyasa pilyamo . Dokona suu pyao pii nakama silyaminyi doko nambanande daa . Rakane namba mapanyi peeyamo dokona pii .
43014025	Namba nakama pipya role pyao karamano dokopa pii dusipa langingi kandale .
43014026	Dopa pirunupape Nyisingi Imambu Poo Pyasi Rakaneme nambana kingi lao mapanyi peeyaramo doko pii peparae mana langyuo pii langilyu dupwa peparae nakama suu pyanyi pyambwakara .
43014027	Mona kyuu lao singi renge doko nakama keta palena lapala jilyu . Namba rangena mona kyuu lao singi renge doko nakama jilyu . Isa wambu dupwame mainginyili pyuo jilyunde daa . Nakama mona nemba napala paka nao karalapape .
43014028	Namba pao kaepala dee nakama kararami dokona eparo lapunu doko selaminyi kandapi . Namba angi mona retamili doko Rakane karamo dokona pelene lao rae maiyuo karamili . Namba Rakanepa manda manjo kara nalyo .
43014029	Kinyi leelyamo lao suu pyarami lapala ene pipa napyamopa dopa pira lao langyilyu .
43014030	Isa wambu dupwana kamongo doko epelyamo dokona nambame pii malu dee langyuo kararo ingya nalyamo . Baame namba kando koo mende kapa pii nange .
43014031	Pii nalyamopa nambame Rakane dokona mona reto karo doko isa wambu dupwa sinya lao nambame Rakane dopa piri lao lengenyili pyuo pyuo karo . Mona sipuralapa , leya .
43015001	Namba isa girapo marange angingyuo karelyonopa Rakange doko wangya dupwa pyakepanyi nembo elya pingi ingyuo karenge .
43015002	Nambana wangya jingi angi lyii nange dupwa peparae baame pyakepanyi nembalu nembo nembenge . Wangya jingi angi lyingi dupwa peparae jingi lyulu lyuo karena lapala baame elya pyuo pyakepenge .
43015003	Nambame pii langipu dokome nakama elya pisi karaminyi .
43015004	Nambapa karo paka lakyuo paa nalapape . Dokopa namba nakama keta kararo . Wangya mende marangena sisingi dokona piso ando kara nara ramo doko rangeme sisu lao jingi lyii nara doko suu pyao nakama nambapa pako kara narami ramo doko nakama elyape keta kara narami .
43015005	Namba girapo isa marange ingyuo karelyonopa nakama wangya ingyuo karaminyi . Akali nambana kararamopa namba banya mona anda palironopa jingi malu lyerasa pira . Dokona lao nakamame namba lakipa nyepala kararami ramo dokopa nakama mendepe pinya saka narami .
43015006	Akali mende wangya ingyuo namba marangena sisingi dokona piso ando kara nara ramo doko baa nembaraminyipa kyapwara . Wangya kyapulyamo dupwa yapo nyepala isare dokona pyambuo yangarami ingilyamo .
43015007	Nakama nambana kingi kapena kararaminyipa nambana pii dupwa nakama keta palira ramo doko mende pipuli yaka lao suu pyaraminyili pyuo piso selapape . Dokopa dokonako paiyuo pyakao karara .
43015008	Jingi malu lyuo karo nambana disaepole ingyuo kararaminyi dokome nambana Rakangena kingi ketae pyambwaramisa pira .
43015009	Rakaneme namba mona reto karapyamo doko suu pyao nambame nakama mona retoko karapu . Nambana mona kulisa retenge renge dokona sukusa karalu karo karalapape .
43015010	Nambame Rakanena pii lengenyili pyuo warombo soo karo dokopa baapa mona reto karambano doko suu pyao nakamame nambana pii warombo soo kararaminyipa nambapa mona reto kararamasa pira .
43015011	Nambana rae maingi renge doko nakama keta palyuo simbwaramopa parami dokona lao pii renge dusipa polo langyalono .
43015012	Nambame mawa palyuo dopa leto . Nambame nakama kando mona reto karapu doko suu pyao nakamame yango mendali mona retaro karalapape .
43015013	Mendeme banya puu minyingi dupwa ama wakasa mona retapala dokome nakama nyiso kumuo maira ingilyamo .
43015014	Nambame nakama pipya lao laronuli pyuo kararami ramo doko nambana puu minyingi ingyuo kararamisa pira .
43015015	Kendemande akali dupwame nakamana kamongo dupwa apa pilyaminyi lao soo gisa nange renge dokona nambame nakama kando kendemande ingyuo karaminyi lao laa nalyo . Laa napunupape nambana Rakane pii namba langiyamopa soo nyiya dupwa peparae nakama polo langyuo karapu dokona nakama nambana puu minyingi lalono kandapi .
43015016	Nakamame namba yapalyapa nayaminyipa nambame nakama yapalyuo nakama wangya ingyuo jingi lyuo karala paraminyipa jingi dupwa lyuo karalu karena lao rombo palyiyu . Dopa pyuo kararami dokopa Rakaneme mende pyakana lao piso seraminyili pyuo pyakao karara .
43015017	Mendeme mendali mona reto karalapape lao dokona mawa pii langilyu .
43015018	Isa enda akalipimi nakama awa nayami kande dokopa , namba wambo awa nayaminyili pyuowako awa nalyaminyi lao soo nyelapape .
43015019	Nakama isa wambunya yongo nyuo karamili dokopa isa wambu dupwame nakama namwana rangelyamo lapala mona reto karamili . Doko doŋo nambame nakama yapo nyiyunupa nakama mee sisi panda ingyuo karaminyipa isa wambu yango dupwa nakama kando awa nalyaminyi .
43015020	Wambo pii mende langyalono kandapi doko suu pyalapape Kendemande akali banya kamongo kando wakasa ingya nange langyalono . Doko suu pyao namba randa joo kareyami ramo doko nakama randa jooko kararami . Nambana pii minyuo kareyamili ramo doko nakamana pii minyuo pyuoko kararamili .
43015021	Nakama randa jerami dokopa namba mapanyi peeyamo doko soo gisa napala nakama namba reke lao randa joo kararami .
43015022	Namba epa napala koo keyangepe pakana palyuo mana lamai napuli doko nakama yulu koo kamenge pimisa pii mende pali napyali . Dakepa nambana pii see napala koo piyama larami ingya nalyamo .
43015023	Mendeme namba kando awa nara ramo doko nambana Rakange opetaeko awa narasa pira .
43015024	Nambame nakama pipya karo wambu mendeme yulu pii nange dopale pyuo kara nayoli doko nakama koo keta paa nayamili . Doko nakama nambana yulu andake dupwa kando kaepala nambapa nambana Rakangepa kando awa naoko karaminyi .
43015025	Namba kandakinyuo awa nayami , dopa lao Mawa Pii pyasi doko palamo pii dokona pyaka silyaminyi .
43015026	Kinyinya Renge Palenge Nyisingi Imambu doko Rakane keta karenge doko epara . Baa Rakane role pyao karenge doŋo nambame baa dae pena laronopa baame nambaŋa lao rolo langira .
43015027	Nakama wambo kanda soo nambamoo pipya kareyama dokona ingyuo nakama dopako pyuo nambana lao polo lao kararami .
43016001	Nakama suu longo paa nalapape lao pii dusipa peparae langyalono .
43016002	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , yuu gii epara ingilyamo dokopa nakama sinakoke anda dupwana neta nembarami . Mendeme nakama pyao kumakapala dokopa Anatunya yulu dokona pipusa pilyamo lao suu pyarami .
43016003	Rakangemoo nambamoo soo gisa napala dokona dopa pirami .
43016004	Dopa pirami doko nambwa Rakanepa soo gisa napala nakama pyarami yuu gii pyaka seramo dokopa dopa langii kande lao suu pyarami dokona langyalono . Wamba role pyao kareyama dokopa pii dapwa langya nayo .
43016005	Doko dakepa namba mapanyi peeyamo doko karamo dokona range pelyo . Paronopape nakama mendalimi anja pelene lao piso see nalyaminyi .
43016006	Epapu rolo langyalono dokona nakama monarena kondome kumulyaminyi .
43016007	Kondalyaminyako doŋo nakama kinyi langilyu , namba kanjakala parono dokopa nakama elyape keta palirami . Namba kanjakala paa naro ramo doko Nyisingi doko nakama keta epa nara . Paro ramo doko nambame baa nakama keta mapanyi peeyakaro .
43016008	Baa epapala dokopa isa wambumi yulu koo dokonape yulu rolae dokonape Anatunya kote pii dokona kyai pyuo suu pyaro karaminyi doko pananyi pyambwara .
43016009	Isa wambu dupwame namba kapa ingingi lao suu pyaa nalyaminyi dokona palyuo baame nakamana koo doko nolakakamira .
43016010	Namba Rakange karamo dokona paronopa nakamame namba dee kando narami dokona lao baame yulu rolae angi doko lasaka pira .
43016011	Anatumi isa wambu dupwana Kamongo doko kando kote lapyaŋa lao doko lyakai pyuo panaramo serami .
43016012	Nambame nakama pii malu langiru ingyapyamopape nakama kapa soo nyii narami ingilyamo .
43016013	Kinyi lengena Imambu doko epapala dokopa baame nakama pii kinyi peparae mana langira . Dokona lao baame range sisu lao larande daa . Baa renge seramuli pyuo polo langyuo karara . Baame ene pipa nalyamo dupwa wambo nolakao lao karara .
43016014	Baame nambana dupwa nyepala mana langyuo dokome namba keta pyambwarasa pira .
43016015	Rakangena kingi rakapana silyamo dupwa peparae nambanaŋa . Dokona lao Imambumi renge lamairunu dupwa nyepala nakama langira ingilyamo langyalono kandapi .
43016016	Rengya usale nakamame namba dee kanda narami . Dee mee mende usale dokopa namba kandarami , leya .
43016017	Leyamopa banya disaepole dupwana lapo nakama lao dopa leyami . Baame namwa langilyamo doko aki pii langilyase ? Usale nakamame namba kanda narami , dee mee mende usale namba kandarami . Rakange karamo dokona paro ingilyamo dokona kanda narami langyalamo kandapi , leyami . Kandarami letamo doko akinde letase lao see nalyamano leyami .
43016018	Baame , Usale dokopa kandarami lalamo doko apa pyuondena lalamo kandapisi ? Apa pyuondena lalamo lao saka nalyamano , leyami .
43016019	Yesumi baa piso selana leyami doko . Sepala baame nakama dopa lamaiya . Usale namba kanda narami , dee mee mende usale namba kandarami lalono dokona apa pyuondena lalepe lao nakama range sukusa piso silyamisi ?
43016020	Kinyi kinyi langilyu , nakama ee lao ipwakuku nyeraminyipa neta wambu dupwame rae maiyuo kararami . Nakama kondo kararaminyipape enakana raeko maiyuo kararami .
43016021	Enda mende wane mata pilyamo dokopa rangena yuu gii doko pyaka sipyalyamo lapala mona randange . Dopa pilyamopape wane doko manjo nyepala dokopa raeko maipala baa randa neyamo dupwa nyuo kame singi .
43016022	Doko suu pyao epapu nakama kondome kumuo karaminyi . Dopa pilyaminyipape nambame nakama dee epo kandarono dokopa nakama monarena pyakalyuo pyaramo kararami . Dokopa mendalimi nakama monarena pyakalyuo pyaramo renge doko rekya lao nyeraminde daa .
43016023	Yuu gii dokopa nakamame namba mende piso see narami . Kinyi kinyi langilyu , Rakange doko kando mende piso serami ramo doko baame nambana kingi reke lao kapa jera .
43016024	Wamba nambana kingi dokona lao piso see nayami . Monarena pyakalyuo pingi renge dokome simbuo pyoko pyoko lena lapala piso selapape . Dokopa kando nyerami ingilyamo .
43016025	Nambame kongwaiu lalya lana pyuo langyalono . Yuu gii mendepa nambame kongwalu pii dupwa kaepala Rakange dokona rolae lao langiru .
43016026	Yuu gii dokopa nambana kingi lapala piso serami . Dokopa nambame nakamana lao ateŋa lakaro laa nalyo .
43016027	Nakamame namba mona reto Rakane karamo dokona karo epee lao suu pyao karaminyi dokona Rakane baa rangeme nakama mona reto karamo .
43016028	Rakane karamo dokona karo epapala isa yuu dakena epeyo . Dopa pipala isa yuu dake yaki nyuo Rakane karamo dokonako pelyo , leya .
43016029	Banya disaepole dupwame , Yuu gii dakepa emba kongwalu pii dokona kaepala rolae lalenelyamo doko kandelyamano .
43016030	Embame peparae soo gisingilyamo lao mendeme embena pii doko kinyi lyasilisi lao piso sepenge ingyapa nalyamo lao epapu namwa soo kaelyamano . Dokome emba kinyi Anatu karamo dokona karo epeelyamo lao suu pilyamano leyami .
43016031	Dokopa Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo , Epapu nakama kinyilyamo lao suu pilyamisi ?
43016032	Yuu gii mende eparamo dokopa nakama bolombalo lao anda palengenyili pyuo paraminyipa namba iki kararo . Kinyi kinyi , yuu gii doko epapu pyaka silyamo . Namba iki kararoko doŋo Rakane nambapa kararamba dokome iki ingya nara .
43016033	Nambana arapu dokona kararami dokome nakama mona kui lao sinya lapala pii doko langyalono . Yuu dakena karo randa narami . Nambame isa yuu dake anamasi minyuo karo doko kandapala mona kuki palyuo karalapape , leya .
43017001	Yesumi pii dupwa lapala yake doko kandalyuo kandapala dopa leya . Rakane , yuu gii doko pyaka sipyalyamo . Embame embena lkinyi ketae pyambwarenepa baame emba ketae pyambwara ingilyamo .
43017002	Dokona lao embame wambu baa maiinyi dupwa peparae baame kyakana renge kulisa palu palenge doko maira lapala embame baa isa wambu dupwa peparae iso karena lee .
43017003	Isa wambumi emba Anatu angi karenge dokome Yesu Koraisa mapanyi pee doko kando serami doko kyakana renge kulisa doko nakama keta palira .
43017004	Isa yuu dakena karo yulu jiinyi doko nambame pyuo otapunupa dokome emba ketae pyambwasi karamo .
43017005	Rakane , isa yuu doko ene wasa nange siyamo dokopa embapa nambapa yanga paupau lao kareyamba dokona suu pyao embena lenge kambu seramo dokona kararonopa embame namba yanga paupau lanyi pyambwape .
43017006	Embame isa wambu lapo yapo nyepala namba jiinyi dupwa embena kingi lamaiyunupa soo nyiyami . Dupwa embena ingyuo kareyaminyipa embame namba jiinyipa embena pii doko warombo soo karaminyi .
43017007	Yulu jiinyi dupwa peparae embena ingilyamo doko soo kaelyaminyi .
43017008	Dokona lao nambame pii jiinyi dupwa nakama lamaiyunupa nakamame soo nyepala kinyi kinyi emba karenge dokona namba karo epeelyamo lao sepala embame namba mapanyi pee lao suu pyao karaminyi .
43017009	Nambame nakamana lao ateŋa lakamilyu . Mee isa wambu dupwana lao ateŋa lakami nalyo . Wambu embame jiinyi dupwa embena ingyuo karaminyi dokona nakama suu pyao ateŋa lakamilyu .
43017010	Nambana ingyuo karaminyi dupwa peparae embena . Dee embena ingyuo karaminyi dupwa peparae nambana . Dopa pyuo karo nakamame namba ketae pyambuo karaminyi .
43017011	Epapu isa yuu dakena angi ingyuo kara nalopono . Kara napala emba karene dokona eparo ingyapyamopa nakama isa yuu dakena karaminyi . Rakane poo pyasi embena kingi poral renge paleta lasi namba keta jiinyi dokome nakama kyawa minyuo karape . Minyuo kararenepa nambwa mendaki ingyuo karambano doko suu pyao nakama opetae mendaki ingyuo karenale .
43017012	Nakama pipya role pyao karamwano mange dokopa embena kingi yaki nyii nana lao embena arapu dokona karenale lao iso karapu . Nambame nakama rapu pyuo karapunupa nakama karaminyi dokona mende kwao pupyande daa . Akali mendakindeme kwao para ingingi doko Baepolena leyamuli pyuo isa peya .
43017013	Dopa pipyamopape epapu emba karene dokona epelyo . Doko nambana mona pyakalyuo pingi renge doko nakama keta palena lapala pii dapwa isa yuu dakena lao karo .
43017014	Nambame embena pii doko nakama lamaiyu . Namba dae yuu range ingya nao karo doko suu pyao nakama opetae mee sisi panda ingyuo karaminyi dokona isa wambu yango dupwame nakama epekanda nao karaminyi .
43017015	Nakama isa yuu dokona karaminyi dokona rekya lao nyakape lao ateŋa lao letonde daa . Koo dokome rambu lasara lao kyawa minyuo karape lao ateŋa leto .
43017016	Namba dae range ingya nao karo doko suu pyao nakama dae range ingya napyamoko karaminyi .
43017017	Embena pii kinyinya renge dokome nakama yapo nyerenepa embena ingyuo pena .
43017018	Embame namba isa yuu dakena mapanyi peene doko suu pyao nambame nakama isa yuu dupwana mapanyi pyambuyu .
43017019	Nakama embena wambu yapasi angingyuo pena lao namba range kame soo kaepala embena iki karo .
43017020	Akali dasipana iki ateŋa lakamilyunde daa . Nakamame pii lamairaminyi sepala namba kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala mona jerami dupwana opetaeko lakamilyu .
43017021	Nakama peparae mendaki ingyuo karamili lapala ateŋa lakamilyu . Isa wambu dupwa emba namba mapanyi peelyamo lao suu pinya lapala Rakane emba namba keta karapinyipa dee namba emba keta karo doko suu pyao nakama opetae nambwa keta karamili lao suu pyao leto .
43017022	Nambwa mendaki ingyuo karambano doko suu pyao nakama mendaki ingyuo karamili lapala embame namba yanga paupau lenge renge jiinyi doko nambame nakama maiyu .
43017023	Nakama mendaki ingyuo karamili lapala emba namba keta kararenepa namba nakama keta kararo . Dokopa isa wambu dupwame embame namba mapanyi peeyapala namba mona retenge doko suu pyao nakama mona reto kareneko lao soo gisarami .
43017024	Rakane , wambu namba jiinyi dusipa namba kararo dokona nakama opetae role pyao karamwali lao leto . Karo dokopa isa yuu ene pyuo wasapa naenepa embame namba mona retapala yanga paupau lenge renge jii doko nakama kandarami .
43017025	O Rakane rolae pingi doko , isa wambu dupwame emba soo nyepa naminyipa nambame emba soo nyuo kaepunupa wambu lapome iki embame namba mapanyi peelyamo lao soo gisilyaminyi .
43017026	Embena kingi doko namba lamaiyuo doko dee lamaiyuo karalu kararoko ingilyamo . Dokome embame namba mona reto karene doko nakamana ingyara . Ingyaramopa nambame nakamana mona anda kararo .
43018001	Yesu pii dokio lapala banya disaepole dupwa pipya netarena pao yuu pota Kitone lenge doko nyuo yalo ee mendena pao sukusa peyami .
43018002	Yesu banya disaepole dupwa pipya yuu gii malu yuu dokona malu palyuo pisipa piyami dokona Jutasa baa mata kando leyamo doko opetae yuu doko kando soo kareya .
43018003	Soo karapala baame purisi akali mupwa dupwape Parisi dupwapeme yanda singi lapope yanda singi mupwa mendasipape nyepala lambepe kendapulipi kakupi wua gelape lapo nyuo minyuo pao yuu dokona peyami .
43018004	Dokopa Yesu baa keta piramo yulu dupwa peparae soo gisapala lenge kambu siyamo dokona epapala nakama lamaiyuo , Api kotelyaminyi ? leya .
43018005	Nakamame isingi lao , Yesu Nasarete range doko , leyami . Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo , Doko namba , leya . Jutasa baa mata kando leyamo doko nakama role pyapeta kareyami .
43018006	Doko namba , lamaiyamo dokopa nakamame matanono papala yuunya paro siyami .
43018007	Baame dee piso soo , Api kotelyaminyi ? leya . Dokopa , Yesu Nasarete range , dokoŋo leyami .
43018008	Yesumi isingi lamaiyuo , Doko nambaŋa langyalono lao kandapi doko namba kotarami ramo doko akali dasipa mee neta pena kaeyalapape leya .
43018009	Baa wambo Anatu kando wambu jiinyi dusipana mendali kwao pakapyande daa , leyamo dokona palyuo leya .
43018010	Dokopa Salmone Pitame banya wua gela mandeyamo doko kolo nyepala purisi mupwa dokona kendemande akali dokona kale rolaerename doko pyao rekya lanyi nembeya . Kendemande akali dokona kingi Malakasa lenge .
43018011	Yesumi Pita lamaiyuo , Embena wua gela doko palenge dokona palyape . Rakaneme pee kapo namba jipyamo dokona naa narose ? leya .
43018012	Dokopa yanda singi malu epeyaminyi dusipa dusipana mupwa dokomoo Juu wambunya yanda singi dusipapeme Yesu minyarapala puu maiyami .
43018013	Puu maipala Anasa kareyamo dokona lanyuo peyami . Anasa baa Kayapasana imwange ingyuo kareyamopa Kayapasa baame ee kana dokona purisi mupwa ingyuo kareyamo dokona Anasa dokona wambo lanyuo peyami .
43018014	Akali mendaki wambu dupwana lao kumara dokopa nakama kapa ingyuo palira leyamo pii doko Kayapasa ingyuo leya .
43018015	Saimone Pita disaepole mendepa Yesu peyamo dokona mata pyao peyambi . Disaepole mende doko purisi mupwa wakasa dokome kandenge dokona baa purisi mupwa dokona anda kamapi sukusa kapa peya .
43018016	Dokopa Pita baa kakota lumbungisa kareya . Dokopa disaepole mende doko purisi mupwa dokome kandenge doko netarena papala kendemande enda kakota lumbungi iso kareya doko lamaipala Pita sukusa epena leya .
43018017	Kendemande enda kakota lumbungi isa kareya dokome Pita lamaiyuo , Emba akali dokona disaepole mende daase ? leya . Pita baa , Namba daa , leya .
43018018	Kendemande wambu dusipape yanda singi dusipape kupwa piyasa isare lengya rena lapala soo kareyami . Pita baa opetae nakama pipya karo isare soo kareya .
43018019	Dokopa purisi akali mupwa dokome Yesu banya disaepole dusipanape banya mana pii dokonape baa piso sepa piya .
43018020	Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo , Nambame isa wambu dupwa panembena karo lamaingi , sinakoke anda dupwanape tembole dokonape Juu wambu peparae elyambu pingi panda dusipanape namba mana lamaiyuo karo pii mende yalu pyuo lengende daa .
43018021	Akipamo namba piso silisi ? Nambana pii siyami wambu dupwa nambame apa lenge lao piso sepe . Nambame lao karenge doko nakama soo kaenge , leya .
43018022	Dopa leyamo dokopa yanda singi kareyaminyi dokona mendeme kingi kapeme Yesu rakyuo pyapala , Embame dopa lao purisi mupwa doko isingi lamaingisi ? leya .
43018023	Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo , Nambame kopetame lapu ramo doko pii kwaelyamo doko polo lalase . Rolae nembo lapu ramo doko akipamo namba rakyuo pyalese ? leya .
43018024	Dokopa Anasame , Kayapasa purisi mupwa wakasa karamo dokona Yesu baa puu maisi piso karena lapala lanyuo pupwape , leya .
43018025	Salmone Pita baa isare soo kareya . Dokopa role pyao kareyami dupwame baa lamaiyuo , Emba doko banya disaepole dokona mende daase ? leyami . Dokopa baame , Ama daa leya .
43018026	Purisi akali mupwa dokona kendemande mende Pitame kale pyao rekya lanyi nembakamiya dokona ree palu mendeme baa piso soo , Emba ee dokona baa role pyao karambinyi kandapu doko daase ? leya .
43018027	Pitame dee Daako , leya . Aopa dokopa kola kali pii leya .
43018028	Dokopa wamba kukwa Kayapasana anda doko kaepala Yesu lanyuo kyapona kote singi anda dokona peyami . Nakama rangeme Juu wambunya yulu suu pyao namwa elyape ingya naramosa Pasopa nenge kapa naa nasarama lapala kyapona kote singi andakare dokona paa nayami .
43018029	Paa nayamisa Pailate nakama kareyami dokona kamanda papala , Akali dake kando aki yulu koo pipyaŋa lao epelyaminyi ? leya .
43018030	Nakamame baa isingi lamaiyuo , Akali dakeme yulu koo mende pii nange pyali doko embena panda peeya namwali leyami .
43018031	Pailateme nakama lamaiyuo , Nakama range baa nyepala nakamana mawa pii dupwana lao range kambuyanda pipwape leya . Leyamopa nakamame namwa Juu akali dupwame akali mende pyao kumakarama ingyuo mawa pii dokona pali nalyamo leyami .
43018032	( Yesu wamba namba dopa pyuo isa dokona pyarami lao reteyamo dokona palyuo leyamisa piya . )
43018033	Pailateme kyapona kote singi anda dokona dee papala Yesu epena lapala , Emba Juu wambunya Kiŋisi ? lamaiya .
43018034	Yesu isingi lao , Embame range maso letepe panda lapome namba lao langiminyi letese ? leya .
43018035	Pailate isingi lao , Namba Juusi ? Embena wambu dupwamepe purisi mupwa dusipamepe emba namba keta peeyalaminyi kandapi . Emba aki mende pipisi ? leya .
43018036	Yesumi isingi lao , Nambana isingi yulu doko dae isa panda pali nalyamo . Nambana isingi yulu doko isa pandana yulu ingyuo pupyali doko nambana yulu pingi akali dupwame Juu wambu keta namba nyuo peeya nana lapala pyakando pimili . Nambana isingi yulu doko isa wambunya yulu dopale ingyuo paa nalyamo leya .
43018037	Leyamo sepala Pailateme Emba kiŋi lyasilisi ? leya . Yesumi isingi lao , Embame namba kiŋi lalene kandapi . Kinyi lengena renge polo lao kararo renge mendaki dokonako isa panda dakena namba manjo nyiyami . Wambu kinyi lengena renge wambu keta karaminyi dupwa peparaeme nambana pii soo karenge , leya .
43018038	Pailateme , Kinyi lengena renge doko apiyakalese ? leya . Dopa pyuo leyamopa Pailateme Juu wambu kareyami dokona neta papala , Akali doko yulu koo mende pipya lao soo kanda nalyo .
43018039	Dokoko doŋo nakamana yulu mende singi kandale doko nenge Pasopa nenge gii dokopa akali mendaki namba mokwakapa pingi . Doko suu pyao Juu wambunya Kiŋi doko mokwakapili lao suu pilyamisi ? leya .
43018040	Dopa leyamo dokopa nakamame poralyuo kaeyo lapala , Akali dake daa , Barapasa mokape , leyami . Barapasa baa kendepo nenge akali ingyuo kareya .
43019001	Dokopa Pailateme Yesu nyuo pyaroko pinya leya .
43019002	Dokopa yanda singi dupwame nepereke lapome minyuo kamenyongwapala lengyapu pipala banya kyawa dokona pee pyakamipala baa komau konele mende bolembale lakamiyami .
43019003	Lakamipala baa kareya dokona epapala , Emba Juu wambunya Kiŋi doko karalenelyamo , lapala baa kingi kapeme piyami .
43019004	Juu wambu kareyami dokona Pailateme kamanda dee papala , Baa koo mende pii napyaŋa lao soo kandapilyamo lao selapase , lapala , Nakama karaminyi dokona baa potemo lanyuo epelyo kande , leya .
43019005	Dokopa Yesu nepereke lengyapu pisi pee piro karo komau konele bolembale laro karo piyamopa kamanda epeya . Pailateme nakama lamaiyuo , Akali laminyi doko dake , leya .
43019006	Purisi akali mupwa dupwape yanda singi dupwapeme wangonali pyuo lapala , Baa isa mamandona pyao palya , baa isa mamandona pyao palya , leyami . Pailateme nakama lamaiyuo , Nambame baa koo mende pii napyaŋa lao soo kandapunupape nakama rangeme baa nyepala isa mamandona pyao palyalapape , leya .
43019007	Juu akali dupwame baa lamaiyuo , Baa Anatunya lkinyingi ingyuo karo lapyamosa dokona namwana mawa pii mende palamo dokome baa kumara ingilyamo leyami .
43019008	Dopa leyaminyi sepala Pailate dee pakaya .
43019009	Pakapala kote singi anda dee kolando papala Yesu lamaiyuo , Emba anja karo epee ? leya . Dopa leyamopa Yesumi isingi mende laa naya .
43019010	Dokona Pailateme baa lamaiyuo , Namba pii mende langiri ingya nalyase ? Emba mokwaro dokope isa mamandona pyao palyaro dokope range doko namba keta palamo lao emba see nalese ? leya .

44009021	Lao kareyamo dokopa banya pii siyami wambu dupwa peparae mona nembeyami . Mona nembapala , Yesunya kingi lao ateŋa lenge wambu Jerusaleme petenge dupwa ukiaki minyuo kareya akali doko baa daase ? Baa ukiaki minyuo karapala dae epeyamopa Yesunya wambu puu maipala purisi mupwa dusipana lenge kambu dokona lanyala epeya kande leyami .
44009022	Leyaminyipape Soleme ama porayapala misi pii soo gisapala lao kareya . Soo gisapala baamoo Juu wambu Damasakesa kareyami dupwa pipya apiyanda pyuo , Yesu baa Koraisa angingyuo karenge , lao kareyamosa doko angi ingiyasa nakamana pii doko bulumbulu piya .
44009023	Enakana yuu malu epo papeyamopa Juu wambu dupwame yalu pyuo pisipala pii mendakinya palyapala baa pyao kumakarama leyami .
44009024	Leyaminyipa dopa letaminyi lao akali lapome baa lamaiyaminyi soo kareya . Dokopa anda malu palyuo kareya nemba nemba dokona kana dupwame kame porai pipala kambu lumbuo reteyaminyi dokona Sole epelyape lao kambu dupwana Juu wambu dupwa pyalana isaro siyami .
44009025	Dopa piyaminyipape kukwa dokopa banya disaepole dupwame baa lanyuo pao kame kana dupwame piyami ketae dokona papala pisiki minyasi dokona petena lapala netarena maiyiyami .
44009026	Dokopa baa Jerusaleme dokona disaepole dupwa pipya role pyao kararama lao suu pyao peya . Dokopa disaepole dupwame baa Kurisene ingyuo kara nalyamo lao suu pyapala baa kando pakayami .
44009027	Pakayaminyipa Banapasa dokome aposele dupwa kareyami dokona Sole lanyuo epapala angi lamaiyuo pakana paiyiya . Baame Soleme Damasakesa kata pao dokopa Kamongo dokome baa pii lamaiyamo kandeya . Kandapala Damasakesa dokona Yesunya kingi lao eŋa nembapala boo pyao kareya . Kareyamo dokopa Banapasame aposele dupwa pakana palyuo lamaiya .
44009028	Dopa lamaiyamo dokopa Jerusaleme kareyami dupwa pipya role pyao karo Yesunya kingi lao kata dupwana epapapu papa piya .
44009029	Juu wambu Giriki pii lenge dupwa baamoo apiyanda pyuo lao kareyami . Dokopa nakamame baa apa pipala pyarama lao kando kareyami .
44009030	Pyalana pyuo kareyami doko sepala yangonge dupwame baa yuu Sisaria lanyuo papala yuu Tasasa dokona pena leyami .
44009031	Dokopa yuu Jutiape yuu Galilipi yuu Samariapena Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwa mona kyuu lao siyamopa kareyami . Nakama monarena Kamongo doko pakao karo Imambu Poo Pyasi dokome nakama nyisiyamopa kareyami . Dokopa wambu malu Elyambu Pingi sukusa dokona konda konda pipala ama malu ingiya .
44009032	Dokopa Pitame Elyambu Pingi wambu panda wakale wakale kareyami dupwa nyiso papyuo karo enakana Anatunya wambu yuu Lita kareyami dokona kandala peya .
44009033	Dokona akaii mende kingi Ainasa lenge baa papae rambuyamopa ee kana mange lama karo banya luu palenge rate dokona mee siyamopa Pitame epapala kando nyiya .
44009034	Kando nyepala Pitame baa lamaiya . Ainasa , Yesu Koraisa dokome emba pyuo nyilyamo . Sipurapala embena luu palenge rate rulipi kyaso mondo lao retape leya . Leyamo dokopa baa aopa sipureya .
44009035	Dokopa wambu yuu Litapa yuu Seronepa palenge dupwa peparaeme akali doko kandapala Kamongo dokona mona kapu kyiyami .
44009036	Dokopa yuu Jopa dokona enda disaepole mende peteya . Baa kingi Tapita lenge ( pii doko Giriki pii lao Dokasa lenge . ) Baa yulu keyange wakale wakale dupwa pyuo piso wambu kondapala ama nyiso pyuokondali pyuo peteya .
44009037	Yuu gii dusipana baa anga pyapala kumuya . Dokopa baa wate pipala anda kanya koe mendena minyuo pulyuo pao reteyami .
44009038	Dokopa yuu Lita doko yuu Jopa repeta siyamosa disaepole dupwa Pita baa yuu Lita karapyalyamo lao sepala akali lama baa waiya lao epena lao pena leyami .
44009039	Dokopa Pita sipurapala nakamba pipya role pyao peyami . Pao anda kambusa peyamo dokopa baa lanyuo anda kanya koe dokona pulyuo peyami . Dokona enda waiya peparae dupwa Pita kareyamo repeta dokona ee lao karo walyapaki dupwape komau dupwape Dokasa baa nakama pipya lete peteyamo dokopa pyuo waso maiyamo dupwa baa kandena lao lasaka piyami .
44009040	Dopa piyaminyipape Pitame peparae kamanda pena lapala wapambu kararo pisipala ateŋa leya . Ateŋa lapala yanenge kaoma siyamo doko kandapala dopa lamaiyuo , Tapita , emba sipura , leya . Leyamo dokopa baa lenge reya . Lenge rapala Pita kandapala roya peteya .
44009041	Dokopa baa kii minyuo nyiya . Nyepala wambu yapasi dupwape enda waiya dupwape epena lapala baa lete kareyamopa maiya .
44009042	Dopa pilyamo lao Jopa dokona kapa kapa pyuo siyami . Dokopa wambu malu mee Kamongo baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona maiyami .
44009043	Dokopa Pita yuu malu Jopa dokona karo akali mende Saimone lenge baa mena yanenge elya pyuo mamba kiso pyuo kareyamo dokona anda paleya .
44010001	` Yuu Sisaria dokona akali mende Koniliasa lenge kareya . Baame yanda singi yuu ltali range liti pyuo kareyami dupwa rapu pyuo kareya .
44010002	Baape banya anda range wambu dupwa peparepe Anatu suu pyaokondali pyuo kareyami . Baa ipyapala wambu muiyane dupwa kana mone dupwa mee mokwa soo maimai pyuo , yuu peparae Anaru kando ateŋa lao kareya .
44010003	Alemanji neta dambisa penge sere keloke dokopale pii repa repa piyamopa aŋala mende epapala , Koniliasa lao lamaiyamo rolae kandeya .
44010004	Dokopa baame aŋala dokona pakame kumapala kandaro siya . Kandaro sepala baa lamaiyuo , Kamongo , apa pinya lao epelene ? leya . Leyamo dokopa aŋalame , Emba ateŋa lao kana mone dupwa mokwa soo maiyuo karene doko Anatumi kandapala emba suu pyao karamo leya .
44010005	Embena yulu akali lapome yuu Jopa dokona akali mende Salmone lenge banya kingi mende Pita lenge doko nyela pena leya .
44010006	Akali mende Salmone lenge doko baa mena yanenge elya pingi dokona anda ipwa maronge dokona karamo dokona upunili ingyuo palamo leya .
44010007	Aŋala doko baa dopa pyuo lamaipala papeyamo dokopa banya kendemande akali lamape dee yanda singi Kouiliasa isaro pyuo kareyami dokona Anatu suu pyaokondali pyuo kareyamo mendepe epena lapala

44010010	Papala lopapala nenge naowane lao suu pyao peteya . Dopa pyuo pisipala nenge rapa rapa pyuo kareyaminyi isaro karo dokopa baa pii repa repa piyasa lemongwasi lao peteya .
44010011	Dokopa bange mende komau andake dopale pinjingi kisima dusipa minyili laro karo isa yuu dokona isa epeyamo kandeya .
44010012	Mena suwa wakale wakale dupwape kau wakale wakale dupwape yaka wakale wakale dupwape komau dokona paleta maiyiya .
44010013	Dokopa pii mendeme baa lamaiya . Pita , roya karapala bange dupwa pyapala naa leya .
44010014	Dopa leyamopape Pitame , Kamongo naa naro leya . Namba Juu akali dokome bange koo dokore wasapala yuu wamba naa nange leya .
44010015	Dokopa pii dokome dee kamba baa lamaiya . Anatumi poo pyasi ingyuo wasiyamo dupwa kooŋo laa napipi leya .
44010016	Lapala pii doko dee kamba yuu repo pyuo leyamopa enakana komau bange paleta doko yake dokona pulyuo peya .
44010017	Pulyo papeyamo dokopa Pita pii repa repa pipyamo kandalono doko aki rengendena pyaano lao suu pyanyi pyano peteyamo dokopa akali Kouiliasame dokona pena leyamo dusipa Saimonena anda anja karamo lao wambu piso sepala epo kambu dokona kareyami .
44010018	Karo , Saimone kingi mende Pita lenge baa dana andakare petape mee ? lao kee leyami .
44010019	Pita baa pii repa repa piyamo dokona monarena suu pyanyi pyano peteyamo dokopa Imambu dokome baa lamaiyuo , Akali rema dusipame emba koto epaminyi lyakande .
44010020	Emba roya karapala lupyuo puu . Nambame nakama dae pena lapunupa epaminyi dokona paro panda kaewane lao lamana palyuo suu pyaa napala emba nakama pipya role pyao pupwape leya .
44010021	Dokopa akali dusipa kareyami dokona papala , Nakama kotala imi doko namba dae karo . Apa pipyasa epamipi ? leya .
44010022	Dokopa nakamame lao , Akali mende Kouiliasa lenge yanda singi yango rapu pingi akali andakende baa yulu rolae pyuo Anatu pakao karamo . Juu wambu dupwa peparaeme baa kando akali keyange letaminyi doko aŋala poo pyasi mendeme baa lamaiyuo , Embame pii lapo lamairi lao emba nyela papala banya anda lanyuo ipupwape lena leyapya , leyami .
44010023	Dopa leyaminyi dokopa role pyao palimana lao andakare epena leya . Yangama dokopa sipurapala nakamape Pitape dee banya Kurisene yangonge yuu Jopa karenge lapo dusipa minyuo pyaso peyami .
44010024	Dokona yangama dokopa nakama yuu Sisaria sukusa epeyami . Dokopa Koniliasa banya ree palu dupwape banya mona reto puu minyingi dupwape sukusa sukusa pyuo epena lapala Pitamoo banya akali dusipape epelyamipi lao isaro kareya .
44010025	Dokopa Pita kolando epeyamo dokopa dokona papala baa mupwa lao banya kimbu siyamo dokona pangu siya .
44010026	Pangu siyamopape Pitame baa minyalyuo nyuo , Emba roya karape . Namba mee akaliŋi emba dopale , leya .
44010027	Lapala nakamba pii lao andakare papala wambu malu sukusa sukusa pyuo kareyaminyi kandeya .
44010028	Kandapala baame nakama lamaiyuo , Juu akali dupwame rara wakalena anda papala role pyao kara nange doko nakamana yulu pinginyili pyuo mawa pii mende palamo doko nakama range silyaminyi leya . 44010029	Namba lasaka piyamo dokona namba lanyala pena leyami dokopa namba daa laa napala mee ipu . Akipamo namba lanyala epena leyamisi ? lao piso silyu , leya .
44010030	Dokopa Koniliasa dopa leya . Jukumane wamba yuu gii dakepa neta dambisa karenge sere keloke dokopa namba andakare ateŋa lao peteyo . Lao peteyono dokopa akali komau lepolepo pingi wapunginde epapala nambana lenge kambu siyamo dokona kareyapya .
44010031	Karapala dopa leya . Koniliasa , emba ateŋa lao karenge kandale doko Anatumi sepala , emba kana mone wambu muiyane maipa pingi doko Anatumi suu pyao karenge .
44010032	Dokona akaii Saimone lenge banya kingi mende Pita lenge baa Jopa dokona kotala pena laa . Baa akali mende Saimone lenge mena yanenge elya pingi akali dokona anda ipwa maronge repeta karamo dokona upunili ingyuo palamo leya .
44010033	Leyamo dokona aopa emba nyela pena leyonopa emba anjiki pipala ipilyamo . Epapu namwa Anatunya lenge kambu dakena Kamongome pii lalale lao langipyamo dupwa larene semana lao petamano leya .
44010034	Dopa leyamo dokopa Pitame sipurapala dopa leya . Kinyi Anatumi wambu lapo iki angi angi lao kara nange , doko epapu soo gisilyu .
44010035	Wambu rara wakale wakale Anatu andake lao pako karo yulu rolae pyuo karaminyi dupwa peparae baame nakama kando rae maiyuo karamo .
44010036	Anatumi banya pii doko Isaraele wambu lamaiya doko silyaminyi . Baa Yesu Koraisa wambu peparaena Kamongo doko keta baame nakama mona anda kyuu lao seramopa kararaminŋi lao waili pii keyange doko lamaiya .
44010037	Joneme bapitisimo nyelapape lao wambo boo pyao kareyamopa enakana Yesu baame yuu Galili dokona kanda soo lapala enakana yuu Jutia kipwa kipwa dupwana pao kapa kapa pipape leya .
44010038	Yesu Nasarete range doko Anatumi Imambu Poo Pyasipi renge porai dokope maiya . Maiyapala Anatu baa role pyapeta kareyamopa baa yuu dupwana papyuo yulu keyange pyuo imambu koo dupwa raka lanyi nembo wambu pyuo nyepa piya .
44010039	Baa Juu wambunya yuu dupwanape Jerusaleme dokonape yulu pyuo kareyamo dupwa peparae namwame kandapala epapu lao rolo karamano . Baa pyapala isa mamando dokona yukuyami .
44010040	Yukuyaminyipa yuu gii repo dokopa Anatumi baa minyalyuo nyepala nolako karena leya .
44010041	Baa sipurao epapala kareyamo doko wambu peparae kanda nayami . Anatumi wambo dokopa namwa yapo nyiyamopa namwa banya yulu dupwana lao kararama dupwa iki kandeyama . Anatumi baa lopo nyiyamopa lete kareyamo dokopa namwa baapa nenge nao yalya kando peteyama .
44010042	Baame namwa kando waili pii doko wambu lamaiyalapape leya . Anatumi baa rombo palyiyamopa wambu wambo kumuyami dupwape lete kararami dupwapena yulu dokona kote lao rolo karara .
44010043	Baa eparamopa wambu baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyarami dupwa banya kingi keyange dokona lao nakamana koo dupwa kame sakasi seraŋa lao poropeta akali peparaeme wambo nolako leyami .
44010044	Pita pii dopa lao kareyamo dokopa wambu peparae banya pii soo kareyami dupwa Imambu Poo Pyasi doko nakama peparae maralyiya .
44010045	Dokopa Juu rara dokona Kurisene akali lapo Pitamoo epeyaminyi dusipame Imambu Poo Pyasi Juu daa wambu rara wakale dupwa opetae keta maralyiyasa kando ayaka lao mona nembeyami .
44010046	Nakamame nakama pii rara mendereke lao karo Anatu lakando kareyaminyi doko sepala mona nembeyami . Dokopa Pita dopa leya .
44010047	Namwa Imambu Poo Pyasi nyiyama kande dokonako wambu dapwa nyelaminyi dokome akali mendeme nakama bapitisimo nyerami dokona daa larami ingya nalyamo leya .
44010048	Lapala Yesu Koraisana kingi lao bapitisimo nyakamainya leya . Enakana yuu malu baa nakama role pyao karamana lao piso siyami .
44011001	Aposele dupwape Kurisene yangonge dupwape yuu Jutia kareyami dupwapeme wambu Juu daa rara wakale dupwa opetae Anatunya pii soo yako lamilyamo lao siyami .
44011002	Dokopa Pita baa Jerusaleme dokona lalyuo peyamo dokopa Juu wambu lapome rara peparae yanenge kalomarami doko mawa pii lao kareyami dupwame baa lao nembo dopa leyami .

44011010	Doko yuu remasa dopa piyamopa bange doko yake dokona ipyuo pulyuo peya .
44011011	Yuu gii dokopako akali rema dusipa yuu Sisaria karo akali dokome namba kareyo dokona pena leyamopa anda peteyamano dokona epeyami .
44011012	Dokopa lmambu dokome namba nakama role pyao paowape panda kaewane lao lamana palyuo suu pyaa napala mee nakama pipya pupwa langiya . Kurisene yangonge akali pakinyamange dasipa pipya namba role pyao peyama . Papala akali dokona andakare kolando peyama .

44011014	Pita baame waili pii mende emba langiramo doko seraminyi dokopa embamoo embena anda palenge wambu dupwa peparae Anatumi nyiso pyuo nyakara leya . Dopa langiyamo kandeyo lao baame namwa langiya .
44011015	Namba sipurapala pii lao kareyono dokopa Imambu Poo Pyasi wamba kanda soo namwa keta maralyiya kande doko suu pyao nakama keta maralyiya .
44011016	Dokopa Kamongo dokome pii mende leyamo doko suu piyu . Baa akali Jone ipwa dokona bapitisimo nyakamyuo kareyamopape Anatumi nakama lmambu Poo Pyasi dokome bapitisimo nyakara , leya doko .
44011017	Namwame Kamongo Yesu Koraisa kapa ingingi lao suu piyamanopa Anatumi mende jiya kande dokoko nakama keta maiya . Doko kandapala namba apiyakalendeme Anatunya kata rokwapala daa larose lao suu piyu leya .

44011021	Dokopa Kamongo dokome nakama porainyi pyambuyamopa Kamongo baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala wambu malu mee mona kapu kyiyami .
44011022	Jerusaleme Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwa doko sepala Banapasa baa yuu Andioko dokona pena leyami .
44011023	Baa papala dokopa Anatumi nakama pyuo elyape keta piso nyisiya doko kandapala rae maiya . Nakamame Kamongo doko yaki nyii nao baa mona reto karalu kararama lao poraiyuo suu pyaokondali pipala pyuo karalapape , lao waipi lao nakama lamaiyuo kareya .
44011024	Banapasa baa akali keyange ingyapala Anatu kapa ingingi lao poraiyuo suu pyao lmambu Poo Pyasi banya monarena simbuo paleyamopa wambu malu Kamongopa pakao pisinya suu pyapala mona kapu kyiyami .
44011025	Dokona Banapasame Sole yuu Tasasa kareyamopa dokona kotala peya .
44011026	Baa kando nyepala Andioko dokona role pyao laeyo epeyambi . Epapala yuu dokona ee kana mendaki Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwa pipya nakamba role pyao kareyami . Karo wambu malu nakambame mana lamaiyuo kareyambi . Yuu Andioko dokona mee wambu dupwame disaepole dupwa kando kingi Kurisene doko kanda soo dokona leyami .
44011027	Yuu gii dusipana Anatunya poropeta akali lapo Jerusaleme yaki nyepala Andioko dokona lano epeyami .
44011028	Epeyaminyi dokona mende kingi Akapasa lenge dokome roya karapala lmambu dokome baa pyongo piyamopa , yuu muu dupwana ene lopo andake mende sera leya . ( Baa leyamo pii doko enakana akali Kolotiasa kiŋi yulu pyuo kareyamo yuu gii dusipana pyaka siya . )
44011029	Dokopa Kurisene yango yuu Jutia karaminyi dupwa lopa nao kapa karena lao kana mendemepe mendemepe kapa mairama ingyaramuli pyuo mairama lao suu pyapala akali lama minyuo maiyala pena larama leyami .
44011030	Lapala leyaminyili pyuo Banapasa Solepame kana nyiyami dupwa minyuo pao rapu akali dupwa maiyala pena leyami .
44012001	Yuu gii dokopale ingyuo Erote kiŋi akali dokome Elyambu Pingi wambu kareyami dupwana lapo eneko palyapala kokwa soo kareya .
44012002	Dopa pyuo karo baame Jemesa Jonena yangonge doko wua gela dokome pyao kumakaya .
44012003	Dopa piyamo doko Juu wambu dupwame kando rae maiyamisa kandapala Pita opetae puu mairu lao suu pyapala puu maiya . ( Borete isi reta nange nenge gii dusipana puu maiya . )
44012004	Puu maiyuo nyepala karapusi anda dokona palyapala yanda singi akaiisa ipisu pakinyamangeme Pita epo paramo lapala kisima larapu kando karapa pinya leya . Pasopa nenge nao otapala mee wambu dupwa kararami dokona kambuyanda pimana lao lanyuo paro lapala leya .
44012005	Dopa leyamopa Pita karapusi anda dokona paiyaro kareyami . Palyaro kareyaminyipa Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwame Anatu lao ateŋa lakamyuokondali pyuo kareyami .
44012006	Erote baame rakya lanyuo paro lao paleyamo kukwa dokpa Pitana parali dolapona yanda singi lama dolapo Pitamoo role pyao puu sane dokome anjapala peteyambinyipa palyuo siya . Dokopa yanda singi lama karapusi anda kambu dokona kando isaro kareyambi .
