46015028	Anatumi Yesu nyisaramo dokopa bange peparae nyuo kalyuo rapu pyuo karara . Koraisa Anatunya punji punji ingyuo kararamopa Anatu kamame ulupisale ingyuo karara .
46015029	Wambu kumuyami dupwana lao suu pyao lapome bapitisimo nyakamimwali yaka letaminyi dupwa apa pyuo nyisaramisi ? Dee akali kumuyami dokona mende kinyi lopo epa nara ramo dokolyamo doŋo akipamo nakama bapitisimo nyuo kumuyami dupwa nyisalana lao suu pilyamisi ?
46015030	Dee namwa opetae akipamo yuu peparae randa nyuo kararamase ?
46015031	Yangonemoo yuu gii peparae namba kumaro ingyapyamo pyuo karo . Namba nakamape namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa lete karenge dokona pyamaiyasi karamano dokona nambame rae maipala dopa pyuo langilyu .
46015032	Namba range semongwanyi nembo Epesasa dakena mena rae lenge pyala peyoli dokona aki keyangende nyiyulisi ? Wambu kumuyami dupwa lete epa nange pili doko , rakya kumarama dokona nenge nao ipwa nao pimana lao pii lenge dokona palyuo lao karamwali .
46015033	Kopetame suu pyaa nalapape . Embena puu minyingi koo dupwame emba nyuo isa nembarami ingilyamo .
46015034	Yulu kopetame pilyaniinyi doko yaki nyuo rolo suu pyalapape . Nakama lapo Anatu see nao karaminyi dokona nambame elyanyi pyambuo leto .
46015035	Akali mendeme lao , Apa pyuo kumasi wambu dupwa lopo eparami ? Nakama yanenge apiyakale nyeramipi lao piso sera .
46015036	Doko kopyali ingyuo larasa pira . Embame ee walngi yuunya wara pingi dokopa wambo doko kumapala enenge kene pyara .
46015037	Jingi wara pingi doko suu pyao mee kenapa panda witi jingi yando nasi nyepala wara pingi kandale . Angi andasi yanenge kareta mende nyepala wara pii nange .
46015038	Anatumi walngi dokona yanenge apiyakale mainya suu pilyamuli pyuo maingi . Baame mendaki mendaki lao rangena yanenge dokoko maingi .
46015039	Yuu muu dupwana lete renge bange piso pelyaminyi dupwa yanenge mendareko daa . Wambunya yanenge mendereke nyuo mena rara dupwa wakale nyuo yaka dopako pyuo oma yanenge wakale nyuoko pingi .
46015040	Dokona yake panda yongope isa yuunya yongope dolapo silyamo . Dopako pyuo yake pandana yongo au pingi doko suu pyao isa yuunya yongo wakale au pingi .
46015041	Netape kanape buipi wakale wakale rao au pingi . Dopa pyuo bui range yango sukusape au wakaleko pingi .
46015042	Kumasi dupwa sipuro eparaminyi piramo dopale ingyuo para . Yanenge doko malu pingi dokopa mee rumbyara ingilyamo . Dee angi sipuro epenge dokopa letena karalu karara ingyuo epenge .
46015043	Malu pingi dokopa pyuku lao rumbyuo pyalusi pyasi singi . Dee sipuro epo dokopa porai au pinginde epenge .
46015044	Malu pingi dokopa mee isa yanenge ingyuo pao dee sipuro dokopa imambunya yanenge nyuo pingi . Dopa pyuo yuunya yanenge silyamo dokoko suu pyao imambunya yanenge sipyamo pilyamo .
46015045	Baepole dopa pyuo letamo . Wambo epeyamo Atame doko mee isa akali ingyuo epeya . Enakana epeyamo Atame doko baa Imambu lete karengena maingi ingyuo epeya letamo .
46015046	Doko wambo dokopa mee isa wambunya yongo nyuo kareyaminyipape enakana imambu lete karengena yongo nyerami ingilyamo .
46015047	Atame wambo epeyamo doko yuu sinjimu dokome wasiyapya . Atame lapo pyuo epeyamo doko yake dokona piso epeya .
46015048	wambu isa yuunya range dupwa akali wambo yuu dokome wasiya dopaleko . Dee yake panda range dupwa yakena piso epeyamo dopaleoko .
46015049	Namyva dakepa akali Atame wambo yuu dokome wasisi kareya dopale karamano . Enakana dokopa akali yake panda piso epeya dopale isa komba pyao parama .
46015050	Yangonemoo mende pyuo leto . Wambunya yongo doko Anatunya panda sukusa paa nara . Rumbingi dupwa sulu see nange kandale .
46015051	Selapape , pii koko palenge mende polo langiru . Wambu lapo dupwa kumapa naraminyipape wambu peparae wakale ingyuo alowa pirama .
46015052	Lenge walya lao lembake pingi doko makande pyuo byara andake pyaramopa kumuyami dupwa komba pyapala karalu kararami . Namwa peparae alowa piramopa kararama .
46015053	Isa wambu kumuo rumbyuo penge dupwa kyaka ingyapala karalu kararami .
46015054	Dokona lao rumbingi dupwa alowa pipala rumbya nao sulu seramopa dee wambu kumungi doko kaepala lete karalu kararami . Yuu gii doko pyaka separamopa , buku Baepole letamuli pyuo kuma nange renge dokome kumungi renge doko nyuo isa palyara lao pyasi palamo doko gii pyaka soo eparasa pira .
46015055	Dokona lao kumungi renge doko embena poral renge doko anja palipyandeme namwa randa jerase ? Embena anamasi minyare renge doko anja silyase ?
46015056	Yulu koo paleta dokome kumungi dokopa randa nao karenge . Koo baa Lowame paka pyao silyamopa poralngi .
46015057	Dopa piramopape Anatumi namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa keta namwame kumungi renge nyuo anamasi minyarami lao poralnya renge jilyamo dokona Anatu ange lao karamana .
46015058	Yangonemoo dokona lao nakamame kaeya napala poralyuo karalapape . Kamongona yulu pilyaminyi doko mee pyuo nemba narami dokome yuu peparae Kamongona yulu imambu see nao pyulu pyuo pyuo karalapape .
46016001	Anatunya wambu yuu Jutia range dupwa kana nyuo nyiso mairama dokona ingyuo pii mende palamo . Nambame yuu Galasia Elyambu Pingi dupwa lamaipunu pilyaminyi doko suu pyao pirami ingilyamo .
46016002	Sande peparaena nakama rangena kana nyeraminyili pyuo dokona lapo maso mokwa soo retapa pirami . Dopa pirami ramo namba eparo dokopa nakama kana mone yapo nyii narami ingilyamo .
46016003	Nakama kana doko akali lapo rombo palyapala mairami . Namba epapala dokopa pepa pase mende nambana kingi palyapala Jerusaleme dokona kana doko nyuo manjo pena laro .
46016004	Dee namba panya suu pyaro ramo doko nakama role pyao parama .
46016005	Namba wambo yuu Masetonia paro papala epo nakama karaminyi dokona eparo .
46016006	Nambame yuu gii mendasipa nakama pipa kararama ingilyamo . Doko yuu kupwa pingi mange dokopa yalya kando kararama rapisa . Dee namba yuu mendasa parono dokopa nakamame namba kapa pare lao mapo nyisarami .
46016007	Namba nakamana yuu epapala angingyuo kara nao walya lao paro ramo doko kapa ingya nara . Kamongome namba nakama role pyao karamili lao suu pyara ramo doko yuu malu mee karamwali lao suu pilyu .
46016008	Dopa pipyamopape namba yuu Epesasa dakena karapala yuu gii Pendekosa otaramo dokopa yaki nyero lao suu pilyu .
46016009	Nyisu petenge malu mee karaminyipape dokona nambana kata wapwakapyamopa yulu angi andakende dakena silyamo .
46016010	Namba Kamongona yulu pilyu doko suu pyaoko Timoti pyuo karamo . Doko nakamana anda epeya kande doko baa nakama keta baa angi yako lao nyerami .
46016011	Baa kilya kanda nalapape . Nakamame baa mona seramopa namba keta walya lao epena lao nyisalapape . Akali yango eparami dokona role pyao epara lao suu pyao karo .
46016012	Namwana yangonge Apolosa dokona pii mende langirowale . Nambame yuu malu mee baa poralnyi pyambuo Kurisene yango dupwa role pyao paeyo nakama kandala pena lamaiyu . Dopa lamaiyunupape baa rolae dakepa parope mee lao saka nao karamo . Dee kandaramo yuu gii mende sera ramo dokopa epara .
46016013	Kando karo Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu piyami dokona poraiyuo minyuo porayapala paka nao karalapape .
46016014	Nakamana yulu peparae rae maiyuo mona reto pyuo kararami .
46016015	Setepanasa banya ree palupi dokona nakama silyaminyi . Nakama yuu Girisi dokona wambo kanda soo Kurisene ingiyami . Nakama Anatunya wambu dupwana nyiso pinya lao kumuo maipala banya yulu pyuo karaminyi .
46016016	Yangonemoo nakamape dee wambu lapo nakama pipya role pyao karaminyi dupwapeme nakambana pii warombo soo nyiso pyuo karalapape lao poralyuo langilyu .
46016017	Setepanasa Poryunetasa Akalkasamoo iminyi dokona rae mailyu . Nakama Korina wambu dupwa epa naminyipape doloma imi dokome kapa ingilyamo .
46016018	Dolomame namba nakamape keta rae mainyi pyambuyami dokona nakamana kingi lakandamanale .
46016019	Elyambu Pingi wambu yuu Esia karaminyi dupwame nakama kando yako letaminyi . Akuila dee Pirisila dee nakambana anda elyambu pyuo misi lenge dupwame angingyuo Kurisene yako lengenyili pyuo langilyaminyi .
46016020	Kurisene yangonge dae karaminyi dupwame yako lao petaminyiko . Nakama Anatu dokona lao suu pyao Kurisene yango sukusa mona reto yako lao karalapape .
46016021	Namba rangena kingimi pepa dake pilyu . Namba Poleme yako leto .
46016022	Mendeme Kamongo doko mona reta nange dokona baa keta kwao pena . Namwana Kamongo emba ipupi .
46016023	Kamongo Yesunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge nakama keta palena .
46016024	Yesu Koraisana kingi lao nambame nakama mona reto karo .
47001001	Namba Pole Anatumi rombo palyiyamo dokona Koraisa Yesunya aposele akali ingyuo karo . Namba Timotipa pepa dake pyao jilyambano . Nambwa pepa dake pyao Anatunya Elyambu Pingi yuu Korina dokonape dee Anatunya wambu peparae yuu Girisi karenge peparaepe pyao jilyambanoko .
47001002	Namwana Rakane Anatu Kamongo Yesu Koraisapame mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge mona kyuu lao singi rengepe jinyale lao letambano .
47001003	Namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisana Rakange Anatu doko baame namwa sakame kumapala mona minyarambu karenge dokona namwa banya kingi lakandamana .
47001004	Namwa keta randa epenge dokopa baame namwa nyiso poralnyi pyambungi dokome wambu yango randa nao karaminyi dupwa kondo mona minyarambu pyuo karamano .
47001005	Koraisa randa wakale wakale nyiyamo doko suu pyao namwa baa role pyao randa nyilyamano . Dopako pyuo Koraisa wambu nyiso karamano doko suu pyao baame namwa nyiso karamo .
47001006	Dokona ingyuo nakama koo soo karapala lete wal pyao parami lao nakamana reke lao randa nelyambano . Dee Anatumi nambwa mona minyarambu karamo doko kandapala nakama randa dopale nyerami dokopa mona kuki palyuo kararami ingilyamo .
47001007	Nakama isa paa nao porai ingyuo kararami lao suu pyalu pyao pilyamano . Namwa randa nyilyamano dokonako nakamame randa nyuo karaminyi . Dokona Anatu baame namwa nyisilyamo doko suu pyao nakama nyisara doko silyamano .
47001008	Yangonemoo , namwa yuu Esia dokona randa andake nyiyama dokona rolo langilyu . Randa namwa keta epeyamo dupwa ama andake ingyuo kenda kenda pipyamo namwa lete paa naramanopa kumulyamano lao suu piyama .
47001009	Kumungi renge namwa keta palamo lao suu piyama . Dopa piyamopape namwa range poral lao suu pyaa napala Anatu wambu kumungi lete nyingi dokona kapa nyisara renge doko mana nyiyama .
47001010	Namwa randa nyuo repeta kumaiana kareyamano dokopa Anatu baame namwa lete nyiyamo dokomeko dee kapa lete nyera ingilyamo . Namwame baa kapa nyiso pyuo lete nyera lao poraiyuo suu pilyamano .
47001011	Dokonako palyuo nakamame ateŋa pyakao karapala namwa nyisinyi pyambulyaminyi . Anatumi ateŋa malu pilyaminyi doko isingi yano pyao namwa baame keyange renge palyuo nyisara . Nyisaramo dokopa wambu malu mee namwana yulu kando sangyu lao ateŋa larami .
47001012	Isa yuu dakena palyuo karo piya Anatu dokona lao suu pyao pii rolae iki langiyama . Akipamo namba rae maiyuo pyakalyuo pilyunu dokona langirowale . Namwame mee wambunya soo gisingi dokome langya nao Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi dokona poralnya renge dokome lao langiyama .
47001013	Namwame kongwalu laa napala yaka lao soo nyuo nyerami pii dupwa iki pyao jilyamano .
47001014	Nakama epapu dakepa kuki silyaminyi dokome enakana soo otalu oto otamili leto . Renge doko Kamongo Yesu eparamo yuu gii pyaka seramo dokopa namwa nakama kando rae maiyuo pyakalyuo pyao kararama . Doko suu pyao nakama namwa kando rae maiyuo pyakalyuo pyao kararami .
47001015	Mendeme kata rokwa nara lao soo kaepala yuu lamasa lao epapala mana langyuo nyisaro lao suu piyu .
47001016	Namba yuu Masetonia panya pao karowape dee anda lano epo karowape dokopa nakama pipya yalya kando pisirama lao mondo lao suu piyu . Dopa pyuo dee lalyuo epo dokopa nakamame nyisaraminyipa Jutia epo paro dokona lao suu piyu .
47001017	Kata dopa pyuo parona lao lao kaeyono doko male lao leeŋe lao suu pilyamisi ? Namba range suu pryunuli pyuo rapa rapa pyuo dokopa suu pingi lamana palyuo eparo lapala enakana daa lao mee kambu ketae lee lao suu pilyamipi ?
47001018	Anatu kyambo laa nange doko suu pyao nambana pii doko kinyiko leto . Namba kana minyuo pii lenge doko waa laope daa laope laparae yuu gii mendakipa laa nange .
47001019	Sallasamoo Timoti nambamoo Anatunya Ikinyingi Yesu Koraisa dokona lao polo leyama doko Koraisa baa kapa laope daa laope laa nange . Doko ama daa . Anatu kapa piruna leyamo doko Yesu karamo .
47001020	Anatumi kana minyuo leya doko Yesu keta kapa pingi . Renge dokona lao Anatu kando namwa Yesu Koraisa karamo dokona alya minyuo namwa doko kinyi lao Anatu lakandenge .
47001021	Anatu baa rangeme namwa nakamamoo pipya Koralsana arapu dokona sukusa karamano lao sinyi pyambulyamo . Anatu baa rangeme namwa yapalyuo nyepala kame wakale dokona kareya .
47001022	Namba banyaŋa lao rombo palyuo banya Imambu Poo Pyasi monarena karena leya . Dopa pyuo dokopa keyangena renge nyerami lao lalu lao leya .
47001023	Anatu baa nambana wusinisi ingyuo karamo . Baa nambana mona kandelyamo doko sepala karo nakama randa jii naroŋo lao yuu Korina dokona epa nayo leto .
47001024	Namwame nakama dopa pyuo suu pyalapa lao kunji kunji pyao laa nalyamano . Nakama range poral ingyuo karo Anatunya kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko yaki nyii nalyaminyi . Namwa nakama rae mainyi pyambuo role pyao pyuo karamano .
47002001	Namba dee kamba epo nakama mona kendanyi pyambwa naro lao suu pyao otapu .
47002002	Nambame nakama mona kendanyi pyambwaro ramo dokopa apimoome namba rae mainyi pyambwaramisi ? Wambu nambame mona kendanyi pyambuyunu dusipa iki neta pisirami .
47002003	Wambu namba rae mainyi pyambwaraminyi dupwame namba mona kendanyi pyambwa nana lao epa naro lao suu pyapala pepa doko pyao jiyu . Namba rae mairu ramo dokopa nakama opetaeko rae mairami doko namba soo otelyo .
47002004	Mona randame kumuo ee andake lao randa nao pepa pase doko piyu . Nambame nakama mona randanyi pyambuo pepa pyao jii nayo . Nakama peparae apa pyuo mona retelyono doko soo nyimiii lao pyao jiyu .
47002005	Akali mendeme wambu yango mona kendanyi pyambuyali doko namba kando pii nao nakama kando pirasa pira . Nakama peparae mona kendanyi pyambuyaŋa lao lao kyawa sisingi bolombalo lanyi nembo laa narowale .
47002006	Nakama lapome akali koo piya doko kando randa maiyami doko kapa ingilyamo . Dee kamba mai nalapape .
47002007	Epapu dopa piramopape baa nyuo kame sepakamipala mona poralnyi pyambwarami ingilyamo . Dokopa baa mona kendange dokome kyangayamasi pyaa nana .
47002008	Baa mona retelyaminyi dokona dopa pyuo mona retelyaminyi lao sinya lamaipape lao poralyuo langilyu .
47002009	Renge dokona lao pase mende wambo pyao jiyu . Nambana mana pii laramuli pyuo warombo seramipi daa lao makande pyuo sipuli lao suu piyu .
47002010	Nakamame akali mendena yulu koo doko nyuo kame sakamiramo doko namba nyuo kame sakamiruko . Namba koo doko nyuo kame sakamiru ramo doko nakamana reke lao Yesu Koraisana lenge kambu dokona piru .
47002011	Sataneme yulu koo pinya karamo doko namwa silyamano . Dokona baame nyuo anamasi minya nana lao pirusa pira .
47002012	Namba yuu Toasa dokona Yesu Koraisana waiii pii keyange kanda soo polo lamaila epeyono dokopa Kamongo dokome banya yulu pirami lao wamba kata wapwakayamo doko kandeyo .
47002013	Kandeyonopape namwana yangonge Taltesa pana nayasa namba mona nembo kareyo . Dokona nambame wambu dupwa karena lao yaki nyepala yuu Masetonia peyo .
47002014	Anatu kando sangyu lao karamanale . Namwa Koraisapa pako karo Anatumi namwa kata laminyipya Koralsame nyuo anamasi niinyiyamo dokona namwame anamasi minyilyako lao karamwasa pilyamo . Kyaa keyange neta raeyo penge doko suu pyao Anatumi Koraisa dokona lao wambu peparae serami lapala namwa keta banya pii raeyo lamailyamo .
47002015	Namwa rendamu pingi Koraisame Anatu kiso maingi dopale ingyuo karamano . Rendamu pingi doko neta raeyo pao sukusa wambupi neta wambupi laparae keta pelyamo .
47002016	Neta wambu dupwa al soo dokopa al koo pilyamosa kumuo penge ingilyamo . Sukusa wambu dupwa kyaa keyange sepala dokome lete kararami . Apimi yulu andake dopale kapa ingyuo pirase ?
47002017	Wambu Anatunya waili pii mupwa ingya nalyamo lao suu pyapala male lao karaminyi namwa dopale kara nalyamano . Kara namwanopape Anatumi namwa mapanyi nembeyamo dokona Koraisana kendemande ingyuo Anatunya lenge kambu dokona panga see nao pii angi rolae lao karamano .
47003001	Pii dakeme namwa rangeme dee lakandelyamano ingyuo pelyase ? Wambu lapo pepa pase minyuo paeyo karaminyi doko wal soo namwa pepa pyao nakama jeramase ? Panda nakamame namwa pyao jeramiyokose ?
47003002	Nakamame namwa mona retelyaminyi dokona akipamo mee pepa pase minyuo papyuo kararamase ? Wambu nakamana yulu kandapala namwana lao kapa serami .
47003003	Koraisa baa range pepa dake pyapala namwa keta minyuo pupwa leya doko silyamano . Pyanjilyi ipwange dokome Mosese kana dolapo nyiya dokona makande minyuo pyasi pali nalyamo . Anatu lete karengena Imambu dokome isa wambunya mona anda dokona pyao reteya .
47003004	Yesu Koraisa keta namwa Anatu kapa ingingi lao poralyuo suu pyapala pii doo letamano .
47003005	Namwa yulu doko mora pisipyamopa range pirama ingya nalyamo . Yulu pilyamano porai renge doko Anatumi jilyamo .
47003006	Anatu baame iki namwa kana minyuo lenge enenge kapa pyuo inginyi pyambuya . Kana minyuo lenge enenge doko pepana pyasi lowa daa . lmambu dokome pingi . Lowa pyasi palamo dokome kumungi renge sipuro epenge . Ipyamopape Imambu dokome lete renge minyuo epenge .
47003007	Anatumi Lowa doko kana dolapona pyao retapala Mosese maiyamo dokopa banya yanga paupau lenge renge doko Mosesena lenge kambu dokona yanganyi peeya . Dokome lenge aumiyasa Mosesena lenge kambu kandalana saka nayami . Enakana dokopa Mosesena lenge kambu mee ingiya . Lowana yulumi kumungi renge minyuo epeya doko yanga paupau lengende epeyali
47003008	Imambunya yulu doko kamame yanga paupau lengende epeyali .
47003009	Mosesena Lowa dokome wambu koo piyami dokona kata lasaka piya . Imambu dokome wambu rolae pilyaminyi dupwa yanganyi nembelyamo . Banya yanga paupau lenge doko ama wakasa andake .
47003010	Epapu dakepa yanga paupau andake letamo yanga paupau wambo lao kareyamo doko nyuo yambe pyapyamo pana nalyamo doko kandelyamano .
47003011	Lowa doko ee kana mendasipa iki paleyamopape yanga paupau lao epeya . Doko suu pyao Imambunya karalu karara doko ama yanga paupau wakasa ingyuo lapyali .
47003012	Namwame doko angi pira lao suu pyapala dokome paka nalyamano .
47003013	Namwa Mosese dopale daa . Moseseme Isaraele wambumi yanga paupau lenge kakondelyamo lao kanda nana lao lenge kambu yambe piya .
47003014	Isaraele wambu dupwana suu pingi pali naya . Nakamame yuu gii dokona piso epo epapu dakepa kana minyuo pii leyamo buku wambarae yaka lenge dokopa nakamana suu pingi doko yambe pilyamosa angingyuo sepa nange . Wambu mendeme Yesu kando nyingi dokopa iki wambu dokona suu pingi doko yambe pyakami nange .
47003015	Epapu Mosesena Lowa yaka laminyipa nakamana suu pingi yambe pilyamo .
47003016	Anatunya pii poo pyasi dokona lao , Moseseme Kamongo mona kapu kyuo maiyamopa banya lenge pendakae leya .
47003017	Kamongo lapu doko Imambu dokona lapusa pilyamo . Kamongona Imambu doko wambu keta eparamopa manda rao kararama .
47003018	Dokona lao namwana lenge kambu dupwana mende yambe pyaa napyamopa karamano dokome Kamongona yanga paupau lenge doko nyepala namwa yanga paupau lao baa yale manda manjinyi pyambulyamo . Yanga paupau lenge jilyamo Kamongo doko baa Imambu .
47004001	Anatu baa sakame kumungi dokome yulu pilyamano dake jiya . Dokona lao namwa mona kenda pii nalyamo .
47004002	Yulu koo elyangepe yalu pyuo pingipi peparae yaki nyilyamano . Yaki nyepala namwa panga sepala Anatunya pii angi dokona alowa pii nalyamano . Banya lenge kambu dokona pii rolae yanganyi nembo letamano . Doko wambu peparae pii doko angiŋi lao suu pyaraminyi dokona pyuo karamano .
47004003	Namwa waili pii keyange letamano doko yalu pyuo sipyali doko neta wambu dupwa pipa yalu pyuo sipyali .
47004004	Isa yuu dakena imambu koo dokome nakamana suu pingi iminjanyi pyambuyamo dokona Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyaa nalyaminyi . Koraisa baa Anatu dokona isa komba pyao karo yanga paupau lao karamo waili pii keyange doko nakamana kata doko yanganyi pee nana lao imambu koo doko nee pilyamo .
47004005	Namwa rangena lao polo laa naiyamano . Yesu Koraisa baa Kamongo karenge dokona reke lao namwa kendemande ingyuo karamano renge doko polo letamano .
47004006	Anatumi pii dake lao dokopa , Iminjingi dokona yango rale pira lao Anatu mendaki dokome banya yanga paupau lenge namwana monarena dokona rao karena leya . Dopa pyuo rao karena leyamo dokopa Anatunya yanga paupau lenge Koraisana lenge kambunya nyiya doko soo gisarama lao namwa keta langyuo jiya .
47004007	Jiyamopape namwa Anatunya renge keyange doko soo nyepala karamano dupwa mee pere awaimi wasisi dopale ingyuo karamano . Dokona lao poralnya renge wakasa doko Anatu baa keta iki palenge doko panelyamo . Namwa keta pali nange .
47004008	Namwa yuu malu randa nyimwanopape kwao puu pao paa nalyamano . Apa pirama lao sakapa nalapape kamame isa puu pao paa nalyamanoko .
47004009	Nyisu petenge malu karaminyipape yuu peparae puu minyingi mende karamo . Yuu lapo randa andake nyimwanopape kwaelu kwaeyo kwaeyo ota nalayamano .
47004010	Yuu peparae namwana yanenge dokona Yesunya kumungi renge namwa keta palipyamo manjo paelyamano . Dokona lao banya lete renge namwa keta palamo doko wambu peparae dupwa kandenale .
47004011	Yesu baa namwa isa wambu yulu koo pingi dupwa keta karamo doko panaramo kandena lao namwa yuu peparae randa nyuo kumarama ingyapyamo karamano .
47004012	Kumungi renge namwa keta palipyamopape lete renge nakama keta palira ingilyamo .
47004013	Baepolena pii lao dokopa , Namba kinyi lao suu pyapala sipurapala lao kareyo letamo . Doko suu pyao namwa pii soo nyepala kinyi lao suu pyao leto lao lao karamanoko .
47004014	Anatumi Kamongo Yesu lete sipuro nyiyamo dokome namwa opetae Yesu role pyao minyalyuo nyera . Nyepala dokopa namwape nakamape role pyao banya lenge kambu seramo dokona lanyuo epara , doko silyamano .
47004015	Anatunya renge keyange dupwa nakama nyisara ingilyamo . Dee Anatumi mona keyange palyuo banya pii doko wambu malu sinya laramo dokopa nakama opetae ateŋa lao Anatu dokona lakando ange larami .
47004016	Dokona lao namwana mona kenda pii nalu nao nalyamo . Namwana isa yanenge lano andelyamopape yuu peparae namwana imambu doko kyaka ingyuo pelyamo .
47004017	Epapu dakepa namwa randa kuki walya lao pao otaramo doko nyimwano dokona rengya yanga paupau lenge renge andake wakasa rao karalu karara doko nyerama . Yanga paupau lenge renge nyeramano doko ama andake ingyaramo dokopa randa wambo nyiyama doko kuki ingyuo peya lao kandarama .
47004018	Bange kandenge dupwana suu pyaa nao kanda nange dupwana iki poralyuo suu pyao karamano . Bange kandenge dupwa waiya lao otara . Bange kanda nange dupwa soo otalu oto otara .
47005001	Namwa isa petamano yanengena anda lalyaramo dokopa Anatu baa rangeme anda yake pandana piyamo karalu karo karara dokona namwa dokona palipa Anatumi lara .
47005002	Namwa dae karo dokopa ee lao karamano . Namwana anda yake panda karamo doko komau pee pipala karenge doko suu pyao namwa koko kararama lao letamano .
47005003	Anda yake panda karamo doko namwa yambe pyara ramo doko namwana yanenge dopale ingyuo para .
47005004	Isa yuunya yongo doko paleta dokopa mona kendo ee lao karamano . Dopa pimwanopape isa yuunya yongo doko nembalana laa nalyamano . Laa namwanopape namwa yake panda dokona yongo doko nyelana lao suu pilyamano . Dopa pira ramo dokopa lete renge sulu seramo dokome kumungi renge doko anamasi minyara .
47005005	Anatumi alowa piramiŋi lao namwana rapa rapa pyakaya . Banya keyange renge doko nakama jero lao mumbwa palyili lao banya Imambu wambo jiya .
47005006	Dokona lao namwa paka napala poralyuo karamano . Isa yanenge nyuo karamano dokopa Kamongona panda kara nalyamano doko silyamano .
47005007	Namwa Anatu lengeme kanda napalape baa iki kapa ingingi lao poralyuo suu pilyamano .
47005008	Porayapala karo isa yanenge nyuo karamano dake yaki nyepala Yesunya panda dokona karamwali yaka letamano .
47005009	Isa yanenge nyuo karowape Anatunya panda dokona karowape pii mende daa . Anatu baa rae mainyi pyambwarama doko iki mupwa lao suu pilyamano .
47005010	Namwa peparae Koraisa kote lao karara dokona paramano dokopa baame namwa apa pyuo yulu piyami lao yapalyuo sera . Yuu gii dokopa namwa isa yuu karo yulu keyange pyuope panda yulu koo pyuope dokona namwana yulu piyamuli pyuo mendaki mendaki lao yole yano nyerama .
47005011	Anatu andake dokona kando pakapala wambu dupwa Kurisene inginyi pyambuo karamwanosa pifyamo . Anatumi namwana mona anda soo gisingi . Nakamame namba dopa pyuo soo giso otamili yaka .
47005012	Namwa akali keyange karamano lao range lakandao laa nalyamano . Nakamame namwa kando rae maiyuo mona anda pyakalyuo pyapyali yaka lao letamano . Dokona wambu lapome mona anda kanda napala mee yanenge ketae kandapala wambu yango lakandenge dupwa kando pii keyange isingi mana lamairami ingilyamo .
47005013	Namwa kopyali minyarama ramo doko Anatu dokona reke lao kopyali minyilyamano . Dee namwa mona palira ramo dokopa nakamana reke lao kararamasa pira .
47005014	Koraisame isa wambu peparaena lao kumuyamo dokona ingyuo namwa peparae baa role pyao kumuyamasa piya . Renge keyange doko separamanopa banya mona retenge renge dokome namwa kame pyuo minyilyamo .
47005015	Yesumi wambu peparaena lao kumuyamo dokona nakama range yeelyo kara narami ingilyamo . Yesu kumapala nakamana lao lopo epeya dokona banya iki karo yulu pyakamyuo kararami ingilyamo .
47005016	Epapu dakepa namwa rangeme wambu dupwa koo pingi panda keyange pingi lao yapalya nalyamano . Wambo Koraisa baa isa akali lao suu piyamo doŋo epapu baa mee isa akali ingya nalyamo doko kandelyamano .
47005017	Wambu mendali Yesu Koraisapa pakarambi ramo doko baa kyaka ingyuo para . Wambarae doko isa paramopa enenge doko sipuro eparasa pira .
47005018	Anatu rangeme yulu andake doko pyuo karamo . Namwa banya nyisu petenge ingyuo kareyamanopape Anatumi Koriasa keta namwa nyuo alowa pipala banya puu minyingi inginyi pyambuya . Pyambuo dokopa baame wambu menge opetae banya puu minyingi inginyi pyambwalapape lao yulu doko namwa jiya .
47005019	Anatumi Koraisa keta wambu peparae banya puu minyingi inginyi pyambuya dokona waili pii doko polo letamano . Doko nakamana yulu koo piyami dupwa yaka lao suu pyakami naya . Suu pyakami nayamopape apa pyuo nakama banya puu minyingi inginyi pyambulyu lao waili pii doko langyuo jiya .
47005020	Namwa dae karo Koraisana pii lakamilyamano . Mendaki dopale ingyuo Anatumi namwa keta nakama poraiyuo piso soo karamo . Koraisana reke lao nakama piso sokondali pyuo letamano . Anatumi nakama nyisu petenge dupwa alowa pipala puu mmyingi inginyi pyambwanale .
47005021	Koraisa baa koo mende pii nange . Koo pii nayamopape Anatumi namwana koo dupwa Koraisa keta palena leya . Dopa piyamo dokona namwa baapa pako karo Anatunya rolae pingi renge namwa keta palamo .
47006001	Namwana yulu Anatumoo role pyao pyuo karamano dokona nakama piso sokondali pyuo lao , nakama Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko nyepala dokopa kokwa see nalapape letamano .
47006002	Anatunya pii letamo doko selapa . Yuu gii keyange pyaka siyamopa naka mana pii siyu . Lete wal pyao nyingi yuu gii dokona nakama nyiso kareyo letamo . Selapa . Epapu dakepa Anatu nyisinya lapenge ingilyamo . Epapu dakepa Anatunya lete wal pyao nyingi yuu gii doko pyaka sepelyamo .
47006003	Namwa kopetame pyuo karaminyi lasaraminyi kandena lapala namwa yulu rolae pyuo wambu kata keyange dokona papala lukumaraminyi yulu mende pii namanale lao suu pilyamano .
47006004	Dopa pyuo namwa yulu peparae pyuo namwa Anatunya kendemande akaii karaminyi lao kandelyaminyi . Namwa randa andake nyuo kenda kenda pipyamo maka napala yaki nyii nao karamano .
47006005	Imbwuapala pyalana pyuo karapusi pyuo randa joo lalya lao kareyami . Namwana yulu andake soo kaeyo siyamopa nenge naa nao lopome kumuo luu paii nao pyuo kareyama .
47006006	Wambu dupwame namwana yulu yapasipi soo gisingipi yulu makao yaki nyii nangepe anjiki pingipi dusipa namwa keta kandapala namwa Anatunya kendemande lao soo kando gisilyaminyi . Imambu Poo Pyasi namwana monarena karapyamopape namwa wambu yango mona retenge doko kandapala namwa Anatunya kendemande akali karamano doko wambu dupwa soo gisilyaminyi .
47006007	Anatu banya pii angi kinyi letamano dokope Anatunya poralnya renge namwa keta palamo dokope kando soo gisilyaminyiko . Namwame rolae pinginya renge dokome nyuo alya ingyuo karapala pyao pingi .
47006008	Wambu lapome namwana kingi lakandenge dee lapome epekanda napala kingi nyuo isa palyingi . Lapome namwa kilya kandalya kandana lengepe dee lapome namwana lao pii keyange lakange . Namwa pii kyambo letaminyi laminyipape pii rolae iki lao karamano .
47006009	Nakamame namwa kando see nalyamano laminyipape nakama namwa soo kaeyo karaminyi . Namwa kumasi silyaminyi laminyipape lete karamano doko nakama Korina wambu silyaminyi . Randa joo piyaminyipape namwa kuma napala lete karamano doko kandelyaminyi .
47006010	Mona kendanyi pyambuyaminyipape namwa yuu peparae rae maiyuo karamano . Namwa akali pendewa lao suu pyaminyipape wambu malu kamonganyi pyambulyamano . Namwame mende daa lao suu pyaminyipape aepyamo karamano .
47006011	O nambana puu minyingi yuu Korina range dupwa . Panga see nao pii rolae iki neta pyakamyuo lao kareyama doko nakama range kapa silyaminyi .
47006012	Namwa nakama pipya suu pingi mendaki palyamana lao suu piyamanopape nakama dopa lao suu pyaa nayami .
47006013	Rakangeme ikinyingi dupwa pii lamainginyili pyuo dakepa nakama pii langilyu . Namwame nakama lao suu pilyamano doko suu pyao nakamame namwa mona retowako karalapape . Dopa pyuo namwa mata jii nao kando nyelapape .
47006014	Nakamame Kurisene ingya nange dupwa kando mona mendare palamo lao suu pyapala yulu mendare role pyao pirami doko kapa ingyuo paa nara . Apa pyuo rolae pinginya rengepe koo pinginya rengepe role pyao pakarambisi ? Apa pyuo iminjingipi yangengepe role pyao pakarambisi ?
47006015	Apa pyuo Yesu Koraisapa Satanepa pii mendakinya palyarambisi ? Wambu Yesu mona kapu kyuo maingi dokope mona kapu kyuo mai nange dokope suu pingi mendaki palyuo kararambi ingya nalyamo .
47006016	Apa pyuo Anatunya Elyambu Pingi dupwape Satanena wambu dupwape role pyao kararamisi ? Namwa Anatu lete karengena tembole anda dopale karamano suu pyalapape . Anatu baa range dopa pyuo leya . Namba nakama pipya yalya kando role pyao kararo . Namba nakamana Anatu ingyaronopa nakama nambana wambu ingyarami .
47006017	Dokona lao Kamongo dopa letamo . Nakamame wambu menge dupwa rekya lao kaepala liti pyuo karalapape . Wambu koo pingi dupwa yalya kando pisa narami ramo dokopa nakama yako laro .
47006018	Namba nakamana rakange ingyaronopa nakama nambana wane wanake ingyarami lao Kamongo andake wakasa doko letamo .
47007001	Yangonemoo Anatumi kinyi lalu lao leyamo renge keyange dupwa peparae namwa keta palamo . Dokona yulu mendeme namwana yongope imambupi karo pisinyi pyambungi doko rekya lao liti pimana . Yulu poo pyasi iki moko minyuo pyuo karo Anatu pako karo baa yeelyo poralyuo suu pyao karamanale .
47007002	Namwa mata joo kara nalapape . Namwa mendali kando koo pii nao kokwa see nao minyoko pii nao pyuo karenge .
47007003	Nakama koo piyami lao lapusa pii nalyamo . Wambo langiyunuli pyuo dee kamba langilyu . Namwame nakama mona retenge dokome lete kararamanopape kumaramanopape nakama pipya role pyao kararama .
47007004	Nakama mondo lao pyuo karaminyi doko sepala rae maiyuo mona anda pyakalyuo pyao karo . Randa peparae nyimwanopape paka nao raeme kumuo karo .
47007005	Kinyi yuu Masetonia pao karapala dokopa koo soo kara nayama . Randa dupwa yuu muu dupwana soo kapa piya . Wambu menge dupwa kando lalya lao paka renge neta epo piya .
47007006	Paka renge neta epeyamopape Anatumi wambu mona nembenge dupwa mona minyarambu pingi doko baame Taltesa jepala namba mona poralnyi pyambuya .
47007007	Baa epeyamo dokome iki namwa poralnyi pyambwa naya . Nakamame banya mona poralnyi pyambuyaminyi doko langiyamo sepala namwa rae maiyama . Nakama namba Pole kandamwali yaka letaminyi lao langiya . Langiyamopa nakama kondome kumapala nambana reke lao lakao karaminyi langiya . Dokona dakepa namba rae andake mailyu .
47007008	Pepa pyao jiyu dokome nakama mona kendanyi pyambuyamopape namba mende suu pyaa nayo . Angi kandeyoli dokopa kondayoliŋi dakepa konda nalyo .
47007009	Nakama mona kendanyi pyambuyu dokona lao rae mailyu laa nalyo . Nakama mona kendayami renge dokome suu pingi alowa piyami dokona lao dakepa namba rae mailyu . Nakamana mona kendo kareyami dokome Anatumi nakamana suu pingi alowa piya . Dokona lao namwa nakama randa julu joo jii nayama kande .
47007010	Namwa mona kendo kararama dokopa Anatu nyisaramopa mona kapu kyepala lete penge kata dokona rae maiyuo parama . Dopa piramanopape wambunya mona kendange renge dokome kumungi renge mmyuo epenge .
47007011	Anatumi nakamana mona kendayami dokona nyepala apa piya lao kandalapape . Dakepa nakama mona angi palyuokondali pilyamo . Koo pii nalyamano lao poralyuo simili yaka lao letaminyi . Nakama koo pilyaminyi larami ramo doko imbwuarami . Imbwuapala koo pilyaminyi laka nanale . Dake mupwa wakasa lao poralyuo suu pyapala namba kando mona andake retelyaminyi . Wambu menge dupwa koo pirami ramo dokopa walya lao pyalana letaminyi . Yulu dake piminyi dokome nakama kopetame pii nayami lao pano nolakaya .
47007012	Pepa jiyunu doko akali koo piyamo dokona reke lao pyaa nayo . Dee akali baa keta koo pyuo pisiyamo dokona lao pyaa nayoko . Nakama Anatunya lenge kambu dokona karo apa pyuo namwa mona retelyaminyi lao lasaka pelana pepa piyu .
47007013	Renge dokona namwa poralnyi pyambulyamo . Renge mende palamo doko nakama peparaeme Taltesa baa rae mamyi pyambuyaminyisa baa rae maiyuo karamo doko kandapala rae mailyamano .
47007014	Namba wambo nakama yulu keyange pingi lao Taitesa lamaiyu . Nakama enakana namba elyanyi pyambwa nayami . Yuu peparae pii rolae angi lao langyuo kareyama doko suu pyao enakana nakama yulu keyange piyami Taltesa kandeya dokome namwa pii kinyi ingyuo peya .
47007015	Baa epeyamo dokopa nakama banya pii warombo sepala lakanda minya minya pyuo yako lao sukusa nyiyami doko suu pyaro karamo . Dopa pyuo piyamisa baa nakama angingyuo mona jilyamo .
47007016	Namba nakama arapu dokona renge renge soo karapunu dokona namba rae andake maiyuo karo .
47008001	Yangonemoo Anatu mona keyange palyuo ipyuo Masetonia Elyambu Pingi wambu nyisiyamopa yulu andake piyami doko selapale lao langirowale .
47008002	Nakama randa koo nao kareyaminyipape rae maiyuo kareyami . Pendewa ingyuo karapalape nakama ipyuo wambu yango nyisamwali lao suu piyami dokome kana andake jiyami .
47008003	Rangeme sipurapala kana siyamo dupwa pyambwapala enakana dee kamameko koto nyepala konda pyuo reteyami doko kinyi langilyu .
47008004	Nakama kana doko retapala nakama suu piyaminyili pyuo wambu Jutia palenge dupwa nyiso maiyakalapape lao namwa poralyuo piso siyami .
47008005	Nakama dopa pyuo yulu andake pirami lao suu pyaa nayama . Nakama wambo mona Kamongo doko maiyuo oteyami . Enakana Anatunya suu pingi doko moko minyapala nakamame namwa mona joo oteyamiko .
47008006	Taltesa dopako pyuo nakama keta epapala yulu kanda soo piyamo doko pyulu pyuo pinya lao poralyuo lamaiyama . Dopa piramo dokopa nakama Anatu mona reto yulu andake pilyaminyi doko baame nyisaramopa pyuo otalu oto otarami .
47008007	Nakama lmambunya kamongapala nakamana Anatu kapa ingingi lao poralyuo suu pingi . Dokome Anatunya pii kapa polo letaminyi . Nakamame renge dupwa peparae soo giso otenge . Nakama namwa rae maiyuo nyisalana namwa mona andake retelyaminyi . Dokona lao Anatu mona retenge yulu doko mumu laa nao rae maiyuo pipape letamano .
47008008	Nambame nakama lowa waso joo laa nalyo . Laa napunupape wambu menge wakale lapome pendewa wambu rae maiyuo nyisalana letaminyi dokona nakama pano langyapala nakamana mona retenge renge doko angipi mee lao koto kandalana pyapi pyuo silyu .
47008009	Kamongo Yesu Koraisa baa mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko nakama silyaminyi . Baa kamongo ingyuo kareyamopape nakamana reke lao baa pendewa ingyuo peya . Dopa pyuo baa pendewa ingyuo peyamo dokome nakama kamonganyi pyambuya .
47008010	Namba dake lao suu pilyu . Ee kana wambo kanda soo piyaminyi yulu doko dakepa pyuo otalapape . Nakama wambo kanda soo pii nalana suu piyaminde daa . Nakama rae maiyuo pimwallinyi iki suu piyami .
47008011	Yulu doko pyuo otalapape leto . Nakama rae maiyuo pinya suu pyao rapa rapa piyaminyi doko suu pyao rae maiyuoko pyuo otalapape . Nakama range aelyamo dupwame nyuo pipape .
47008012	Nakama rae maiyuo mailana suu pyarami ramo dokopa bange seramuli pyuo mairaminyi doko Anatu kapa lao suu pyara . Bange daa ramo doko mende laa nara .
47008013	Nambame nakama iki randa nyuo karaminyipa menge dupwa mee manda rao karenale laa nalyo . Laa napunupa epapu dakepa nakama bange malu reto karaminyi dokona wambu pendewa dupwa nyisarami ramo doko kapa rolae ingyuo pelyamo . Enakana nakamana bange see naramo dokopa doloma bange seramo kararaminyi dokome nakama nyisarami . Dopa piramo dokopa nakamba laparaena mendare ingyuo para .
47008014	
47008015	Baepoleme lao dokopa , Akalimi malu mee yapo nyiyamo doko kamame andakya naya . Akalimi kuki lama yapo nyiyamo doko kamame kukya naya letamo .
47008016	Namwame nakama rae maiyuo nyisalana suu pilyamano doko suu pyao Anatumi Taltesa opetae nakama rae maiyuo nyisinya lao kareya . Dokona lao Anatu kando sangyu letamano .
47008017	Taltesa nakama nyisarepe mee lao piso siyamanopa baa mende laa nao warombo soo piru leya . Mee piimi ŋee leyande daa . Baa nakama nyisapuli yaka lao suu piyamuli pyuo nakama keta epeya .
47008018	Akali yango mende Anatunya waili pii keyange polo letamo doko Elyambu Pingi peparaeme banya pii epe singi doko baa opetae Taltesa role pyao pena letamano .
47008019	Akaii doko , Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwame baa rombo palyapala namwa Anatu mona retenge yulu dokona pyuo kamongona kingi lakandalana baa role pyao papyuo kararama leyami . Yulu mendena baa namwamoo pipya nyisamwaii lao suu pilyamano .
47008020	Namwa keta kana malu pyamaiyiyaminyi doko ukiaki minyaramanopa wambu dupwa mumu lasaraminyi lapala waso karamano .
47008021	Kamongo Anatunya lenge kambu dokonape wambu dupwana lenge kambu dokonape yulu rolae pimwali lao suu pilyamano .
47008022	Dokona namwana yangonge akali mende opetae role pyao pena lao peelyamano . Namwa yuu malu mee banya yulu apiyakale lao makande piyamano dokopa baa rae maiyuo waa waa karo nyisalana piya . Epapu dakepa nakama mondo lao karaminyi doko sepala rae mailyamo dokona nakama lama opetae mona karo nyisapuli lao suu pyao karamo .
47008023	Dee Taltesa baa nambana yulu role pyao pingi dokome nakama pyuo nyisilyambano . Dee akali menge role pyao paraminyi dupwa nakama Elyambu Pinginya rombo palyisi akali ingyuo dupwa Koraisana kingi ketae pyambuo lakando pelyaminyi .
47008024	Nakama mona retelyaminyi dokona lasaka pyuo pipape . Dokopa nakamana yulu keyange doko namwame lakandaramano kandapala namwame kapa letaminyi lao kandarami .
47009001	Nakama lapome Anatunya wambu Jutia palenge dupwa nyiso kaelyaminyi dokona aki letoŋo lao dee pepa pyao jerose ?
47009002	Nakama waa waa karo nyisalana karaminyi doko silyu . Nyisalana karaminyi doko sepala nakamana lao yuu Masetonia wambu rae maiyuo mona anda pyakalyuo pyao lamaiyuo kareyo . Ee kana wambo dokona oiso pao epapu dakepa nakama Korina Kurisene yuu Girisi karaminyi dupwame nyisalana karaminyi , dokona lao lamaiyakayo . Nakamame mona nyepala nyisalana piyaminyi dokome wambu malunya monarena piya .
47009003	Nambame nakamana lao rae maiyuo mona anda pyakalyuo pyao leyono doko mee ingyuo paa nanale lao dakepa yangonge dapwa pena leto . Doko nakama epeyaminyi kande dokopa wamba langjyunu dokona kata palyuo nyisarami lao silyu .
47009004	Dokona Masetonia wambu namba role pyao eparama dupwame nakama nyisalana rapa rapa pii nao mee kararami ramo doko kandapala elyaramanopa nakama Korina range dupwa opetaeko elya nyerami ingilyamo .
47009005	Dokona lao nambame akali wambo nembelyo dusipame kana lasaka pyuo jerama leyaminyi doko nyepala rapa rapa pirami . Namba eparono dokopa wambo elya pisi seramo kandaro . Nakama Anatu mainya mumu lao karo mai nalyaminyi . Nakama rangeme mamya suu pyaminyili pyuo mailyaminyi doko panara .
47009006	Akali mende ee kuki wara pira ramo dokopa ee jingi kukiko manjo nara . Akaii mende ee malu wara pira ramo dokopa ee makande pyuo manjo nara doko suu pyalapape .
47009007	Akaii rae maiyuo kana maingi doko kando Anatumi mona retelyamo . Dokona lao akaii mendaki mendaki lao banya suu pilyamuli pyuo simbi simbi pii nao rangena suu pyaa napala kana mainya rae maipala mainya .
47009008	Dopa pyuo pirami ramo doko Anatumi isingi bange kuki lama jii nara ingilyamo . Nyepengele dupwa kapa seramopa dee wambu lapo nyisalana suu pyarami ramo kakana pyuo seramo dokona pingyu nyepala kapa konda pyuo mairamioko .
47009009	Baepole lao dokopa , Anatu baame ipyapala pendewa wambu dupwa mee maingi . Banya anjiki pingi yulu doko mee sulu singi .
47009010	Anatumi ee wara pirami lao ee wal jepala nenge nenge dokona nyisingi kandale . Doko suu pyao nakamana bange konda napala mokwa soo maiyami dokona baame walngi keyange jeramo doko andena lapala nakama keta banya yulu andanyi pyambwara .
47009011	Anatu nakama nyiso kamonganyi nembaramopa nakama mee maso bange mokwa soo maipa pyuo kararami . Dokome kana namwa keta jeraminyipa mairama wambu malu dupwame Anatu kando sangyu larami ingilyamo .
47009012	Laraminyipa yulu keyange pilyaminyi dokona renge lama palamo . Anatunya wambu nyisaraminyipa wambu malumi Anatu kando ange lapala lakandarami ingilyamo .
47009013	Nakama ipyapala bange mokwa soo mairaminyi kandapala wambu malumi nakama Koraisana waili pii keyange lao karaminyi doko yaki nyii nao rolae pyuo karaminyi lao suu pyapala Anatu ketae pyambwarami ingilyamo .
47009014	Anatumi banya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge keyange nakama jiyamosa dokona nakama kando mona andake reto ateŋa lakarami .
47009015	Anatunya renge ama mupwa wakasa mende jiyamo dokona lao sangyu lamanale .
47010001	Namba Poleme nakama piso sokondali pyuo leto . Namba nakama pipya karo dokopa pau lao anjiki pyuo karene lao letaminyi . Lapala namba nakama pipya kara napunu dokopa nakamana lao namba poralyuo kaelene letaminyiko . Dokona Koraisana kondange rengepe anjiki pingi rengepe dolapona lao piso sokondali piruwale .
47010002	Namba eparonopa poralyaiase lao pupi lao laa nalapape . Namwa rangena kingi lakandalana karaminyi letaminyi wambu dupwa kando pii poral kapa pupi lao laro .
47010003	Doko kinyi kinyi namwa isa yuu dakena karamano . Karamanopape isa yuunya lao pimwalyuo kara nalyamano .
47010004	Yanda pingi bange dusipame minyuo yanda pyuo karamano dupwa mee isa bange daa . Anatunya yanda pingi bange poral panda koo dupwa kokwa singi dusipame minyuo yanda pyuo karamano . Pii kyambo letaminyi dupwa namwa kokwa silyamano .
47010005	Wambu lapo Anatunya pii selana suu pyaminyipape suu pingi wakale dupwame nakamana kata doko rokolyaminyi . Doko pyao kokwa silyamano . Namwa suu pingi peparae nyuo malu palyapala Koraisa keta ralinyi pyambulyamano .
47010006	Nakamame namwana pii laramanuli pyuo mondo lao piraminyi dokopa nakamana yulu keyange doko kandapala wambu kamba lao karaminyi dupwa randa mairama .
47010007	Nakamame neta yanenge ketaena maro lapyamo doko iki kandelyaminyi . Akali mendeme namba Yesu Koraisana akali karo lao suu pilyase ? Dopa pira ramo baa rangena mona anda kandenale . Baa Koraisana akali ingyuo karamo dopako pyuo namwa opetaeko Koraisana akali ingyuo karamano .
47010008	Kamongome yulu andake namwa jiyamo dokona lao yuu malu mee rae maiyuo enokwanyi nembo leyonopape namba elya nalyo . Yulu andake jiyamo dokome nakama kwaenyi pyambwa napala pyuo andanyi pyambulyamo .
47010009	Nambame pepa pase pyao joo pakanyi pyambulinyi lao suu pyaa nalapape .
47010010	Akali mendeme dopa lao dokopa , Polena pepa pase pyao imbuo pii poralyuo lengeŋe , dee namwa pipya karelyamo dokopa pii kata pao laa nangeŋe dopa pyuo lara .
47010011	Dopa larako doŋo baa akali doko dopa lao suu pinyale . Yuu nanesa karo pepa pyao jowape nakama pipya role pyao karowape pii larono dupwa wakale ingyuo paa naiyamo .
47010012	Wambu nakama range lakando mupwa ingyuo karamano letaminyi dupwa pipya namwa makande pirama ingya nalyamo . Nakama kyawa sisingi bolombalo lasi dupwa lao karaminyi . Kyawa sisingi bolombalo lasi dupwa yango sukusa apiyakale lao mendeme mende makande pyuo mendeme mende makande pyuo range karo palyuo piminyili pyuo lao karaminyi .
47010013	Namwa mee langa range lakanda narama . Anatumi yulu makande pyuo jiyamo liti doko yalo paa nalyamano liti jiyamo dokona sukusa nakama karaminyi .
47010014	Liti doko yalo paa napala nakama kando nyepala Koraisana waili pii keyange boo pyao langiyama .
47010015	Akali lapo panda wakale dupwana yulu andake piyami dokona range lakanda narama . Anatunya make yalo paa napala nakama baa kapa ingingi lao angingyuo suu pyaraminyi yulu andake pyakarama lao suu pilyamano .
47010016	Enakana nakama palaminyi matarena waili pii keyange raeyo paa nalyamo dokona kapa polo lamairama . Polo lamairama ramo dokopa akali mendeme yulu piyamo dokona lao rae maiyuo pyakaiyuo pyao lao kara narama ingilyamo .
47010017	Baepole lao dokopa , Akali mendeme sipurapala lakandalana suu pyara ramo doko Kamongome yulu piyamo dupwa iki lakandena letamo .
47010018	Mendeme keyange pilyu lao suu pyapala ketae pyambusi kara nara ingilyamo . Kamongome keyange lao suu pyaramo doko ketae pyambusi kararama ingilyamo .
47011001	Kopyali pii kuki mende laro ramo dokopa mata joo kaeya namili lao leto .
47011002	Anatumi nakama poralyuo suu pyapyamuli pyuo nambame dopako pyuo suu pyao karo . Nakama enda mapwae pepo kareta , akali role pyaa nange akali mendaki nyelana rombo paiyisi petenge doko dopale ingyuo karaminyi . Nakama akali nyerami doko Koraisa .
47011003	Nakamana kyawa sisingi kwaepala Koraisana yulu mondo lao poralyuo pilyaminyi doko yaki nyesaraminyi lao mona kendalyo . Kaumi enda Ipi panga soo lamaiyuo makande piyamo doko suu pyao nakama makande pira lyakande lao suu pilyu .
47011004	Akali mende epapala dokopa Yesunya lao pii namwa lenge doko yaki nyepala Yesunya lao pii wakale palyuo lenge ramo doko nakama mee rae maiyuo soo nyilyaminyi . Imambunya piipi waili pii keyange langiyamanopape pii dolapo kame sepala dakepa kyaka wakale imambunya piipi walii pii wakalepe koto nyilyaminyi .
47011005	Nakamana aposele akali mupwa ingyuo karaminyipa namba isa palya nalyaminyi lao suu pilyu .
47011006	Namba sipurapala pii mora piso laa nange doŋo pii renge dupwa angingyuo silyu . Doko yuu malu mee rolo langiyama .
47011007	Anatunya waili pii keyange nakama polo langyuo dokopa namba nakamana yole nyii nayo . Nakama ketae pyambwalana range isa nembo kareyo . Dopa pyuo dokopa kopetame piyusi ?
47011008	Namba nakama pipya role pyao yulu piyunu dokopa Elyambu Pingi wambu wakale dupwame namba yole jiyami . Dupwana yole waa nyepala nakama nyisiyu . Pii doko mee kongwalu leto .
47011009	Dee nakama pipya role pyao karo kana mone oteyamo dokopa nakama keta kee laa nayo . Kurisene wambu yango yuu Masetonia piso epeyaminyi dupwa bange nyelana suu piyunu dusipa minyakao epeyami . Wamba namba nakama mona kendanyi pyambwa nayo kande doko rengya opetae nakama mona kendanyi pyambwa naro .
47011010	Koraisana pii kinyi namba keta palamo dokome pii dake elya nao leto . Pii doko yuu Girisi peparae dokona range pyapeta seramopa mee serami lao lalu lao leto .
47011011	Aki rengendena namba pii dake letose ? Nakama mona reta napunu dokona lao letose ? Ama daa . Mona angingyuo reto karo doko Anatu baa soo karamo .
47011012	Aposele menge dusipana yulu pilyaminyi dokona range lakandapala namwa pilyaminyi dokoko pilyamano laa nana lao namba yulu pilyu dakeko mee pela paro ingilyamo .
47011013	Akali dusipa aposele angi daa . Nakama Anatunya pii rolae laa nange . Namwa Koraisana aposele akali karamano kandalapape lao mee kyambo ingyuo lao karaminyi .
47011014	Yulu dopale doko silyamano . Sataneme alowa pipala aŋala yanga paupau lenge dopale ingyuo makande pyuo karenge .
47011015	Dokona lao Satane banya kendemande wambu alowa pipala rolae pingi rengena kendemande dopale ingyuo makande pyuo kararami ramo dokopa namwa mona nembo yamarangwa narama . Lumwa piramo yuu gii dokopa yulu piraminyili pyuo yole nyerami .
47011016	Pii lapunu doko dee kamba larowale . Mendeme namba kopyali minyuo letene lao suu pyaa nana . Dopa lao suu pyarami ramo doko namba kopyaliyoko lao kando nyerami . Nyeraminyi dokopa nambana yulu dokona lao suu pyao karo kuki range lakando kararo .
47011017	Namba epapu letono pii doko Kamongome lamaiyalase lapyamo laa nalyo . Namba range lakando kararo ramo doko namba kopyali minyarosa pira .
47011018	Wambu malu mee isa bangena suu pyapala nakama rangena kingi lakandelyaminyi dokona namba dopako pyuo pelana leto .
47011019	Nakama kendepuli ingyuo soo giso karaminyi dokona kopyali minyingi akali kando rae mailyaminyi .
47011020	Akali mendeme nakama iso nembo kararamopa panga soo minyako piramope dereke piramope randa joo elyanyi pyambwaramope doko baa mee kando nyerami ingilyamo .
47011021	Namwa dupwa inyimungu kareyamano dokome dopale ingyuo paa nayama . Dokona lapu dokopa elya pilyamo . Akali mendeme baa rangena lao lakandalana lara ramo doko namba opetae range poralyuo lakandaro . Dokona ingyuo namba kopyali pii leto .
47011022	Aposele angi daa dupwa , Ipuru rara ramo doko namba opetaeko Ipum rara . Nakama Isaraele rara ramo doko namba opetae dokoreko . Nakama Aporakamena para pyasisi ? Namba opetaeko .
47011023	Nakama Koraisana kendemandese ? Namba doko kopyalindelyamo lao seraminyipape namba kendemande mupwa ingyuo karapunupa doloma mee dolapo karaminyi . Doko namba yulu andake pyuo kareyo kande . Yuu malu karapusi palyuope yuu malu kusape nyuope dee namba andarele ingyuo repeta kumaro ingiyamopa nakama randa dopale nyii nayami .
47011024	Juu wambu dupwame wambu pyalana dokopa marapu dokome pyao karelyaminyipa yuu akalisa rema ipisu mange mendaki karo pingi doko suu pyao namba yuu kingi paki piyami .
47011025	Orome wambu dupwame yuu rema marapu dokome namba piyami . Dee yuu mendepa kana dupwame piyami . Yuu rema namba ipwa sipunya pao kareyono sipu kapu kyiya . Yuu lama kapu kyiyamopa namba walya lao nyiyaminyipape repo ingyuo kapu kyiyamo dokopa kukwa yuu gii mendaki korakama yuu gii mendaki doko peparae ipwa dokona palyuo siyu .
47011026	Namba yuu malu kata papyuo kareyono dokopa ipwa dupwa paiipalape waa nyingi akali dupwame Juu wambu yangope Juu daa rara wakale wambu dupwamepe pyalana piyami . Yuu taone dokonape imwana peyo dokopape ipwa sipu dupwanape randa epeyamopa puu angi minya nange dupwame opetaemeko randa jelana pyuo piyaminyi kareyo .
47011027	Dopa pyuo nambana yulu andake wakasa siya . Yuu malu luu pali nayo . Dee nenge ipwape nanome kumuo kareyo . Yuu malu mee nenge aeya nao anda kara nao komau see nao piyamo kareyo .
47011028	Yuu malu mee Elyambu Pingi doko randa nyilyaminyi dokome nambana mona yanyi pilyamo . Dee randa wakale lapo epelyamoko .
47011029	Elyambu Pingi wambu mendeme poralya nara ramo doko namba dopako piru . Dee mendeme yulu koo pira ramo doko namba mona nembo kararoko .
47011030	Namba rae maiyuo pyakalyuo pyao laro ramo doko namba angi daaŋa lao dokona ingyuo laro .
47011031	Namwana Kamongo Yesunya Rakane Anatu , kyambo laa nalene lao silyamo . Banya kingi poo pyasi ingyuo sulu soo sinya .
47011032	Namba yuu Damasakesa kareyonopa Kiŋi Aretasana gapomane akali dokome akali lapome namba anjirami lao taonena kambu repeta kandaro karena leya .
47011033	Taonena kana kame maiawal lasi dokona windowa mende siyamo dokona namba pisiki minyasi kameya dokona palyapala neta nembeyaminyipa neta puu pao peyo .
47012001	Rae maiyuo kingi lakandenge yulu dokome mendali nyisa nalyamo . Nyisa napyamopape kata wakale mende see nalyamo dokona mende larowale . Kamongome kombeyame dupwanape pii repa repa pyuo langiyamo dupwape polo langirowale .
47012002	Kurisene akali mende yake panda ketae dulurena lanyuo peyamo doko silyu . Yuu wamba ee kana akalisa ipisu kisima dokopa piya . ( Doko kinyi angi piyase panda kombeyame ingyuo pii repa repa piyase lao see nalyo . Anatu baa iki soo gisilyamo . )
47012003	Dee kamba leto . Akaii doko walya lao panda ama elyape peya doko silyu . ( Dee kambako leto . Doko kinyi angi piyase panda kombeyame ingyuo pii repa repa piyase lao see nalyo . Anatu baa iki soo gisilyamo . )
47012004	Baa yake panda karo dokopa pii lapo isa wambu dupwame kapa laa naramiii dupwa soo nyiya .
47012005	Dokona lao akaii dokona rae maiyuo lakandaro . Namba range lakanda naronopape namba angi daaŋa lao dokona iki laro ingilyamo .
47012006	Namba rangena kingi lakandalana lao suu pyaro ramo doko pii doko kinyi ingyaramo dokona namba kopyaii ingya nara . Wambu dupwame nambana yulu kando pii dokona pyapi pyuo soo pirami dokona iki suu pinyale . Dokona nambana lao suu pyaraminyi doko rolae ingyuo para . Namba rangena kingi lakandaro ramo doko angi ingya nara .
47012007	Bange keyange wakasa dupwa kandeyono dokome namba moŋokyaŋe see nare lao randa pyuo anga yakane kisiya . Doko Satanena kendemande ingyapyamo dokona namba pyapala moŋokyaŋe see nareŋe lao lasaka pilyamo .
47012008	Yuu remasa lao Kamongo kando ateŋa lao anga yakane doko neta nyuo nembakare lao piso siyu .
47012009	Dokopa Yesu baame dopa pyuo yano pyao langyuo , Nambana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge dokome iki emba kapa pyakara . Emba koo ingyuo papala pinya saka nange dokopa nambame poralnya renge dokome emba minyalyingi , leya . Koraisana poralnya renge namba keta palira lao namba yakara pipyamopa rae maiyuo pyakalyuo pyao karo .
47012010	Namba poral napunupape Koralsana reke lao dokome rae maiyuo karo . Koraisana reke lao wambu namba kando giyalya giyana piyaminyipape randa andake wakale wakale nyiyunupape rae maiyuo kararoko . Namba poralya nange dokopa Kamongona poralnya renge dokome paka pyao singi . Poleme Korina Wambu Dupwa Ponuyuo Suu Piya
47012011	Nakama kopetame piyaminyisa namba kopyali pii lao karo . Nakama nambana kingi lakandarami ramo doko kapa ingilyamo . Namba mende daa ingyapuli doko nakamana aposele akali wakale dupwa kamame isa pumili .
47012012	Namba nakama pipya yulu mondo lao pyuo kareyono dupwa kandapala namba aposele akali angi doko range siyami . Yuu gii dokopa yulu mupwa Anatumi namba keta piya dupwa wambu kandapala yamaranguyami . Doko wambumi yulu pii nangende piyamosa yamarangyuo kareyamiko .
47012013	Elyambu Pingi menge dupwa nyisapala nakama range kame siyusi ? Elyambu Pingi wakale dupwame nyisinya leyono dokopa nakama kando laronde kaeyo . Yuu gii dokopako Elyambu Pingi wakale dupwa pinginyili pyuo pii napala nakama iki nyuo kame siyupya . Dopa piiŋi lao suu pyaa nalapape .
47012014	Dake yuu repo ingyuo nakama kandala epana karo . Eparono dokopa nakamana bange mende nyelana pupi lao kee laa naro . Nakamana kana mone nyipulinya masa nalyo . Nakama namba mona nyilyu . Dokona ingyuo wane wanakepeme endangi rakangepe bange maiyuo rapu pinginde daa . Endangi rakangepena yulu singi .
47012015	Namba nakama nyisalana rae maiyuo nambana bangepe dee namba range opetae nakama joo otarowale . Nambame nakama mona wakasa ingyuo retelyono dokona nakamame namba mona kuki ingyuo retaramisi ?
47012016	Namba epeyono dokopa randa jii nayoŋo doko silyaminyi . Siminyipape akali mendeme kyambo panga soo minyako piiŋi leya doko akipamo leyase ?
47012017	Aki mendena minyako piyusi ? Nambame wal minyingi akali pena leyono dokopa panga soo leyopyase ?
47012018	Nambame Taitesa pisokondali pyuo lao dee Kurisene yango mende role pyao pena leyo . Taitesame nakama minyako piya letamisi ? Taitesa nambapa suu pingi mendaki palyuo yulu mendare pyuo pii nangese ?
47012019	Yuu peparae wambu dupwame pii nambwa keta yanda pimwaiyuo lakalyaminyi dokopa nambwa range kyawa minyuo letambinyi lao suu pilyamisi ? Dopa pii nalyambano . Anatunya lenge kambunya karo Koraisame pii lalapape lapyamuli pyuo letambano . Yangonemoo nambwa yulu peparae pilyambano dokome nakama nyisalana pilyambano .
47012020	Namba eparono dokopa nakama kapu kyepala wakale ingyuo kararaminyi lao pakalyo . Dee nakamame namba karareli lao suu pyaraminyi doko kaepala wakale ingyuo karasarono lapala dokona mona kendalyoko . Nakama yango sukusa lalya lao yango palyuo imbwuapala rango nao wambu yango lao nembo pyuo kararami ingilyamo . Nakama kopetame pyuo mata kando lao moŋokyaŋe soo kararami ingilyamo dupwana mona kendo karo .
47012021	Dee eparono dokopa Anatunii nakamana lenge kambu dokona namba elyanyi pyambwara dokona pakalyo . Dopa suu pyao wambu malumi yulu koo pyuo kepo enda kando lyanolyano pipala mona kapu kyii nayami dupwa nakama kando ee laro , lao suu pilyu .
47013001	Dake yuu repo pyuo namba kandala eparo ingilyamo . Buku Baepole pii dokona lao dokopa . Akali mendeme mendali kando randa maiyuo lara ramo dokopa wusinisi akali lamape remapeme baa nyiso larami ramo dokopa baa kapa kote lara letamo .
47013002	Nakama wambo yulu koo piyaminyipape dee menge lapo koo piyaminyi dupwape opetae nambana pii selapape . Pii larono doko wambo yuu gii lapo pyuo epeyono dokopa leyono pii doko nanesa karo dee kamba laro . Namba dee kamba eparono dokopa mendali pyarepala paa nana lao randa mairu .
47013003	Koraisame namba keta pii lenge dokona dokopa nakama soo gisarami . Soo gisaraminyi doko Koraisame nakama kando angangi kararande daa . Dopa pyuo banya porainya renge lasaka pira .
47013004	Baa pau lasi ingyuo kareyamopa isa mamandona pyao palyiyaminyipape Anatunya porainya renge dokome Koraisa lete karamo . Baamoo pipya pakao karenge dokome namwa opetaeko pau lasi ingyuo karenge . Anatunya porainya renge namwa keta paliramopa namwa Yesupa role pyao karo nakama rapu pyuo kararama .
47013005	Nakama Kurisene panda Kurisene angi daa lao range makande pyuo kandalapape . Koraisa Yesu nakamana mona anda palamo doko soo gisilyaminyi . Soo gisa naminde pili doko nakamana Kurisene yulu doko mee ketae pupyali .
47013006	Namwa isa puu pao paa nalyamano doko nakama soo gisamili .
47013007	Nakama yulu koo mende pii namili lao Anatu kando ateŋa lakalyamano . Ateŋa lao dokopa namwana yulu mupwa ingyuo pelyamo lao laa nalyamano . Namwa isa puu pao pelyaminyi lao suu pyaminyipape nakama yulu rolae iki pirami dokona reke lao dopa pyuo ateŋa lakalyamano .
47013008	Namwa Anatunya pii kinyi dokona isa palyalana saka nange . Yulu pilyamano doko Anatunya pii kinyi dokona nyiso pingi .
47013009	Nakama porai ingyuo karelyaminyipa namwa mee karapala rae maingi . Nakama koo mende pii naraminyipa yapasi ingyuo pisirami lao ateŋa pyakalyamano .
47013010	Renge dokona lao namba nanesale karo pepa dake pyao jilyu . Dokona namba eparonopa Kamongome namba rapu pyuo iso karare leyamopape poraiyuo pyalana pyuo kara naro . Kamongome namba rapu pyuo iso karare leyamo dokopa kwaenyi pyambwa napala pyuo andanyi pyambwalase langiya .
47013011	Yangonemoo karalapape . Koo mende pii nao mondo lao karalapape . Nambana pii dake warombo selapa . Nakama mona mendare palyuo dokopa suu pingi mendaki palyuo lambo lao karalapape . Dopa piraminyi dokopa Anatu mona retengepe mona kyuu lao singipi doko baa nakama pipya role pyao karara .
47013012	Wambu yango dupwa yako lao kingi nyuo karalapape . Anatunya wambu dae karaminyi peparaeme nakama yako letaminyiko .

47013014	Kamongo Yesu Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi rengepe Anatunya mona retenge rengepe Imambu Poo Pyasinya yalya kando petenge rengepe nakama keta palenale .
48001001	Namba Pole . Isa akali mendeme namba rombo palyapala nembowape panda akali ketako Anatumi namba aposele ingyuo rombo palyiyande daa . Yesu Koraisapa Rakane Anatu Yesu lopo nyiyamo dolapome rolae namba rombo palyiyambi .
48001002	Nambamoo akali yango dae role pyao karamano dupwa pipyame pepa dake Galasia Elyambu Pingi dupwana pyao jilyamano .
48001003	Namwana Rakane Anatupa Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana mona kyuu lao singi rengepe mona keyange palyuo ipingi rengepe nakama keta palena .
48001004	Koraisa namwana koo dupwana lao Rakane Anatunya suu pingi doko moko minyuo range kumuo palipala yulu koo dakepa silyamo dupwana lao namwa kiiramo nyiya .
48001005	Dokona lao Anatunya kingi doko lakando palu palena , doko kinyi .
48001006	Nakamba Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi dokome kyakale leyamo doo walyako lao yaki nyepala waili pii wakale mendenako pumisa namba kando yamarangulyu .
48001007	Waili pii doko lamande daa . Dokona akali lapome Koraisana waili pii doko alowa pelana pii mendena wakale kyawa sisingi bolombalo lanyi nembamisa dokona leto .
48001008	Namwa rangemepe panda aŋala yake panda karenge dupwamepe waili pii wambo mana langiyama doko yaki nyepala waili pii wakale polo langirama ramo doko baa Satanena panda dokona para ingilyamo .
48001009	Namwa wamba lao kaenge dokona kamba leto . Nakama wambo waili pii soo nyiyami doko kaepala wakale mendeko langiramo akali doko Satanena panda para ingilyamo .
48001010	Pii dae lapu doko akali dupwame namba lakandena lao lapusi ? Doko daa . Anatu rae mainyi pyambuo leto . Wambu peparae nambana kingi lena lao pilyusi ? Dopa pinya lao lao karapuli doko Koralsana kendemande angi ingya napuli .
48001011	Yangonemoo pii dake langirowale selapa . Waili pii lao karo doko akalimi wasa nayami .
48001012	Akali mendali keta soo nyuope dee mendeme namba mana langyuo pii naya . Pii nayamopape Yesu Koraisa baa rangeme waili pii namba nolakao langyuo jiya .
48001013	Namba wambo Juu wambunya misi yulu dokona sukusa karo yulu kopetame piyu dokona langiyaminyi siyami . Doko anjiki pii nao Anatunya Elyambu Pinginya wambu randa maiyuo kokwa selana suu pyao piyu .
48001014	Namba Kurisene ingyapa nayonopa tembole anda yulu mana nyuo dokopa Juu wane yango andarele dupwa nyuo isa nembowale mana nyuo kareyo . Namwana rora ambasupinya yulu palenge dupwana suu pyale pyale kareyo .
48001015	Kareyonopape Anatu mona keyange palyuo ipyapala namba ene manjipa nayami dokopa baame namba rombo palyuo banya yulu dokona pyakare lao kyakale lao kaeyapya .
48001016	Baame banya lkinyingi namba keta panaronopa waili pii keyange doko Juu daa rara wakale dupwa lamairi lao suu piyapya dokona nambame wambu mendali keta apa pyuo piru lao piso sela paa nayo .
48001017	Dopa pyuo paa naoko dee wambo aposele ingiyami dupwa Jerusaleme kareyami dokona kandala paa nayoko . Kaepala yuu Arapia walya lao papala yuu Damasakesa dokona dee lalyuo epeyo .
48001018	Enakana kana rema epo papeyamo dokopa Jerusaleme Pita kareyamo dokona papala lapo piso siyu . Siyunupa koro lama role pyao kareyamba .
48001019	Dokopa namba Kamongona yangonge Jemesa iki kandeyonopape aposele menge dupwa kanda nayo .
48001020	Pii pyao retelyo dake kinyi . Kyambo laa nalyo doko Anatu soo karamo .
48001021	Enakana yuu Siria Silisiapana liti dolapona peyo .
48001022	Yuu gii dusipana Jutia Kurisene wambu dupwame namba soo pakana palyapa nayami .
48001023	Wakale dupwame nambana yulu dupwa polo lamaiyaminyi lasi pii siyami . Nakamame lao dokopa , Akalinde namwa randa jiya kande dokome epapu waili pii wambo kokwa selana piyamo dokoko minyuo lao karamo leyami .
48001024	Leyaminyi sepala nambana yulu dokona kando Anatu lakando kareyami .
48002001	Enakana ee kana akalisa dee ipisu kisima epo papeyamopa Jerusaleme Banapasapa role pyao lambuo peyamba . Dokopa nambame Taltesa opetae lanyuo peyo .
48002002	Namba dokona mee peyonde daa . Anatumi pupili lao langiyasa peyo . Doko namba Elyambu Pingjnya mupwa dupwamoo pipya wato leyami dokona nambame waili pii Juu daa rara wakale dupwa polo lamaiyuŋu lao lamaiyu . Nambana yulu dakepape dee wambo piyunupape dupwana mee ingyuo paa nana lao suu pyao peyo .
48002003	Nambana akali yango Taltesa baa Giriki rara ingiyamopape yanenge awali lao pyakepinya lao laa nayami .
48002004	Laa nayaminyipape akali lapo namwana wato lenge dokon panga soo mee yangonge ingyuo kolalyuo epeyami dupwame baa yanenge pyakepakaminya leyami . Akali dupwame namwa pipya karo Yesu Koraisana arapunya namwa karenge dokome apa pyuo lao lowana kiiramo pasi karamano dokona maa palyuo kandala epeyami . Nakamame namwa lowa malu dupwana dee puu maiyuo bwuakarami lao suu piyami .
48002005	Nakama Kurisene dupwana lao suu pyapala waili pii dokona renge keyange dupwa isa pakami nana lao nakambana pii doko ama see nayama .
48002006	Wato lao kareyama dokona akali mupwa dupwame namba waili pii lao kareyo dokona suu pingi enenge mende langya nayami . ( Nakama kingi londapala lao kareyaminyipape namba dokona mende suu pyaa nayo . Anatumi wambu kuki andakepe lao mende suu pyaa nange kandale . )
48002007	Nakama Anatumi Pita Juu wambu dupwa keta waili pii lamaira lao mapanyi pyambuyamo doko suu pyao namba Juu daa rara wakale dupwa lamairi lao mapanyi peyalyamo lao kandeyami .
48002008	Anatunya porainya renge dokome Pita Juu wambu pipya yulu pinya lao aposele inginyi pyambuyamo dopako pyuo namba Juu daa rara wakale dupwana lao aposele inginyi pyambuya .
48002009	Jemesa Pita Jonemoo Elyambu Pinginya akali andake dusipame Anatumi yulu mupwa dake namba keta jiyalyamo lao siyami . Sepala namba Banapasapa yako lao kingi nyiyami . Namwa peparae yulu mendakinya pyuo nakama doloma Juu wambu pii lamairaminyipa nambwa rara wakale dupwa lamairama dupwana sepala kapa lao kaeyama .
48002010	Yulu mendaki iki jiyami doko wambu pendewa dupwa nyiso karalapape lao leyami . Dopa leyamioko doŋo namba dokonako suu pyao yulu poralyuo kaeyo pyuo kareyo .
48002011	Pita yuu Andioko epeyamo dokopa nambame wambu kareyami dokona baa kyal pyuo piyamo dokona pyalana pyuo rolo lamaiyu .
48002012	kali lapo Jemesame pena leya dusipa epapa nayaminyi dokopa Pita baa akali wakale yanenge kaloma nange dupwa pipya nenge nao peteya . Dee akali yanenge pyakepenge mawa pii dokona poral minyingi dupwa epapeyaminyi dokopa Pita pakapala rara wakale pipya yaki nyuo kaeyo nenge role pyao naa nao peteya .
48002013	Dokopa Juu yango lapo opetaeko pakapala Pita peyamo kata dokonako peyami . Dopa pyuo yambe pyao piyami kata dokona Banapasa opetae kaki rambe rambe palyuo panya piya .
48002014	Dopa piyamo dokona nambame kandapala waili pii rolae dokona kata angi paa nayami dokona lao wambunya lenge kambu dokona Pita kando dopa lao , Emba Juu angi kandape . Juu ingyuo kareeneko doŋo palyuo karo pipinyi dupwame Juu ingya napala rara wakale karo palyuo pilyaminyi dokonako mende ingilyamo . Dokome apa pyuo menge akali dupwa Juu inginya lao letese ? lamaiyu .
48002015	Kinyi namwa Juu rara dokona mandeyaminyi karamano . Rara menge dupwa yulu koo paleta mandeyami dopale ingyuo kara nalyamano .
48002016	Akali Yesu Koraisa kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dupwa Anatupa rolae ingyuo penge doko silyamano . Lowana moko minyingi ramo dokome rolae ingyuo paa nange . Namwa opetae Yesu Koraisa mona reto baa kapa ingingi lao suu piyamanopa dokome namwa Anatupa rolae ingyuo peyama . Lowa iki moko minyiyamali dokopa Anatupa rolae ingyuo paa nayamali . Mendeme Lowa letamuli pyuo doko iki moko minyuo pira ramo doko Anatupa rolae ingyuo paa nara .
48002017	Namwa rara menge yulu koo pingi dopale pipala Anatu namwana yulu koo dupwa kame sakana lao Koraisa dokona repeta eparama ramo doko Koraisame namwana koo dupwa kando rae maiyuo kararasa pirase ? Ama daa .
48002018	Namba Lowa wambarae kaeyapenge leyo dupwa deeko nyepala pyuo karo laro ramo doko nambame Lowa kokwa sinyi nembelene lao panara .
48002019	Lowa dokome namba mata rukyu piyamo kumasi ingyuo kareyo . Lowa rangeme dopa pyuo namba pyao kumuyamopa epapu Anatunya lete dokona karalu kararo . Koraisapa isa mamandona kumasi paleyo dokona epapu namba range angi kara nalyo . Koraisa banya lete renge doko namba keta palamo . Epapu yulu pyuo karo dupwa Anatunya lkmyingi namba mona retapala kumuyamo doko baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao pyuo karapusa pilyamoko . Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko mata maiyuo nemba nalyo . Akali dupwa Lowa dokome Anatupa rolae ingyuo peyamili doko Koraisa baa mee kumuo paleyali .
