52005028	Kamongo Yesu Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge nakama keta palena .
53001001	Rakane Anatu Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana Elyambu Pingi wambu yuu Tesalonalka karenge dokona namwa Pole Sallasa Timotimoome pepa pyao jilyamano .
53001002	Rakane Anatupa Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge dokope mona kyuu lao singi renge dokope nakama keta palena .
53001003	Yangonemoo yuu peparae nakamana lao Anatu sangyu lapenge ingilyamo . Nakamana Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko ando andakyapala nakamana wambu yango kando mona retaminyi renge doko ando pelyamoko . Ando pupyamosa namwa Anatu kando kapa sangyu letamano .
53001004	Dokona lao Anatunya Elyambu Pingi dokona nakamana yulu piminyi dupwana lakandelyamano . Wambu lapome nakama kando randa wakale wakale jiminyipape nakama kaeya nao Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karaminyi dokome namwa nakama kando rae maiyuo lakandelyamanoko .
53001005	Anatunya isingi panda dorena reke lao randa andake nyuo kata wapulyaminyi . Nakama dokona sukusa parami dokopa Anatu rolae pyuo kote lenge doko panara .
53001006	Anatu baame rolae ingyuo nakama randa jilyaminyi wambu dupwa randa maira .
53001007	Nakama randa nyilyaminyi dokona Anatumi mandaranyi pyambwara . Kamongo Yesumoo banya aŋala porai dupwamoo yake dokona piso pano eparaminyi dokopa namwa opetae koo soo pisarama .
53001008	Wambu Anatu see nangepe Kamongo Yesunya waili pii keyange warombo soo pisa nange dupwape Yesu banya aŋala poral dupwa pipya isare kekenge dokome randa maiyala eparami .
53001009	Anatu see nange wambu dupwa Kamongopa pakao kara narami . Yuu gii pyaka seramo dokopa baa poral wakasa neta renge ingyuo epapala dokopa nakama rekya lanyi nembalu nembo nembara .
53001010	Baa eparamo dokopa banya wambu baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karenge dupwame banya kingi ketae pyambuo lakandarami . Dokopa nakama waili pii langiyama doko soo nyiyami dokona nakama opetae role pyao kararami .
53001011	Namwana Anatu baame nakama kee lao rombo palyiyamuli pyuo nakama kapa karamili lao yuu peparae ateŋa lakao karamano . Anatu banya poralnya renge dokome nakama pyuo au pyuo nyeramopa nakamana kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko ando kameya inginya lao ateŋa letamano .
53001012	Dokopa namwana Kamongo Yesunya kingi doko nakama dokona mange karanyi pyambwaraminyipa nakama baame dopako pira . Dokopa namwana Anatu Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana mona keyange palyuo ipyuo pingi dokona ingyuo para .
53002001	Namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa eparamo dokopa namwa Yesumoo role pyao pisirama dokona lao langirowale .
53002002	Yangonemoo wambu lapome Kamongo Yesunya yuu gii doko wambo pyaka soo kaeya lao letaminyi dokona nakama walu lapala kyawa sisingi bolombalo lanyi nembo mona rando pisa nalapape , lao poralyuo langilyu . Pii kyal doo leyami dokona lao akali mendeme banya suu pingi dokona pyongo piyamo leya panda mendeme misi pii ingyuo leya lao see nalyo . Panda namwa Yesunya yuu gii epapeyamo dokona pepa pase pyao reteyamaŋa dolo kyambo leyami rapisa .
53002003	Dopa pyuo panga seraminyi pii doko soo nyii nalapape . Akali koo karapenge doko wambo epara dokopa yanda pii andake sipuraramopa enakana yuu gii doko pyaka sera . Akali koo karapenge doko panda koo dokona papala karalu karara .
53002004	Koo karapenge akalimi Anatunyape dee Anatunya yulu peparaepe yanda pimwalnyi pyambwara . Pyambwapala baa wakasa dulusale ingyuo suu pyao Anatunya tembole anda pao piso namba anatuŋu lao karara .
53002005	Nakama kame simisi ? Namba nakama pipya karo dokopa pii dake langiyu kande .
53002006	Langiyunupape bange mendeme akali koo karapenge doko epa nana lao minya minya silyamo . Nakama doko aki lao silyaminyi . Yuu gii angi pyaka seramopa koo karapenge akali doko baa panara .
53002007	Akali karapenge doko dakepale banya minji nanji pyuo yulu pingi doko yalu pyuo pyuo karamo . Pyuo karapyamopape baa yulu angi piramo doko ene pii nalyamo doko mendeme banya kata pyakepelyamo . Banya kata pyakepelyamo doko isa paramopa baa panara .
53002008	Panaramo dokopa Kamongo Yesumi banya porainya renge dokome akali koo karapenge doko pyao kumakao baa neta renge ingyuo yanga paupau lao eparamo dokopa akali karapenge doko isa puu pao para .
53002009	Akali koo doko Satanena porainya renge paleta epapala yulu pii nange wakale wakale dupwa pyuope yamarangungi yulu dupwa pyuoko pira .
53002010	Pipala dokopa wambu yulu koo pyuo koo keta parami dupwa kando makande wakale wakale pira . Piramo dokopa koo pingi wambu Anatunya pii angi soo nyii nao mona reta nayami dupwa kumuo otarami . Pii angi doko mona reteyamili doko nakama lete wal pyao pumili .
53002011	Dokona lao kyambo pii soo nyerami lao Anatumi nakamana kyawa sisingi ukiaki minyuo kwaenyi nembara .
53002012	Dopa piramo dokopa wambu Anatunya pii soo nyii napala koo dupwana rae maiyami dupwa koo keta parami .
53002013	Yangonemoo Kamongo Yesumi nakama mona retenge dokona lao namwame nakama suu pyao yuu peparae Anatu kando sangyu larama ingilyamo . Nakama Anatunya pii angi doko kapa ingingi lao suu pilyaminyi dokona Anatumi nakama banya wambu angi ingyara lao Imambu poralnya renge dokome nakama wambo pyuo nyeroŋa lao kee lao rombo palyiya .
53002014	Waili pii keyange polo langiyamano dokome Anatu nakama kee lao nyiya . Nyiyamo dokona namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisana neta renge doko nakama keta palira .
53002015	Yangonemoo dokona lao paka nao poralyuo suu pyao karo Anatunya pii angi langiyama dupwa minyaro karalapape . Anatunya pii angi polo langyuo pepa pase pyao joo kareyama dusipa minyaro karalapape .
53002016	Namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa baapa dee namwana Rakange Anatupame nakama poral inginyi pyambwarambi . Namwana Rakange Anatu baame namwa mona retapala mona keyange palyuo ipyuo karenge dokome namwa poralnyi pyambwalu pyambuo pyambuya . Pyambuyamosa Yesu dee epara lao mona kare kare karamano .
53002017	Nakama yulu keyange pyuope pii keyange laope mondo lao karalapa lao baame nakama poral inginyi pyambwara .
53003001	Yangonemoo epapu pii lumwa pyuo leto . Doko nakama Kamongo Yesunya waili pii keyange waiya lao sepala Anatu lakandeyami . Doko suu pyao yuu muu wakale dupwana wambu peparae walya lao soo nyepala Anatu lakandarami dokona ateŋa lakalapape .
53003002	Akali koo kopyali kopetame pingi dupwame namwa koo keta pyambwa nana lao Anatu baame namwa pyuo nyinya lao dokona opetae ateŋa lakalapapae . Renge doko wambu lapo Anatunya walii pii soo nyii nange kandale .
53003003	Kamongo Yesu baa kapa ingingi dokome nakama porainyi pyambuo Sataneme nakama keta koo mende pii nana lao kyawa minyuo karara .
53003004	Namwame nakama Kamongo Yesu keta pyamaiyinyi pyambuyama dokome namwa pii langiyama dupwa moko minyuo karapala pyuoko kararami doko soo gisilyamano .
53003005	Kamongome nyisaramopa nakama Anatu dokona mona maiyapala Koralsame yulu kaeya nao piyamo dokona mana nyepala dopako pyuo karaniiii yaka leto .
53003006	Yangonemoo Kamongo Yesu Koralsana kingi lao Kurisene wambu yango lapome namwana pii dupwa soo nyii napala yulu pelana makapala mee karaminyi dupwa role pyao kara napala yaki nyuo kaelapape .
53003007	Namwa nakama role pyao karo yulu andake piyama doko soo gisilyaminyi . Nakama sipurapala dopako pyuo yulu andake pirami doko rolaeŋe lao range silyaminyi .
53003008	Nakamana nenge nenge dupwa mee langa naa nayama . Yuu peparae range ropo pyao nyuo neyama kande . Nakamana nenge nao apa nanyi nembasarama lao suu pyapala namwa kaeya nao kukwa korakamape yulu andake pyuo kareyama .
53003009	Nakama nenge mee jinya lao kapa leyamali doŋo doko laa napala range yulu pyuo nyiyama kandapala nakama dokonako palyuo parami lao suu piyama .
53003010	Namwame wamba nakama role pyao karapala dokopa dopa pyuo langiyama kande . Mendalimi yulu pii nara ramo doko nenge anja seramo nyuo narase ? Lopara ingilyamo .
53003011	Wambu yango lapo nakama role pyao piso karo pilyaminyi dupwa nakama maka suku suku nao yulu pii nao karaminyi doko sepala letamano . Nakama range yulu pii napalape wambu yango dupwa kando mora pii lao kanda lyanolyano pyuo karaminyi .
53003012	Dokopa Kamongo Yesu Koraisana kingi doko nakama mondo lao karo yulu au pyuo poralyuo pyuo rangena yole nyerami lao laokondali pyuo letamano .
53003013	Yangonemoo yulu keyange doko maka nao pyuo karalapape .
53003014	Nakama role pyao karaminyi wambu dokona mendeme pii pepa pase dakena palamo dupwa warombo see nara ramo doko lengeme iki makande pyuo kandapala baa keta mende pii nalapape . Dopa pirami ramo dokopa baa elya nyera .
53003015	Baapa nyisu petenge ingyuo yanda pimwainyi pyambwa nalapape . Pyambwa nao baapa Kurisene yango ingyuo yulu poraiyuo pinya lao baa kando anjiki pyuo nyisalapape .
53003016	Kamongo Yesu baa range mona kyuu lao singi renge renge kuiyuo karenge dokome baame randa wakale wakale eparamopape panda rae maingi renge eparamopape yuu peparae nakama mona kyuu lao singi renge jinya . Kamongo Yesu nakama pipya role pyao karena .
53003017	Nambana rangena kingimi yako lao lenge pii dake namba rangena kingi pilyu . Pepa pase yuu wakale peparaena pyao maingi dokopa nambame dopa pyuo pingi . Namba Pole yako leto .
53003018	Kamongo Yesu Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko nakama peparae keta palena leto .
54001001	Namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya aposele akali Anatu namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi dokope Koraisa Yesu namwa keta dee epara dokope leyambinyili pyuo aposele akali ingyuo karo .
54001002	O Timoti nambana Kurisene wane angi doko emba pepa dake pyao jilyu . Rakane Anatu namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesupame mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge dokopa sakao nyiso karenge renge dokope mona kyuu lao singi rengepe emba keta palena lao leto .
54001003	Wambo namba yuu Masetonia panya karo dokopa emba yuu Epesasa dokona karare lao langiyunu doko suu pyao epapu dee kamba emba Epesasa dokona karareko langilyu . Emba doo karapala akali lapo Anatunya pii dokona kyambo letaminyi dupwa kando kaena lamairi .
54001004	Nakama sinju pii dupwape rora ambasupinya kingi dupwape ketae pyambuo lao kara nana lamairi . Pii dopale lao kararami ramo doko wambu dupwana kyawa sisingi bolombalo larasa angi doko anjuku lao saka naramisa pira . Pii kyal dokome Anatunya yulu dupwa moko minyuo paa nalyamo . Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi wambu dupwame iki Anatunya yulu rolae kandenge .
54001005	Nakama mona mendaki palyuo Anatu kapa ingingi lao kulisa palyuo suu pyapala koo mende nakama keta pali nalyamo doko monarena pyapi pyuo soo otapala kararaminyi dokopa mona retenge renge doko ando nyimbwaraŋa lao mana pii dake langilyamano .
54001006	Wambu lapome kata angi doko yaki nyepala mee kambu pii lao papyuo karaminyi .
54001007	Wambu dusipa nakama Anatunya mawa pii mana lenge akali karamwali lao karelyaminyipape pii poralyuo letaminyi dokona angi doko aki lao soo gisa nalyaminyi .
54001008	Namwame Anatu suu piyamuli pyuo Mosesena Lowa doko moko minyuo parama ramo dokopa Lowa doko keyange lao kandarama .
54001009	Anatumi lowa dupwa akali keyange dupwana lao wasa naya . Wambu lapome lowa dokona kokwa singipi karapusi palengepe wambu Anatu suu pyaa nangepe koo pingipi misi anda paa nangepe wambu Anatunya Imambunya yulu dokona see nangepe wambu lapo nakamana endangi rakangepa pyao kumakangepe dee wambu yango pyao kumakangepe peparaena serami lao wasiya Anatumi .
54001010	Dopako pyuo wambu pundange yulu pingipi wambu kepo pingipi wane wanake nyaŋa waa nyingipi wambu kyambo lengepe wambu pii kyarepa pingipi wambu angi rolae pii nangepe Anatumi nakamana lao suu pyao lowa pii dupwa wasiya .
54001011	Nakamame Anatunya waili pii keyange wakasa namba keta epelyamo doko yalo pelyaminyi dokona Anatu neta rengepe elyape keta karengepe baa lowa pii dupwa wasiya .
54001012	Namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesumi namwa poralnyi pyambuo banya yulu piri lao rombo palyiya dokona rae maiyuo sangyu leto .
54001013	Namba wambo Anatu kando pii koo lapala lekeleke rena lao baa kilya kando leyonopape namba baa soo gisa napala mee kamenge lao kareyonopa baame namba kando kondo sakao karapala sukusa nyiya .
54001014	Kamongome banya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko namba keta maralyiya . Dee kapa ingingi lao suu pingi rengepe mona retengepe dolapo Anatumi jiya . Namwa Koraisa Yesumoo pipya yalya kando role pyao karenge dokona Anatumi dusipa jingi .
54001015	pii langilyu dake ama kinyi kinyi palamo . Soo nyepala minyalapape . Koraisa Yesu baa namwana yuu dakena epapala wambu koo pingi dupwana lao lete wal pyao nyeroŋo lao epeya . Wambu doloma yulu koo pyuo kareyaminyipape namba kamame koo ingyuo kareyo .
54001016	Dopa pyuo yulu koona mupwa ingyuo piyunu dokona lapala Anatumi sakao pyuo nyuo nyisiya . Anatu baa rape rape lao karenge doko namba akali koo wakasa pingi doko keta lasaka piya . Wambu enakana Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao kyakana renge kulisa palu palenge nyerami dupwame serami lao namba keta lasaka piyasa piya .
54001017	Kuma napala karalu karenge Kiŋi doko baa wambumi kapa kanda nange Anatu mendaki doko kando wambu peparaeme lakandapala kingi ketae nembo karalu kararami doko kinyi .
54001018	O nambana wane Timoti mawa pii dake emba langilyuŋu sepe . Yuu wamba poropeta akali dupwame emba keta nolakayami dokona suu pyao karo . Pii poropeta dupwame leyami dusipa lao minyuo nyisu petenge wambu anamasi minyare .
54001019	Minyapala embena kapa ingingi lao suu pilini renge dokome minyuo embena suu pingi renge doko poo pyasi ingyuo palena lao yaki nyii nao karare . Wambu lapome yulu rolae dupwa sepala karo kando kaeyo koo pyuo kareyaminyipa nakamana Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko isa peya .
54001020	Akali lama nakambana kingi Aimeniasa Alekesandapa lenge dolapome dopako piyambi . Piyambinyisa nambame Anatunya kando pii koo laa nana lapala Satanena arapu dorena karena lamaiyu .
54002001	Wambu peparaena lao piso singipi ateŋa lengepe kee lengepe sangyu lengepe lao pii dusipa mupwa ingyuo Anatu kando lamaiyalapape lao poralyuo langilyu .
54002002	Namwa mona kyuu lao seramopa elya kalo Anatunya Imambunya yulu pyuo yulu rolae dupwa suu pyao karamwali lao Anatumi kiŋipi gapomanepe dupwa nyiso karena lao ateŋa lakamyuo karamana .
54002003	Yulu keyange dopale dokome namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi Anatu doko rae mainyi pyambungi .
54002004	Anatumi wambu peparae lete wai pyao nyelana banya pii angi soo nyimili lao suu pyao karamo .
54002005	Anatu baa mendaki iki karo , dee kanya akali mendaki doko Anatu akalipa nyuo pakao pingi doko Koraisa Yesuko karo pingi .
54002006	Akali peparae kiiramo nyelana baa range kumuo maiya . Dokome Anatumi akali peparae pyuo nyelana suu piya , yuu gii rolae doko pyaka sera dokopa panara .
54002007	Renge dokona lao namba Juu daa rara wakale dupwana aposele akali ingyuo nakama mana lao karare lao waili pii angipi Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi dokona lao Anatumi namba mapanyi nembeya . Doko nambame kyambo letonde daa . Kinyi leto .
54002008	Anatu iki suu pingi dupwa imbuo apiyanda pyuo lao kara napala yuu muu dupwana peparae ateŋa lao karamili lao suu pilyu .
54002009	Pii mende doko enda dupwa nakama inyimungu mona palenge ingyuo piso nakama range komau kapa pira dupwa mondo lao wapunya . Dopako pyuo wambu kandamili kandamili lao kyawasi kalya pyuo kupinyi dorena palya dakena palya nalapape . Moŋokyaŋe soo mola wakale wakale dupwame kalya pii nao kana malu penge komaupi wapuo pii napenge . Dee kalya wakale wakale lapo opetae pii kaena .
54002010	Yulu keyange dupwa nyuo komau ingyuo wapurami . Dopa pirami doko Imambunya kata ingyuo paramisa pira .
54002011	Misi anda dupwana nakama range inyimungu pii laa nao mee petena .
54002012	Endame mana pii lao nakamame akali rapu pili lasarami kaena leto . Nakama mee elya kalo petena .
54002013	Doko Anatumi Atame baa wambo ingyuo wasapala Ipi enakana wasiya .
54002014	Dee Sataneme akali keta wambo panga soo maralya naya . Enda doko dokona rambu lapala keta panga soo maralyamopa enda dokome Anatunya lowa pii dokona kamba leya .
54002015	Dopa piyamopape enda dupwa Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona nembo Anatunya Imambunya yulu pyuo inyimungu pisarami ramo dokopa wane mandenge yuu gii pyaka sera ramo Yesumi iso karara .
54003001	Pii dake kinyi palamo . Akali mendeme Elyambu Pinginya yulu pinya mona nyera ramo doko yulu keyange dokona pinya pirasa pira .
54003002	Dopa pyuo palamo dokona Elyambu Pinginya akali mupwa dupwa pii pali naramo kararami ingilyamo . Baa enda mendaki ikinya akalingi ingyuo karena . Moŋokyaŋe see nao rangena suu pingi kame pyuo niinyuo karo yulu rolae pyuo karena . Wambu upunili dupwa banya anda yako lao nyuo nenge pyuo pyuo karena . Baa niana lenge yulu dokona wanonguli ingyuo niana lao karapenge ingilyamo .
54003003	Dopako pyuo Elyambu Pinginya rapu pingi doko biya wasinyi nembo walya lao imbwualana wangu lakao pyakandenge akali ingyuo kara nara . Baa niona kyuu lao seramopa elya kalo karo kana monena niona nyingi ingyuo karara ingya nalyamo .
54003004	Baa rangena enda wanepe niondo lao rapu pyuo karo banya wane wanakepeme baa kando kamba laa napala banya kingi ketae nembo petena lao karara ingilyamo .
54003005	Rapu pingi baame banya enda wanepe niondo lao rapu pii narande ramo dokome apa pyuo Anatunya ree palu doko niondo lao rapu pyakamyuo kararase ?
54003006	Dokonako ingyuo ene alembole Anatu niona nialya ramo dokome baa Elyambu Pinginya rapu akali ingya nana . Dopa pyuo pira ramo dokopa Sataneme piyamuli pyuo kyaŋe singi renge dokome ipwa ingyuo palyuo pyoko pyoko larasa pira . Satane koo keta paleyamo doko suu pyao akali dopale doko koo keta palira .
54003007	Neta wambu dupwame baako kando pisirami . Moŋokyaŋe see nara ramo dokopa kando pisaranii dokome Satanena kone makara dokona lyii nara .
54003008	Elyambu Pinginya nyisingi akali dupwa mona palyuo pii lamana laa nao karapenge ingilyamo . Ipwa waene malu mee naa nao bange nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pyao karara ingya nalyamo .
54003009	Anatumi pii kinyi doko pano lasaka piyamo doko kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona dokona pyapi pyuo soo niinyaranii .
54003010	Nakamana yulu dupwa wambo makande pyuo kandapala kapa piranii lao suu pyarami ramo dokopa nyisinginya yulu dokona rombo palyaranii .
54003011	Nakambana enda opetae niona angi palenge ingyuo wambu mata kando dopale dapale , lao lao pisa narami . Nakama biya naa nao yulu rolae pyuo petena .
54003012	Elyambu Pinginya nyisingi baa enda niendaki ikinya akalingi ingyuo karara . Baame banya enda wanepe mondo lao rapu pyuo karara ingilyamo .
54003013	Wambu Anatunya yulu keyange pingi dupwana kingi wambu peparaenie ketae nembo pisirami . Nakamame Koraisa Yesunya wambu ingyuo banya waili pii keyange kapa poralyuo lamaiyuo pisirarmi .
54003014	Pepa dake wambo pyao jepala rengya repetaleko emba kandala eparo lao suu pilyu .
54003015	Namba walya lao epa naro ramo dokopa emba pepa pyao jilyu dake kando yaka lapala namwa apa pyuo Anatunya Elyambu Pingi ree palu wambu dupwa kapa rolae pinginyili pyuo pirama lao sere . Elyambu Pingi doko lete palenge Anatu dokona ingyaro karapyamopa dokome kinyinya renge dokome paka pyao sakao karamo .
54003016	Elyambu Pingi doko anda pinginya ingyaro Anatunya Imambunya yulu dokona renge yalu pyuo siyamopa kando nyiyama doko mendeme mupwa daa lao matarena pii larami ingya nalyamo . Wambu wai pyapala akali lenge kambu nyuo paneyamopa , Imambumi baa rolae wakasaŋa lao lao paneyapya . Aŋala dupwame baa kandeyamiko . Rara wakale dupwana baa dokona lao lamaiyuo peyami . Yuu muu dupwana baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona maiyami . Baa lopo epapala yake panda peya .
54004001	Imambumi rakyame akali lapo Anatunya kata yaki nyerami doko wambo nolakao letamo . Nakamame imambu mee kyambo lenge dokona pii minyuo imambu koona mana pii larami dupwana soo parami ingilyamo .
54004002	Akali pii kyal pyuo lenge dupwame panga soo lao mana pii kyambo letaminyi . Akali dusipana monarena kerange pyao otapyasa koo keyangepe anjuku lao soo saka nalyaminyi .
54004003	Akali mana koo larami dupwame lao nakama enda nyii nao nenge lapo wasaka pyuo karo pipwape larami . Nenge waso karalapape letaminyi dusipa Anatumi narami lao jiya . Wambu Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao pii kinyi doko soo nyingi dupwame ange lapala narami dokona jiya .
54004004	Bange Anatumi wasiyamo dupwana mende koo daa . Dokona mende yaki nyuo nembarama ingya nalyamo . Nenge dupwana lao Anatu kando sangyu lao nao kararama .
54004005	Anatunya pii dokope dee ateŋa dokomepe banya lenge kambu dokona nenge dupwa poo pyasi ingyuo pelyamo .
54004006	Embame pii dake Kurisene yango dupwa lamairi ramo dokome emba Koraisa Yesunya kendemande keyange ingyuo karare . Yuu gii dokopa Anatunya imambunya nenge nao pirisa pira . Imambunya nenge angi doko nakama Anatunya pii soo nyuo banya yulu poralyuo minyuo angi pyuope dolapo angi ingilyamo .
54004007	Arome pii kwaeyarali Anatu rae mai narali dupwa wasapala Imambunya yulu dokona rangeme range sukunde ingyuo kiso rolare .
54004008	Mee yulu andake piri dokome yanenge poraiyaramo dokopa yanengena yulu kapa pira . Dopaleko ingyuo imambu dokona porainyi pyambwarami ramo dokona isa pandape yake pandape laparaena kapa ingyuo pare .
54004009	Pii dake ama kinyi kinyi dokome wambu peparae soo nyepala kinyi lao suu pyarami .
54004010	Anatu lete karenge dokome baa kapa ingingi lao suu pilyamano dokona lao yulu andake randa nao pyuo karamano . Baame wambu peparae lete wai pyao kapa nyera ingyapyamopape baa mona angingyuo maingi wambu dupwa kaeya nao lete nyera ingilyamo .
54004011	Pii dapwa enda akalipi keta mana lamaiyuo letamanuli pyuo pinya lare .
54004012	Emba wanyane akali lapala wambu lapome emba pirinyi dupwa kando epekanda nasarami kando lao yulu auwo kandaramili dupwa iki yapo piri . Pii laope wambu yango mona retope Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karo emba kando laa naramili dupwana palyuo rolae pyuo karape .
54004013	Wambu peparae elyambu pyuo pisiraminyipa buku Baepole pii yaka lao misi pii lao mana lamairi . Lamaipala namba iso karowale pyuo karo dokopa yulu rema dasipanako kare kare soo piri .
54004014	Poropeta akali dupwa misi andake lao kareyaminyipa Elyambu Pinginya mupwa dupwame emba elya pyuo pyambuo nakamana kingi dupwa embena kyawana reteyami dokopa Imambumi emba keta mora petenge jiyamo doko mee kaka soo nemba napipi .
54004015	Yulu dokonako emba kumuo maipala mana nyuo piri . Pirinyi dokopa yulu doko ando paramopa wambumi kandenale .
54004016	Emba rangena yulu pyuope mana pii laope dolapona kando pyuo karape . Dopa pyuo puu pare ramo dokome emba rangepe dee wambu embena pii serami dupwape kyawa minyara ingilyamo .
54005001	Alemo dupwa kando pyalana pyuo laa nao pii elya kalo lao rakane kando lamainginyili pyuo lao rolo karare . Dopako pyuo wanyane akali dupwa embena yangone kando lamainginyili pyuo lao rolo karare .
54005002	Dee endemo dupwa endakinyi kando leto lao maso lao rolo dee mapwae dupwa kando dokopa pemalene angi lamaingi dokona kata palyuo lao rolo mende suu pyao lao kara napipi .
54005003	Enda walya dupwa saka nalya nana pyuo pisirami ramo dokopa ketae pyambuo nyiso karare .
54005004	Baa wane mandenge ramo panda apusingi karenge ramo nakambana Kurisene yulu mupwa doko endangi rakangepame wamba rapu piyambi dokona isingi rapu pyuo karena . Dopa pyuo pirami doko Anatu baa epe soo karara .
54005005	Enda waiya doko baa mendali range palya nangende ramo doko baame Anatumi mende pyakara lao suu pyao kukwa korakamape yuu peparae kaeya nao ateŋa lao petena .
54005006	Enda akalingi kumasi doko kopyali ingyuo yanengena laramuli pyuo pisira ramo doko mee peto lao lete pisiramopape kumuo kaeyo pisirasa pira .
54005007	Enda walya dupwa keta pii doko kyawa ingyuo lamairinyi soo nyerami dokona mendeme enda dupwa kando larami ingya naiyamo .
54005008	Mendeme banya ranjama mendare dee yangonge rakangepe dupwa mondo lao suu pyao rapu pii nara ramo dokome banya Kurisene yulu suu pyaa narasa pira . Mee Kurisene ingya nange akali dopale daako . Baa ama koo wakasa ingyarasa pira .
54005009	Enda walya doko wamba akali mendaki iki nyiyande ramo doko Elyambu Pinginya nyisingi enda ingyuo yulu pinya lara ramo doko kapa rombo palyuo kingi retarami . Endemo dupwa iki rombo palyarami .
54005010	Endemo yulu rolae pingi letaminyi dupwa iki rombo palyarami . Banya wane mondo lao rapu pyuo andanyi pyambuo wambu nenge pyuo Kurisene yango pipya kendemande yulu pyuo wambu randa nyerami dokopa pyuo nyiso yuu peparae yulu keyange dopale dusipa pyuo petengende ramo doko banya kingi pepana sinya .
54005011	Enda angi lapo walya ingyuo pisirami dupwa rombo palya nalapape . Nakama sipurapala akali nyelana suu pyaraminyi dokopa Yesu Koraisana yulu doko yaki nyepala parami .
54005012	Dopa pyuo pisirami enda dupwame Koraisa kando wambo lalu lao leyami pii dokona yalapala koo piramisa pira .
54005013	Enda dopale doko mora pisi napala anda kambu yaka lao papyuo pii wakale mendena laminyi dupwa palya nao lao pii laa narali dupwa kata raena lao lele lao lao pisinyi pyambuo papyuo karaminyi . Dopako pyuo pii kapa laa naramili dupwana lao yulu koo dopale dupwa mana nyilyaminyi .
54005014	Dokona enda walya dupwa akali kapa nyuo wane kando nyepala anda rapu pyuo pisipenge . Dokopa namwana yanda pimwal dupwame pii koo lao giyalya giyana pii nanale .
54005015	Dokonako enda walya lapome Anatunya kata doko yaki nyepala Satane kata dokona papelyaminyi .
54005016	Enda mende walya ingyuo peteya kande doko banya ree palu dokona Kurisene enda dupwame rapu pyuo pisirami . Doko kaepala Elyambu Pingi wambu wakale dupwame rapu pyuo karena laa narami . Elyambu Pingi doko enda waiya saka nao petaminyi dupwa nyisarami yulu doko palamo .
54005017	Elyambu Pinginya akali rapu pingi lapome Anatunya yulu doko mondo lao rapu pilyaminyi dupwa nakama yole kana konda pyuo mairami ramo doko kapa ingyara . Misi yulu dokona angingyuo pilyaminyi dupwasa leto .
54005018	Baepoleme lao dokopa , Mena bulamakaome witi jingi kambena lao kalyiya kande dokopa kambu doko puu pyakami napipi dee , Yulu pingi akalimi yole kana kapa nyepenge lao silyamano doko letamo .
54005019	Akali mendeme Elyambu Pinginya akali mupwa doko kando kyal pyuo pilyamo leya kande doko baame iki laramo dokopa pii minyakami nalapape . Dee wambu rema lamapena pii larami dokopa kote kapa larami .
54005020	Koo piyami kande dokopa wambu menge dupwana lenge kambu dokona pano pyalana pyuo lape dopa pyuo larene kandapala dokopa lapo dupwa pako kararami .
54005021	Anatu dokonape Koraisa Yesu dokonape aŋala poo pyasi dupwanape lenge kambu doko pii dake emba poralyuo langilyu . Emba wambu dupwa kando yapalya yapana pyuo lapo nyiso lapo nyisa nao pyuo kara napipi .
54005022	Kamongona yulu dokona mendali langa walya lao rombo palya napipi . Mendena koo piramo dokona mee isa lakao palele lapala pii nao range waso kandanyi nembo karare .
54005023	Yuu malu mee emba anga pingi dokona mee ipwa nao karalu kara napala embena inginya anga nyerene dokona lao waene mee kuki nare ramo doko kapa nyisara .
54005024	Wambu lapona yulu koo panelyamo dupwa kote laramo dokopa yake panda wambo pao panda koo sera . Dee wambu lapona yulu koo yalu pyuo silyamo dupwa yuu gii angi pyaka separamopa panara .
54005025	Dopako pyuo lapona yulu keyange dupwa kandelyamano . Yulu keyange yalu pyuo pilyaminyi dupwana yulu doko enakana panara silyamanoko .
54006001	Yulu pingi akali dupwame nakamana yulu pyakamaingi akali doko keyange ingyuo karamo lao suu pyao karo banya kingi ketae pyambuo pyuo kararami . Dopa pyuo kararami ramo dokopa Anatunya kingi dokonape dee Kurisene yulupi dolapona kwaelyamo laa narami .
54006002	Yulu pingi akali dupwame nakamana yulu pyakamaingi akali doko Kurisene ramo dokona baa nambana yangonge angi ingilyamo lao suu pyapala banya pii doko kamba larami ramo doko kapa ingya nara . Nakamana yulu pyakamaingi akali doko Kurisene ingyuo karenge ramo doko banya yulu ama poraiyuo mondo lao pyakamirami . Dopa pirami ramo dokopa Kurisene wambu yango dupwa nyisaramisa pira . Pii langilyu dusipa mana lamaiyuo polo lao kara .
54006003	Lapome Kamongo Yesu Koraisana pii angipi namwana misi pii rolaepe yaki nyepala pii wakale lao eparaminyi dupwa mee moŋokyaŋe sepala renge angi see nao kararami ingilyamo . Pii wakale wakale dupwana lao apiyanda pyuo karalana lalya lao karaminyi . Nakama yango palyuo sisi nyuo giyalya giyana pyuope mee nambana yulu lakao pilyaminyi lao suu pyao pingi yulu dopale pilyaminyi .
54006004	
54006005	Dokona nakama akali kyawa sisingi mondo lao pali naope dee Anatunya pii kinyi angi doko nakama keta pali nangepe mee yuu peparae apiyanda pyuo karaminyi . Wambu dopale dupwame Anatunya yulu pingi dokome nakama kamongarama lao suu pilyaminyi .
54006006	Akali mendeme Anatunya yulu rae maiyuo pyuo sikya pira ramo doko baa keta renge keyange palira .
54006007	Namwa endangimi mandeyamo dokopa bange mende minyuo epa nayama . Dee yuu dake yaki nyerama dokopa bange dokona mende minyuo paa naramako .
54006008	Dokona lao namwa epapunya ingyuo nenge komaupi kapa sera ramo dusipa kapaŋa lao suu pyao karamana .
54006009	Akali bange andake nyuo retalana suu pilyaminyi dupwa isa parami ingilyamo . Kopyali minyuo bange nyelanako suu pyarami kata dokona randa opetaeko nyerami . Randa nyeraminyipa dokome nakama nyuo sinjimu paro kokwa sinyi nembara .
54006010	Kana mone mona nyingi dokome koo dokona mona anda pingi pyarasa pira . Lapome mone dokona rungi rungi pyapala Anatunya Imambunya yulu kame silyaminyi . Dopa pipala nakamana mona dokona randa nyuo kondo mona rumbungi karaminyi .
54006011	Emba Anatunya wambu dokome yulu koo doko waso karare . Yulu rolae dokonape Anatunya Imambunya yulu angipi kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retenge rengepe Anatunya yulu yaki nyuo kaeya naope anjiki pyuope yulu dopale dupwa pyuo gii lao minyaro karare .
54006012	Wambu Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala kyakana renge nyingi doko akali bange nyelana makandenge dopale . Anatumi letena renge nyepala pyuo karare lao rombo palyiyamopa wambu malu mee kando kareyaminyipa emba sipurapala Yesunya kingi lao ketae lakandee kande .
54006013	Anatumi lete karenge renge maingi dokopa dee Koraisa Yesumi akali Pondiasa Pailate lenge kambunya karo dopa pyuoŋo lao polo leya dokope dolapona lenge kambu dokona karo epapu nambame emba dopa pyuo piri lao langilyu .
54006014	Emba mawa pii doko kokwa see nao yapasi ingyuo sinya lao poralyuo minyarenepa Kamongo Yesu Koraisa eparamo dokona iki liti pira .
54006015	Anatu baa kamongona Kamongo dee kiŋinyako Kiŋi mupwa ingyuo karenge . Baa iki wambu peparaena Rapu Pingi ama elyape ingyuo karamo . Baako Yesu eparamo gii doko pyaka seramo kandapala epena lara .
54006016	Anatu baa iki kumungi renge doko pali nange . Baa rao yanga paupau lao karelyamo dokona mendali repeta paa nange . Baa mendemepe kanda nange dee mendeme kapa kandarami ingya nangeko . Banya kingi ketae pyambuo paliramopa wambu peparae iso karalu karena , doko kinyi .
54006017	Wambu isa bange malu mee retenge dupwa moŋokyaŋe see nana lao poralyuo lamairi . Bange peparae mee ingyuo isa para dupwana lao andanyi nembo mona nyii napala Anatumi bange monarena rae maiyuo kamongarami lao jiyamo dupwana rae maiyuo mona nyuo karena lare .
54006018	Nakama bangena kamongo dupwame rango naa napala mee mokwa soo mainya suu pyapala maiyuo yulu keyange pyuo kamongo karena lamaipi .
54006019	Nakama dopa pyuo pirami ramo doko rengya kapa paiyuo parami dupwa nyuo nakamana rangena kulisa ingyuo seramisa pira . Dokona lao nakama lete kararami angi doko nyuo kaiyuo minyaramisa pira .
54006020	O Timoti emba keta Anatumi yulu jiyamo dokona waso minyuo pyuo karape . Wambu lapome soo gisapala lao karamano laminyipape pii doko Anatunya pii daa mee isa wambunya kopyali pii letaminyi dupwa waso karape . Mee pii lapo Anatunya kata dokona ingya nange dopale dupwa mata maiyuo karape . Pii dopale dupwa kyambona ingyuo singiŋi lao larami lyakande .
54006021	Wambu lapome namwa soo gisingiŋi lao karaminyi dupwa nakamame Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko papu pyuo lamisa pilyamo . Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko nakama peparae keta palena leto .
55001001	Namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya aposele akali Anatu pipili lao suu piyamuli pyuo mapanyi nembeyamopa Anatumi lete karenge nyerami lalu lao leyamo dokona Koraisa Yesumoo nyuo pakao karamano .
55001002	Nambana mona retenge wane Timoti emba keta pepa dake pyao jilyu . Rakane Anatu namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesupana mona keyange palyuo ipingipi sakao nyiso karenge mona kyuu lao singipi emba keta palena lao leto .
55001003	Nambana rora ambasupimi Anatu lakando mona suu pinginya pyapi pyuo soo lenge dokona namba opetaeko piyaminyili pyuo pipala eŋa pupyamopa Anatu sangyu lao karo . Yuu peparae kukwa korakamape ateŋa lao dokopa embena lao suu pyao Anatu sangyu lao lapa pilyu .
55001004	Namba embena ee leene dupwa suu pyapala kandapulimi kumulyu dokona epo emba kandapala dokopa raeme kumaro .
55001005	Namba embame Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mandeene doko angi ingilyamo lao kame see nalyo . Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dokore embena apusingi Loisa endakinyi Yunisapame opetae suu pyao peteyambipya . Doko suu pyao embena doko mendare ingyuo pelyamo lao silyu .
55001006	Dokona lao misi andalce dokona nambame emba kingi nyuo rombo palyiyunupa Anatumi banya yulu emba keta jiyamo doko isasa pinyi pyambuo karape lao langilyu .
55001007	Anatumi Imambu jiyamo dokome pakange renge doko jinginde daa . Pakange renge jilyuŋi lao dokopa poralnya rengepe mona retengepe range rapu pyuo karengepe dupwa Imambumi joo simbungi .
55001008	Namwana Kamongo dokona pii polo lalana elya nao dee namba banya ingyuo karapusi palo dokona lapala elya nyii napipiyoko . Dopa pyuo Anatu emba poralnyi pyambwaramopa waili pii keyange dokona lao randa emba keta eparamo epena rao laoko karape .
55001009	Baame namwa lete wal pyao nyepala banya ingyarami lao kyakale leya . Doko namwame range yulu keyange piyamande daa . Baa rangena suu piyamuli pyuo mona keyange palyuo ipyapala kyakale lao rombo palyiya . Yuu ene wasaroŋo lao karo dokopa Koraisa Yesu keta mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko joo kaeya .
55001010	Namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi akali Koraisa Yesu baa epo panapala Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko baa keta paneya . Koraisame kumunginya rengena poralnya renge namwa keta palenge doko nyuo anameya . Anamo waili pii keyange dokome kuma nange renge doko nyuo nolakaya .
55001011	Anatumi namba aposele yulupi mana lenge yulupi dolapona waili pii keyange polo lare lao rombo palyiya .
55001012	Renge dokona lao namba keta randa nyilyu . Randa nyipunupape namba dokona lao elya nalyo . Nambame akali kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karo doko range silyu . Yuu gii mupwa ene pyaka sepa naramopa yulu piri lao rombo palyakaya dokona minyuo pyuo kararo dokopa kyawa minyuo karara .
55001013	Pii langiyunuli pyuo piri lao pii angi langiyu dupwa minyuo karape . Koraisa Yesupa pakaro karaminyi dokona Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retengepe dolapo poralyuo minyuo pyuo karalu karare .
55001014	Imambu Poo Pyasi namwa maralyiyamo dokome emba nyisaramopa renge keyange emba keta palamo doko sakao sakao pyuo minyuo karape .
55001015	Yuu Esia wambu peparaeme namba yaki nyiyami dokopa Piselasa Emoseuisapa opetaemeko yaki nyiyambi doko emba silinyi .
55001016	Ouisimasa namba yuu malu mee rae mainyi pyambuyamo dokona Kamongome banya ree palu sakao pyuo nyinya . Baame namba karapusi kareyo dokona elyapala kaeya naya .
55001017	Dopa pyuo karo baa yuu Orome epapala dokopa namba kaeya nao karapala kando nyiya .
55001018	Yuu gii mupwa pyaka seramopa Kamongo dokome Ouisimasa baa sakao nyiso karena lao suu pilyu . Embame nambana lao yuu Epesasa dokona Ouisimasame yulu andake pyakaya doko ama soo gisasi karene .
55002001	Nambana wane Timoti emba Koraisa Yesupa pakao karo baa mona keyange palyapala ipyuo kararamopa porayapala karape .
55002002	Wambu malu soo kareyaminyipa lao kareyo pii dupwa emba soo gisii kande dupwa embame wambu mona palenge dupwa lamairinyipa nakama soo nyepala wambu wakale lamairami dokona mana lamaiyuo karape .
55002003	Koraisa Yesunya yanda pyakamaingi akali ingyuo yasoko nao karare ingilyamo .
55002004	Akali aminya yulu pingi dupwa yulu wakalena minyuo komonda nange . Baa aminya yulu dokona yeelyo ami rapu pingi akali mupwa doko rae mainyi pyambuo pingi .
55002005	Akali bange nyelana makandenge baame makandengena lowa dupwa minya napala dokome bange nyuo kapa wini larande daa .
55002006	Ee wara pingi akalimi randa nao yulu poralyuo piramo dokome ee mupwasa doko manjo nara ingilyamo .
55002007	Namba pii langilyu dupwa apa pyuonde lao suu pyao pisirinyipa Kamongome epapala nyisaramo dokopa kapa rolo sere .
55002008	Yesu Koraisa Dapitinya para pyasi baa kumuo palyuo lopo epeyamo dokona waili pii keyange nambame lao karo doko suu pyaoko karape .
55002009	Namba waili pii keyange lapunu dokona lao randa nyipunupa wambu pingi akali dopale ingyuo puu saneme kiimbwaminyi karo . Dopa piminyipape Anatunya pii doko puu maiyuo retarami ingya nalyamo .
55002010	Dokona lao Anatunya rombo palyisi wambunya reke lao randa peparae nyuo karapusa pilyamo . Doko Koraisa Yesumi nakama opetae lete nyakaramopa yanga paupau lenge panda dokona karalu kararami lao randa nao karo .
55002011	Pii dake angingyuo letamo lao soo nyimana . Namwa Yesu kumuyamo dokona kumuyamande ramo doko baa lete karamuli pyuo karamwasa pilyamo .
55002012	Namwa Anatunya yulu reto kaeya nao pyuo kararama ramo doko baapa role pyao iso kararamasa pira . Banya kingi reto kaeyarama ramo doko baame namwana kingi reto kaeyarako .
55002013	Namwame banya yulu au pyuo rape rape lao pii nao karamanopape baame namwa yaki nyii nara . Baa rolae dupwa renge kniyuo pyuo karenge dokome alowa pipala kopetame pira ingya nalyamo .
55002014	Pii dakeme embena wambu dupwa dee kamba mana lamairi . Dopa pyuo Anatunya kingi lao nakama pii wakale wakaleme minyuo yanda pii nana lao lamaipi . Pii dopale dokome wambu nyisa napala , serami wambu dupwa kokwa serasa pingi .
55002015	Emba yulu poraiyuo pipala Anatunya lenge kambu dorena angi yulu pingi wambuŋu lao kandaraminyi karape . Yulu akali angimi rangena yulu dupwana elya nyii nange . Dopale ingyuo Anatunya waili pii doko rolae mana lamairi .
55002016	Anatunya daa mee kopyali pii larami dokome Anatunya kata dupwana rekya lao paramili dopale dupwana wanjo karape .
55002017	Nakamame mana lamairami doko rete andake minjunya pipala ipwange nao isa ingyuo kulimbungi dopale . Aimeniasa Pallitasapa dolapo dokona mana lao karambinyi .
55002018	Nakama pii kinyi angi rolae lenge kata doko yaki nyepala wambu wambo kumuyami dupwa lopo neta epapeyami lao kyambo lao karaminyi . Nakambana pii dopale dokome akali lapona Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko ipwa palyinyi nembo lamisa pilyamo .
55002019	Dopa laminyipape Kurisene yulu doko Anatumi kanda soo piyamo doko ama poral wakasa ingyaro karamo dokome isa paa nara . Dokona pii dasipa pyasi palamo . Kamongo baame apimoo banya lao soo karamo . Mendeme , Namba Kamongona karo lara ramo doko baa koo dupwana rekya lanyi nembo kararasa pira .
55002020	Anda andake dokona pete sanapengepe rara wakale wakale dupwa singi . Dokona lapo golope kana kulingipimi wasisi dee lapo isape yuupimi wasisi dupwa singi . Lapo ama yapasi ingilyamosa mee langa nyuo yulu pii nange . Lapome meeŋe lapala dokome andakarena yulu pingi .
55002021	Dokona suu pyao mendeme range waso poo pyasi ingyuo karara ramo doko baa yulu yapasi dupwana pira . Kamongo Anatumi baa rombo palyapala banya yulu mupwa lapo dupwa opetaeko pyakana lara ingilyamo . Dokona lao yulu keyange peparaena kapa pira ingilyamo .

58006020	Yesu baa panda dokona wambo sukusa papala Melekiseteke piyamo apo dokona namwana purisi mupwa ingyuo karalu karara .
58007001	Melekiseteke baa yuu Seleme dokona kiŋi ingyuo karo Anatu wakasa karenge dokona purisi ingyuo kareya . Aporakameme yanda pyuo kiŋi dupwa pyao wini lapala epeyamopa Melekiseteke baa kando nyepala Anatunya kingi lao elyape keta pena leya .
58007002	Aporakame yanda pyapala apa nao nyiyamo bange akalisa dupwana mendaki yapo nyepa nyepa pyuo karo Melekiseteke maiya . ( Melekiseteke kingi wambo doko rolae pinginya kiŋi leyami . Yuu Seleme doko Ipuru pii lao mona kyuu lao singi dopale dokonako palyuo Melekiseteke baa yuu dokopa kiŋi yulu piyasa mona kyuu lao singinya kiŋi karamo leyamiko . )
58007003	Baa endangi rakangepe apimi mandeya lao banya wambu dokona mendepe pakana palyuo see nayami . Baa kyakala peyami dokope kumuya dokope see nayamioko . Baa Anatunya Ikinyingi dopale purisi akali ingyuo puu pao para ingiya .
58007004	Akali kyawa mendaki Aporakame banya apa nao bange nyiyamo dokona akalisa doko pingyu nyuo maipa piyamo dokome Melekiseteke baa andake wakasa kareya doko panelyamo .
58007005	Lipaena rara purisi ingyuo karenge dupwa suu pyao Lowame lao dokopa wambu peparae bange akalisa dupwana pingyu nyepa nyepa pyuo karo maipa pirami ingingi leya . Doko nakama peparae Juu rara ranjama mendaki Aporakamena para pyasi ingiyamopape Lipaena rara doko bange kapa pingyu mairami ingiya .
58007006	Melekiseteke baa Lipaena rara dokona angi ingya nayamopape Anatunya akali andake Aporakamena bange akalisa dokona mendena mendena pyuo pingyu nyiya . Nyepala Anatumi Aporakame elyape keta karena lao lalu lao lasi dokoko Melekisetekeme banya pii dokome opetae elyape karenako leya .
58007007	Elyape keta palena lao pii lenge akali baa ketae ingyuo karelyamopa pii soo nyingi doko isa ingyuo karenge doko soo gisilyamano .
58007008	Namwa Anatu lao bange akalisa dokona mendaki larapu purisi mee kumuo parami dupwa maiyuo karenge kandale . Melekiseteke dokona lao lete mee karamo laminyi silyamano .
58007009	Aporakame Melekiseteke katasa kandapala bange maiya . Yuu gii dokopa Lipae baa rakange kyawa Aporakamena imbwange dokona baame opetae Aporakame keta Melekiseteke maiyasa piya .
58007010	Dopa letamo dokome Melekisetekeme Lipaena bange lapo opetae nyiya ingilyamo .
58007011	Lipaena rara purisi ingyuo kareyami dupwame Lowa doko nyepala minyuo lao kareyami . Dokona lao Lipaena purisi yulu dokome enda akalipi elyape keta peteyamili doko purisi mende Erone yale daande Melekisetekepa mandande epeyalisi ?
58007012	Purisi alowa pirami doko lowa kare kare alowa pira ingyuo silyamo .
58007013	Purisi enenge doko namwana Kamongo dokonasa letamo . Doko baa Lipaena rara ingya naya . Banya rara dokona mendeme bange Anatu kiso maingi kana pyare dokona wamba yulu pyuo kara nange .
58007014	Baa Jutana rara dokona mandeyami dokona Moseseme Juta baa purisi ingyuo karara laope laa nayapya doko silyamano .
58007015	Dopa pyuo leyamo doko randa nao soo nyeraminde daa . Renge doko purisi mende wakale Melekiseteke dopale epeya .
58007016	Lipaena rarame pinginyili pyuo wambunya yulu palyuo Yesu purisi ingyuo rombo palyuo kareyaminde daa . Baa lete karalu karara renge poral dokome purisi ingyuo peya .
58007017	Baepolena lao dokopa , Embame Melekiseteke apo dokona ingyuo purisi akali karalu karare letamo .
58007018	Lowa wamba dokome yulu angi ingyuo pira ingya nayamosa Anatumi alowa pyuo wakale palyiya .
58007019	Mosesena Lowa dokome wambu mendali rolae inginyi pyambwa naya . Pyambwa nayamopape Koraisa keta kapa paramo doko soo nyepala Anatupa repe repe pyuo epo karamano .
58007020	Anatumi Koraisa denge palyuo lao , Purisi ingyuo karalu kararaŋa baame mee epe epe lao yakane ingyuo leyande daa . Kana yuwale pyuo lao reteya , leya . Purisi menge dupwana pii dopale lao reta nangepya .
58007021	
58007022	Dokona ingyuo Anatumi dopa pyuo Yesu purisi karalu karare lao lalu lao leyamo doko enenge kamame keyange enenge ingyuo para .
58007023	Purisi doloma yulu doko pyuo puu pao paa narami ingiyasa kumuyaminyipa malu mee karapa piyami .
58007024	Yesu baa lete karo banya purisi yulu doko mee pyuo kararamoko karara .
58007025	Isa wambumi Anatu karamo dokona eparami dokona Yesu baame lamaiyakamingi akali ingyuo karalu karenge , Dokona lao baa kukingisa karenge akali ingyuo Anatu keta eparami dupwa pyuo nyulu nyuo nyera ,
58007026	Yesu baa purisi mupwa keyange dokome randa epelyamo dupwa kunjinyi nembakao angi kapa pyala paramopa nyisara . Baa yulu koo mende pii napala poo pyasi ingyuo karamo . Baa isa wambu koo pingi dokona yapo nyisinde yake panda dokona karamo .
58007027	Baa purisi menge dopale daa . Doloma nakama rangena koo dupwana wambo Anatu dokona lao mena pyao kiso maipala enakana wambu menge dupwana lao kiso maiyakamingi . Baa dopa pyuo pii napala yuu mendaki dokonako baa range Anatu dokona namwana lao kumuo maiya .
58007028	Mosesena Lowana yulu paleyamo dokopa mee isa akali koo palenge dupwa purisi ingyuo kareyami . Enakana Anatumi banya pii lao kana minyiyamo dokome banya Ikinyingi baa yapasi ingyuo purisi yulu pyuo karaiu karara leya .
58008001	Pii angi leto dupwana renge simuisa doko dakeŋe . Namwana purisi mupwa doko Anatu wakasa dokona kingi rolaerename yake panda dorena petamo .
58008002	Baa panda poo pyasi dokona purisinya yulu pyuo karamo . Tembole anda doko isa wambumi pii nayaminyipa Kamongome anda angi doko rangeme pyuo wasiya .
58008003	Purisi mupwa peparaeme Anatu bange maingi dupwa minyuo epo mena pyao kiso maiyuo pyuo karenge . Dopa pilyamo dokona lao namwana purisi mupwa opetaeko mende kiso mairamo doko kapa ingyuo para .
58008004	Baa isa panda pyuo karapyali doko purisi angingyuo rombo palya nayamiii . Mee purisi dupwame Juu wambunya Lowa minyuo mena kiso Anatu maingi kandale .
58008005	Doko nakama kulisa palyuo pii nao yake pandana yulu angi dupwa mee makande pyuo pyuo karenge . Mosesena yulu mendaki dopale ingyuo peya kande . Doko baame Anatunya tembole anda komaume wasisi pinya pyuo kareyamo dokopa Anatumi lao , Yuu kyaunya kareenepa lasaka piyu kande doko suu pyao kopetame pisarono kando lao angi rolae makande pyuo piri lao laokondali pyuo leto lamaiya .
58008006	Doko Koraisana purisi yulu dokome purisi dolomana yulu isa palyiya . Doko suu pyao Yesu kanya akali ingyuo kareyamo dokome Anatupa namwa pipa enakana lalu lao leyamo doko renge kamame keyange nyerami dupwa suusa isa ingiyamosa wambo lalu lao leyamo doko pyalya pyalya paleya
58008007	Wambo doko kapa paleyali doko kana minyuo lenge pii enenge doko epa nayali .
58008008	Anatumi banya wambu dupwa rae mai napala dopa leya . Yuu mendepa nambana kana minyuo lala lao lenge pii doko Isaraele dee Juta rara pipape laronyaŋa leya .
58008009	Kana minyingi pii dake nambame nakamana kauwanemoo pipa Isipi dokona neta nyiyu dokopa kii minyuo papala lao reteyo dopale daa . Lalu lao leyo pii doko yalo kareyamisa nakamba mata maiyuo kaeyo letamo Kamongome .
58008010	Dokona lao lalu lao lenge pii enenge mende Isaraele wambu pipa laro letamo . Doko nambana lowa dupwa nakamana suu pingi dorena retaro . Nakamana mona anda dokona nambana lowa dupwa pepana ingyuo pyao retaro . Nambame nakamana Anatu angingyuo kararonopa nakama nambana wambu angingyuo parami .
58008011	Nakamana andare dokona yango sukusa dopa pinya dopa pinya lao kara naramioko . Yangonge dupwa kandowape emba Kamongo doko soo nyinya lao laa naramioko . Yuu gii dokopa wambu kuki andakepe peparae namba soo nyerami .
58008012	Nakama koo pirami dokopa nambame sakame kumuo karapala nakamana koo dupwa nyuo kame silya sana pyuo kaeyaro leya .
58008013	Anatumi lalu lao lenge pii enenge retelyo leya doko wambarae doko isa pelyamo lao leyasa piya . Bange wambarae momo nelyamo dokopa mee isa penge kandale .
58009001	Wambo Anatumi wambu pipa lalu lao leyamo dokona pii lapo kingi wapambupi lakao misi larami dokona lao reteya . Misi leyami anda doko mee isa panda dakena piyamipya .
58009002	Tembole anda komaumi wasisi dokona panda kamarena doko panda kingi poo pyasi leyami . Anda dokona lambe mendepe dee raepope dee borete Anatu kingi lao maingi dokope reteyami .
58009003	Tembole anda dokona nakama komau mendeme sukusa dokona apya ingyuo liti pyuo urumu mende wasiyami . Panda lapo pyuo doko kingi Kamame Poo Pyasi leyami .
58009004	Urumu dokona rendamu pingi kiso maingi kana pyare golome wasisi dokope dee Anatunya Kana Minyuo Lalu Lao Lenge Pii Palenge Bokote , yanenge ketae dokona golome rambu lao wasisi dokope reteyami . Bokote dokona penge mende golome wasisi dokona nenge myana lenge pyanapala reteyaminyi siya . Dokona Eronena pangali isa dokona isa imbu piya dokopa dee kana lamana mawa pii pyao maiyamo dolapo paleta reto kareyami .
58009005	Bokote singi ketaerename aŋala serapeme lenge dolapome koo dupwana nyuo kame sakamaingi pyuo nyingi rate dorena papake dolapome sinyinyi pyambwaro kareyambi . Dokona lao pii malu palipyamopape dakepa renge dupwa pyaa nalyo .
58009006	Bange peparae rapa rapa pipala dokopa panda mupwa dokona yulu paleyamo dokopa purisi dupwa rangena yulu pelana mee maso kolandeyami .
58009007	Tembole anda urumu lapo pyuo dokona purisi mupwame iki papala ee kana mendena larapu karapa pingi . Banya koo dupwanape dee wambu kamenge koo piyami dupwanape lao ranjama minyuo kisala kolando papa piya .
58009008	Panda mupwa dokome panda poo pyasi doko nee piro silyamosa namwa dokona sukusa parama ingya nange doko Imambu Poo Pyasi dokome Iasaka pilyamo .
58009009	Pii wamba lao ranaisa poko sereyami doko yuu mange dakepana manda manjo palamo . Lowa wambarae dokona bange mee maingi dee kiso maingipi yulu dupwa paleya . Dopa piyaminyipape mena kiso maiyaminyi dupwana monarena koo dupwa angi kwuanyi nembakamiyande daa .
58009010	Lowa wambarae dupwana nengepe ipwape dee Juu wambunya wate pingi yulu dupwanape lao waso kareyami dupwa yanengena lowa iki ingiya . Lowa wambarae doko mee kingi wai lete lao minyaro kareyaminyipape enakana angi doko epara ingiya .
58009011	Yulu enenge epelyamo dupwana Koraisa baa purisi mupwa ingyaro karamo . Tembole anda wakasa wambunya kingi mono palyuo isa panda pyuo wasiyamande daa baame dokonako pyuo karenge .
58009012	Yesu Koraisa mena meme bulamakaopena rajama doko minyuo andakare paa naya . Rangena ranjama yuu mendaki dokonako kumuo maiya dokome namwa ropo pyao nyulu nyuo nyiyasa piya .
58009013	Lowa wambarae dokome akali mende koo pilyamo dokopa purisi mupwa dokome memepe panda bulamakao kalyuwape dee bulamakao inyape kisinyi nembenge dokopa rao pee ingyuo penge doko nyepala akali koo pisi dupwa keta pyarendanyi pyambuo kisakamaingi . Dopa pipala Anatunya lenge kambu dokona nakamana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakasi silyamo lenge .
58009014	Dopa pyuo kareyamiko doŋo Koraisana ranjama dokona yulu dupwana manda manji naya . Koraisa koo mende pali nange doko baame Imambu lete karaiu karenge doko keta Anatu dokona namwana koo dupwana lao kumuo maiya . Banya ranjama dokome namwana yulu angi kapa pali nange dupwa poo pyanyi nembaramopa Anatu lete karenge dokona yulu minyarama .
58009015	Anatumi sukusa ipupwape lao kyakale leyamo dupwa keta lete renge mairunya leyamo doko nyepala karalu kararami lao Koraisa baa Anatunya lalu lao lenge pii enenge dokona kanya akali ingyuo kareya . Nakama ropo pyao nyili lao baa kumapala mawa pii wambarae siyamopa koo pyuo kareyami doko nembakamiya .
58009016	Juu wambunya yulu pinginyili pyuo akali mendeme kumalana karo dokopa wambo moyange dupwa dopa pyuo mokwa soo nyerami lao pepana pyao retenge . Baa ene kumapa naramo dokopa bange mokwa soo nyii nange .
58009017	Baa lete kararamo dokopa bange dokona pii mende pali nara . Kumaramo dokopa pii leyamo doko angingyuo para .
58009018	Yulu dopale palenge dopako pyuo lalu lao lenge mawa pii wambarae doko ranjama iki dokome elyape ingyuo siya .
58009019	Doko Moseseme Mawa Pii wambu dupwa polo lamaipala dokopa enakana mena bulamakao memepena ranjama doko ipwa pipa wanya puu wale kone dee yoko lapopeme poeyuo nyuo buku lowa palenge dokonape dee wambu ketape raiye raiye minyuo pyarendanyi piso piya .
58009020	Pyuo dokopa Moseseme lao Anatumi pimana lao lalu lao leyamo doko ranjama dakeme kiso pii kapa wai wara pisi silyamo leya .
58009021	Dopako pyuo Moseseme tembole andape dee petenge isa akipare siyamo dupwa opetaeko ranjama piya .
58009022	Lowame leyamuli pyuo ranjama dokome bange peparae wate pyuo poo pyao nyepa pingi . Dopako pyuo ranjama isa para ramo dokome koo dupwa nyuo kame sera ingyasi siya .
58009023	Yake pandana bange angi singi dupwana makande minyuo bange lapo nakamana tembole andana reteyami dupwa dopako pyuo menana ranjama dokome poo pyao reteyaminyipape yake pandana bange angi dupwa bange angindeme kiso mairamo mona palira ingiya .
58009024	Isa wambumi yake pandana tembole poo pyasi doko suu pyao panda dakena makande pyuo wasiyami anda dokona Koraisa kolando peyande daa . Baa yake pandana angi dorena papala doko dakepa wambu dupwana lao Anatunya lenge kambu dorena karamo .
58009025	Juu wambunya purisi mupwa dupwana ee kana yaka lao mena ranjama minyuo tembole andana urumu poo pyasi dokona penge . Dopa pyuo piyaminyipape Koraisa baa ee kana peparaena kumapa kumapa pyuo kareyande daa .
58009026	Baa ee kana yaka lao kumuo maiyuo peyali doko Anatumi yuu wasiyamo dokona piso yuu malu randako pyuo ipu epeyali . Doko kaepala yuu gii repeta lumwa pira ingiyamopa Koraisa isa epo namwana koo dupwa rekya lao nyelana suu pyapala yuu mendakisa kumuo maiya .
58009027	Wambu peparae yuu gii mendakiko iki kumungi kandale dokona enakana doko Anatumi kote sera .
58009028	Koraisa baa wambo yuu mendaki iki wambunya koo dupwana lao Anatupa kumuo maiyuo kaeya . Dee eparamo doko koo dupwanako kumala eparande daa . Baa epelyape lao iso pisarami dupwa nyeramo dokona suu pyale pyale epara .
58010001	Juu wambunya Lowa doko lowa kulisa angi dokona mee kongwalu palyuo sipyasa pilyamo . Angi eparamo doko dopaleNe lao mee makande pyuo piyasa piya . Ee kana epo pao piyamo yaka lao Anatu lao mena pyao kiso maingi yulu doko mee minyaro petenge . Dopa pyuo epo mena pyao kiso piyaminyipape nakama rolo paa nayami .
58010002	Dopa pyuo paa nayamosa nakama ee kana yaka lao koo dupwana mee alya lao mena pyao kiso pyuoko kareyami . Mena pyao kiso maiyami dokopa koo dupwa angi isa pelyamo lao siyamili doko deeko pyao kisapa kisapa piyami doko kaeyamili .
58010003	
58010004	Doko mena bulamakao kalyuwa dee memepena ranjama dokome wambunya koo dupwa isa paa nange .
58010005	Doko kandapala Koraisa baa isa panda oo epena piso dokopa Anatu kando , Emba menana rendamu nyelana rae mai napala namba yanenge wal pyapala kumuo jelase lao rapa rapa pyaane leya .
58010006	Nakamana koo dupwa kame sakalase lao mena pyao kiso jilyaminyi doko rae maiyuo nyii nalene kandelyo .
58010007	Kandapala nambame buku kao pele pele lasi dokona leyamuli pyuo dae karo . Emba suu pyarenyili pyuo piri leya .
58010008	Yesumi Anatu kando wambo dopa leya . Yulu koo palamo dokona suu pyao Lowa letamuli pyuo mena kiso jiminyi dupwana rae mailyinde daa . Dee rendamu pingi kana pyare doko emba epekanda nalenyako .
58010009	Pii doko lapala pii mende konda pyuo lao , Namba dae karo doko doŋo . Emba pinya lao suu pyarenyili pyuo piru leya . Anatumi yulu wambarae doko nembapala Koraisana kumuo maingi yulu enenge dokome alowa pyuo panda nyiya .
58010010	Yesu Koraisame Anatu leyamuli pyuo baa rangena yongo doko Anatu suu pyao mendakisa iki kumuo maiya dokome namwana koo dupwana elya pinyi nembo nyiya .
58010011	Juu wambunya purisi dupwame yuu peparae tembole andana yulu pyuo mena kiso maipa maipa pyuo karenge . Dopa pilyaminyipape koo dupwa nyuo angi nembakamira ingya nange .
58010012	Koraisa baa yuu mendakinya kumuo maiyuo dokome mena kiso maingi yulu doko kyawa pyaiu pyao piyamopa Anatunya kingi rolaerename dokona peya .
58010013	Pao pisipala Anatumi Yesu banya nyisu petenge dupwa banya kimbu yukuna isarena nyuo kaiyinya laramo mange doko isaro karamo .
58010014	Baa yuu mendakisa iki range kumuo maiya dokome Kurisene ingiyami dupwa elya pyuo nyulu nyuo nyiya .
58010015	Dokona ingyuo Imambu Poo Pyasinya pii mende palipyamo wambo ingyuo letamo .
58010016	Kamongome lao dokopa , yuu gii doko pyaka separamopa lala lao lenge pii dake nakama pipya laro nambana lowa dupwa nakamana mona anda retapala suu pingi dokona pyao paiyakaro letamoko .
58010017	Pii leyamo dokona ayemba nembele lao lao , Nakamana yulu koo kopeta kapeta pyuo kareyami dupwana deeko suu pyale pyale kara naro letamo .
58010018	Dokona ingyuo koo dupwa kame sakasi seramo dokona apa pyuo dee kamba mena kiso maiyuo piramisi ?
58010019	Yangonemoo Yesunya ranjama namwana lao kukmbuo jiyamo dokona lao urumu kamame poo pyasi dokona mendeme kata rokwa naramopa kapa parama .
58010020	Komaumi nee piro kareyamopape Yesumi lete nyingi kata enenge doko rangena yongo dokome wapwakaya .
58010021	Epapu namwana purisi ama keyange doko Anatunya wambu rapu pyuo karamo .
58010022	Dokona lao suu pingi lamana palya nao Anatu baame namwa kapa nyera doko soo gisapala karo mona anda yapasi dokome koo mende range keta pali nalyamo doko monarena pyapi pyuo soo kaepala ipwa yapasi dokome yongo wate pipala Anatu dokona repe repe pyuo monale .
58010023	Yesu epapala elyape keta palyara lao karamano suu pingi doko manjo karamana . Anatu lao kaeyamo dokona dee alowa pii nara doko soo gisilyamano .
58010024	Namwa yango sukusa dokona apa pyuo wambu dupwa mona maiyuo yulu keyange pyakamirama lao kata dokona suu pyao pyuo karamanale .
58010025	Wambu yango lapo misi anda paa nalyaminyi dopale ingyuo kara napala Kamongona yuu gii repetale pyaka seralyamo dokona misi anda imili lao pyuo karalapape .
58010026	Yesunya pii angi sepalape kandakinyuo yulu koo pirama ramo doko pyao kiso maingi yulu wakale mendeme koo doko kwua nara ingilyamo .
58010027	Doko Anatu banya yanda pimwal kando kote lapala isare renge panda dokona kopeta kapeta pena laralyamo lao suu pyao mona nembo kararama ingilyamo .
58010028	Juu wambu mendeme Mosesena Lowa yalaramo dokopa wambu lama panda remame baa kando leyami kande doko akali dokona lao sakao kara napala pyao kumarami yulu singi kandale .
58010029	Doko suu pyao mendeme Anatunya Ikinyingi dokona kandanyi nembapala Anatunya lalu lao leyami pii kapa wai wara pyuo piyamo ranjama wamba poo pyao nyiya doko meeŋe lao suu pyao , mona keyange palyapala ipingi Imambu doko kilya kando lara ramo doko baa keta apa pirase ? Baa randa dokona kuki ingyuo paralya silisi ?
58010030	Koo pirami dokona namba range isingi pyakaro . Nambame bakeme pyuo isingi pyakaro leya doko apimi leya namwa silyamano . Dee pii mende , Kamongome banya wambu peparae kando kote pii laro leya .
58010031	Dokona ingyuo Anatu lete karenge dokome mende koo keta pena lara ramo doko baa randa nao lepo soo para .
58010032	Nakama wamba Kurisene yulu dokona reke lao randa nyuo kareyami kande doko suu pyalapape . Yulu enenge epo eŋa peyamo dokona lapome nakama randa andake jiyami dokona maka napala mee pyuoko kareyami .
58010033	Yuu lapo nakama wambunya lenge kambu dokona nyuo karapala kilya kando mona kendanyi pyambuo lao kareyami . Dee yuu lapo wambu dopa pyuo randa nyiyami dupwa yaki nyii napala nyiso role pyao kareyami .
58010034	Wambu lapo puu anda paleyami dupwa kando kondo karo dee nakama rangena bange nyakamiyami dokopa mona yaepo kareyami . Nakamame bange kulisa sulu singi doko nyerama lao soo kapa kareyami .
58010035	Nakama mona porayapala paka nalapape . Yole keyange nyerami ingilyamo .
58010036	Anatu laramuli pyuo maka nao waa waa lao pyuo kararami ramo doko baa yole jeroŋo laa lasaka piyamo dupwa nyerami ingilyamo .
58010037	Dokona ingyuo Baepolena pii mende pyasi palamo doko . Mende epopyamo doko baa kaeya napala oo repetale epena pyuo karamo .
